\imt1 Akar faragha zuim
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam…®n aven, Israelia namba 2…®n dughiam…®n God…®n Araziba ini, eght…® da men n…®ghn…®ziba f…®va gavgavim men navir averiabar an…®ngam. Dughiar kam…®n, Israelia Moapian nguazim gapiaghav ikia, egh Jordan…®n Fanem abigh Kenan…®n nguazim iniasava ami. Moses me ko mang…®ghan kogham, kamagh…®n, a uan akar abuananam isa me gan…®ngi. Moses m…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevir 3pla isa Israelia gan…®ngi, ez…® ak…®nafarim…®n abuan m…®g…®r…®g…®aba Moses…®n ovevem…®n eghaghanim an iti.
\ip Moses kamagh…®n akar ekiabar gun m…®gei. A God Israelian darorir kam…®n men gara me bagha amizir ingangarir ekiar av…®riba, uam a dagh n…®ghn…®si. God uab…® uan gavgavim…®n men akura, kamagh…®n amiz…®, me an apengan ikiam. Moses ua God…®n 10plan Akar Gavgaviba dar gun m…®gei, egha God…®n Akar Gavgavir kabar m…®ngarir maba, a Israelian ik…®r…®m…®rim bagha me geghari. A God…®n Akar Gavgavir faragha itiba, gavgavim dagh an…®di, egha Israelian n…®ghn…®ziba fe, eght…® God me dan…®ngasa m…®kemezir nguazim dapiamin dughiam…®n, me deraghv…®ra Arazir kabar g…®n mangam.
\ip Bizir ekiar ak…®nafarir kam damuasa m…®geim, a Israelian akuraght…®, me God…®n Akar Gavgaviba deraghv…®ram dar g…®n mangam. God…®n Arazir kam, a sapta 6:4-6…®n ikia kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa uan navir averiam ko uan n…®ghn…®zim ko uan gavgavim sara bar Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, a gifongegh.‚Äù Moses Akar Gavgavir kam gavgavim a dan…®ngasa, tintinibar m…®ghs…®abar mavanang egha asebar ziaba fan men anogoroke. Me God g…®fozir puvat…®zir arazibar amuan mark…®. Egh me danganir vam…®rara am…®sefegh, egh gumazamiziba bar an mang…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam f…®.
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam God Israelia ko amizir Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam…®n men n…®ghn…®ziba fe. God uab…® Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam…®n g…®n ghua iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, eght…® me uaghan deraghv…®ra n…®ghnigh me Kenan…®n nguazim ikiamim…®n dughiam…®n, me Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam…®n g…®n mang…®s…® bar gavgafigh.
\c 1
\ms1 Israelia Sainain M…®ghs…®am ategha izezir eghaghanim, Moses a geghari
\mr (Sapta 1--3)
\p 
\v 1 Ak…®nafarir kam…®n aven itir akaba, Moses da Israelian gumazamizibav keme. Dughiar kam…®n, me gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim aghuigha an iti. Kar Jordan…®n Fanem…®n borogh…®n aruem anadi nagh…®n itir danganim. Danganir zarir me itir kam, Sup…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®n ikia, egha bar m…®s…®ngi. Ez…® Paran…®n nguibam, vong…®n amadaghan iti, ez…® Tofel…®n nguibam, ko Laban…®n nguibam, ko Haserot…®n nguibam, ko Disahap…®n nguibam, da vong…®n amadaghan itima, Israelia dar tong…®n iti.
\v 2 Gumazitam ti Sainain M…®ghs…®am…®n ikegh Kades Barnea mang…®s…® 11plan aruebar Idom…®n kantrin m…®ghs…®aba atugh mangam.
\v 3 Ez…® Israelia fom…®ra Isip…®n kantri ategha iza 40plan azeniba danganir kam…®n arui. Dughiar kam, namba 40…®n azenim, an namba 11…®n iak…®nim…®n, an dughiar faragha zuim otoz…®, Moses Ikiav…®ra Itir God a m…®kemezir bizibar gun me m…®gei.
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt D…®boboniba 21:21-35\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Amorian Atrivim, Sihon, ab…®razir dughiam…®n g…®n, bizir kaba otifi. Atrivim Sihon Hesbon…®n nguibar ekiam gativagha an gari. Ez…® uaghan Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Basan…®n danganim…®n Atrivim Ok aneb…®ra. Ok, a Astarot…®n nguibam ko Edrein nguibam gativagha aning…®n gari.
\v 5 Dughiar kam…®n Israelia Jordan…®n Fanem…®n, aruem anadi nagh…®n, Moapian nguazim…®n itima, Moses Akar Gavgavir kabar gumazamizibav g…®a men sure gamua ghaze:
\p 
\v 6 ‚ÄúE Sainain M…®ghs…®am…®n itir dughiam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, kamagh…®n e m…®g…®a ghaze:
\p ‚Äú ‚ÄòIa dughiar bar ruarim…®n m…®ghs…®ar kam…®n borogh…®n iti. Ian dughiar kagh itim, a iza kamagh…®ra tu.
\v 7 Ia d…®kavigh danganir kam ategh, egh Amorian m…®ghs…®aba itir danganim, ko an borogh…®n itir danganibar mang…®. Kar Jordan…®n danganir zarim ko m…®ghs…®aba itir danganiba, ko saut…®n amadaghan itir nguazir m…®s…®ngiziba, ko Mediterenian…®n Ongarir Ekiam…®n dadarim…®n itir nguaziba. Egh ia Kenanian nguazim ko nguazir Lebanon…®n M…®ghs…®abar vong…®n itiba sara inigh mang…® Yufretis…®n Faner Ekiam…®n tugh.
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Jenesis 26:3; Ua Me Ini 33:1; D…®boboniba 14:23; 32:11\x*Ia oragh! Nguazir kaba bar, k…® ia gan…®di. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ian inazir afeziaba, Abraham, Aisak, ko Jekop, ko men ovavir borir g…®n otivamiba, nguazir kaba is…® me dan…®ngasa me koma akam ak…®righa g…®fa. Eght…® ia dat…®r…®gh…®n d…®kavigh mang…® da inigh dar apiagh ik…®.‚Äô ‚Äù
\s1 Moses gumazir dapaniba am…®sevez…® me Israelian jasbar m…®n iti
\r (Ua Me Ini 18:13-27)
\p 
\v 9 Egha Moses gumazamizibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® faragha kamagh…®n ia m…®keme, ‚ÄòK…® ia gativagh ian ganamin ingangarim, a bar ekefe. K…® uab…®ram a damuva avegham.
\v 10 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ia gamiz…®, ia borir av…®riba bategha, bar av…®rasemegha iti. Ian d…®bobonim, overiam…®n itir m…®kovezibar d…®bobonim…®n m…®n ghu.
\v 11 Nan ifongiam kamak…®n. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a en inazir afeziabar God, a uan akar d…®k…®r…®zim…®n g…®n mang…®, ia damight…® ia guizbang…®ra bar av…®rasemegh…®va ian g…®n otivamin d…®bobonim, ian d…®bobonir dat…®r…®gh…®n itim bar a gafiragham. Eght…® a uaghan ian bizibar amut…®, da bar deragh otivam.
\v 12 Eght…® k…® manmagh…®ra uab…®ra ian os…®mt…®ziba ko ian akamadariba ak…®ram? K…® uab…®ra dar amuan iburagham.
\v 13 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia fofozir gumazir aghuitaba ko, gumazir derav…®ra n…®ghn…®gha biziba tuis…®zitaba, me ian gumazir dapanibar ik…®s…® me am…®sefegh. Ia uan anababar tong…®n vaghvagh me am…®seveght…®, k…® me ginabaght…® me ia gativagh ian ganam.‚Äô
\v 14 K…® kamagh…®n ia m…®kemez…®, ia na ikaragha ghaze, ia kamagh…®n damuasa ifonge.
\v 15 Kamagh…®n, ia uari uan anababar tong…®n vaghvagha m…®sevezir fofozir gumaziba ko, gumazir dapanir aghuir gumazamiziba derav…®ra me g…®foziba, k…® me ini. K…® me am…®sevez…®, men marazi 1,000plan gumazamizibar garima, marazi 100plan garima, marazi 50plan garima, marazi 10plan gari. Ez…® k…® uaghan gumazir ekiar maba bar ian anababar tong…®n vaghvagha me am…®sefe.
\p 
\v 16 ‚ÄúEgha dughiar kam…®n k…® ian jas…®n kaba akar gavgavim me gan…®ga ghaze, ‚ÄòIa gumazamizibar akamadarir men tong…®n otiviba baraghamin dughiam…®n, ia deraghav…®ra kuariba arigh da baragh. Egh akamadariba bar deraghv…®ra da tuis…®gh. Kar ti, ian namakar pumuning…®n tong…®n itir akamadariba, o akamadarir ian namakaba ko ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizir ian tong…®n itiba, ia uaghara derav…®ra da baragh guiz…®n arazim…®n g…®n mang…® da tuis…®gh.
\v 17 K…® kamagh…®n me m…®keme: Gumazim a ziam iti o ziam puvat…®, ia arazir vam…®ran g…®n mang…® bar men araziba tuis…®gh. God uab…® kot…®n dughiam…®n n…®ghn…®ziba ia dan…®ngam, eght…® ia gumazitam…®n atiatingan mark…®. Eght…® os…®mt…®zim bar ekeveght…®, ia anek…®ran iburagh…®va, a inigh na bagh iz…®t…®, k…® a baragham.‚Äô
\v 18 Egha dughiar kam…®n bizir igharazir ia uaghan damuamiba sara k…® ian sure gami.‚Äù
\s1 Israelia moga gari gumaziba amangi
\r (D…®boboniba 13:1-13)
\p 
\v 19 Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, en God, e damuasa m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, e ami. E dughiar kam…®n d…®kavigha Sainain M…®ghs…®am ategha ghua danganir bar kuram…®n zui, kar gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim. E ghuav…®ra ikia Amorian m…®ghs…®aba itir danganim…®n otivigha Kades Barnean otifi.
\v 20 Ez…® k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòE dat…®r…®gh…®n Amorian m…®ghs…®aba itir danganim…®n otifi. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, nguazir kam dat…®r…®gh…®n ia dan…®ngasava ami.
\v 21 Ia gan! Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God nguazir kam isa ia ganigha g…®fa. Ia d…®kavigh mang…® a inigh, mati Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian inazir afeziabar God, a ia m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra, ia a dapiagh. Egh atiating…®va okam n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®.‚Äô
\p 
\v 22 ‚ÄúEz…® ia bar mogh…®ram iza na m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòE gumazitaba amangight…® me en faragh mang…®, mongegh nguazir kam…®n ganigham. Egh me tuavir bar aghuitam en akaght…® e an mangam. Me e m…®k…®m suam nguibar ekiar kaba, da manmagh…®ra gari.‚Äô
\p 
\v 23 ‚ÄúEz…® k…® oregha ghaze, e akar kam…®n g…®n mang…®t…® a ti deragham. Egha uan 12plan anababar aven, k…® vaghvagha dar aven gumazir maba am…®sefe, eght…® 12plan gumaziba mangam.
\v 24 Egha me d…®kavigha m…®ghs…®aba itir danganim…®n p…®n ghua, Eskol…®n Danganir Zarim…®n otivigha moga garagha rui.
\v 25 Egha me dagher nguazir kam…®n otivir maba inigha ua iza e ganigha ghaze, ‚ÄòNguazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, dat…®r…®gh…®n e gan…®dir kam, a bar dera.‚Äô
\p 
\v 26 \x - \xo 1:26 \xt God…®n Araziba 9:23; Hibru 3:16\x*‚ÄúMe kamagh…®n m…®kemez…®, ia ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n akaba batuegha kantrin kam…®n ghuavanangan aghua.
\v 27 Ia uan purirpenibar ikia uarir tong…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®ribagh amua uarigh imoba ghaze, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God e gifongezir puvat…®. Egha kamagh…®n an e is…® Amorian dafarim dat…®ght…® me e gas…®ghas…®ghasa, a Isip…®n kantrin e inigha azenan ize.
\v 28 E tizim bagh danganir kam…®n mangam? Gumazir e nguazir kam…®n mong…®va an ganasa amangiziba, ua izegha kamagh…®n e m…®g…®a ghaze, Gumazamizir nguazir kam…®n itiba bar gavgavigha agharapaniba bar ruari, ez…® men d…®bobonim, en d…®bobonim bar a gafira. Ez…® me itir nguibar ekiaba, da av…®nizir d…®vaziba bar overiam…®n ghuavanabogha bar is…®n mar iti. E uaghan men garima, gumazir dafabara men tong…®n iti. Me ti gumazir bar ruarir fom…®ra itim Anak, an ovavir boribara!‚Äô
\p 
\v 29 ‚ÄúEz…® k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®gei, ‚ÄòIa gumazamizir kabar atiatingan mark…®.
\v 30 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, a fom…®ra Isip…®n kantrin aven ian akuraz…® ia ganiz…® mogh…®n, a dat…®r…®gh…®n ian faragh mang…® ia bagh apanibav sogham.
\v 31 \x - \xo 1:31 \xt Aposel 13:18\x*Ia faragha gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, a ian akuragha ia inigha ia atera izav…®ra ikia nguazir ia dat…®r…®gh…®n itir kam…®n oto. Ez…® an arazir kam, ia an ganigha g…®fa. A mati afeziam uan borim ghurafaz…® mogh…®n, ia gami.‚Äô
\v 32 \x - \xo 1:32 \xt Hibru 3:19\x*K…® kamagh…®n ia m…®geima, ia akar kam barazir puvat…®gha, n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n itir puvat…®.
\v 33 A ian faragha ghua tuavim ian akagha danganir ia purirpeniba asamim ian aka. Egha a d…®magaribar, avivzariar ekiam…®n aven ian faragha ghua, aruebar mati, ghuariar ruarir ekiam…®n m…®n ia gis…®n faragha zui.‚Äù
\s1 God ivezir kuram Israelia gan…®ngi
\r (D…®boboniba 14:20-45)
\p 
\v 34 \x - \xo 1:34-35 \xt Hibru 3:18\x*Egha Moses me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®ribagh amima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ia baragha ghua ian an…®ngaghegha bar pamtem…®n m…®g…®a ghaze,
\v 35 ‚ÄòIa gumazamizir bar kuraba, ian tav nguazir aghuir k…® ian inazir afeziabar an…®ngasa me koma akam ak…®rizim…®n mangan kogham. Bar puvat…®gham.
\v 36 K…® garima, Jefunen otarim, Kalep, a bar na baghav…®ra ikia nan g…®n zui. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a uab…®ra mang…® nguazir kam…®n ikiam. Eght…® nguazir a ghua ganizir kam, k…® a is…® a ko, an ovavir boribar an…®ngam.‚Äô
\p 
\v 37 ‚ÄúIan arazir kam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God gamima, a uaghan bar na basemegha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòMoses, n…® uakan, n…® nguazir kam…®n aven mangan kogham.
\v 38 Eght…® n…®n akurvazir gumazim Josua, a Nun…®n otarim, a uab…®ra mangam. N…® gavgavim is…® Josuan n…®ghn…®zim danight…®, a Israelia inigh men faragh mang…® nguazir kam inigh a dapiam.‚Äô
\p 
\v 39 ‚ÄúEgha g…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kamagh…®n bar e m…®gei, ‚ÄòIan borir agh…®rir dat…®r…®gh…®n itiba kamagh…®n fozir puvat…®, bizir tizim a ikufi, ez…® bizir tizim a dera, merara nguazir kam…®n aven mangam. Borir kabara, ia me m…®g…®a ghaze, Apaniba me m…®sueght…® me ar…®ghiregham. Eght…® k…® nguazir kam me danight…®, me a inigh a dapiagh an ikiam.
\v 40 Ez…® ia gumazamizir aruaba, ia dat…®r…®gh…®n uamategh gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n mang…®. Egh Ongarir Aghevim bagha zuir tuavim…®n mang…®.‚Äô
\p 
\v 41 ‚ÄúEgha ia na m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòMoses, e Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kuram gami. Egh e dat…®r…®gh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God e m…®kemez…® mogh…®n mang…® m…®sogham.‚Äô Egha ia ghaze, M…®ghs…®aba itir danganim…®n itir gumaziba, da pura biziba. E me d…®kab…®namin gavgavim iti. Egha ia vaghvagh m…®dorozim…®n biziba suigha me d…®kab…®nasava ami.
\p 
\v 42 \x - \xo 1:42 \xt D…®boboniba 14:41-43\x*‚ÄúEz…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® ikiangs…®zir kam me dan…®ng: Me m…®dorozim bagh mangan mark…®. K…® me ko mang…® men akuraghan koght…®, apaniba bar me ab…®nigham.‚Äô
\v 43 Ez…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akar kam…®n gun ia m…®gei. Ez…® ia an akam barazir puvat…®. Ia an akam batuegha, uari fa ifaghata d…®kavigha apanibav soghasa m…®ghs…®aba itir danganim…®n ghue.
\p 
\v 44 ‚ÄúEz…® Amorian m…®ghs…®aba itir danganir kam…®n itiba, aparir ivibar m…®n okoruabar m…®n m…®gha iza ian ag…®nt…®gha ghua Idomian m…®ghs…®aba itir danganim…®n ghua, Horman…®n nguibar ekiam…®n otogha bar ia d…®kab…®ra.
\v 45 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia uarir akurvaghasa Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n diava arai. Ez…® a tong ia baraghizir pu. Bar puvat…®.
\v 46 Ez…® bizir kam bang…®n ia dughiar bar ruarim…®n Kades…®n ike.‚Äù
\c 2
\s1 Israelia ghua Idom…®n kantri ko // Moap…®n kantrin oto
\r (D…®boboniba 21:10-20)
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt D…®boboniba 21:4\x*Egha Moses kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúE g…®n uamategha ghua gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ghua Ongarir Aghevim bagha zuir tuavim…®n zui. Egha e, Ikiav…®ra Itir God e m…®kemez…® mogh…®rama ami. Egha e Idomian m…®ghs…®abar itir danganim…®n, dughiar bar ruarim…®n ighuagh arui.
\p 
\v 2 ‚ÄúEgha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ua na m…®g…®a ghaze,
\v 3 ‚ÄòDughiar bar ruarim…®n ia pura m…®ghs…®aba itir danganir kam tintinibar a garuavti, dughiam g…®fa. Ia dat…®r…®gh…®n not…®n amadaghan mang…®.‚Äô
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Jenesis 36:8\x*Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevir kam ia dan…®ngasa na m…®keme, ‚ÄòIa dat…®r…®gh…®n Idomian m…®ghs…®aba itir danganim…®n torim abigh mangam. Kar Ison ovavir boribar nguazim, me ian namakaba. Me ian atiatingt…®, ia deraghv…®ra ganigh.
\v 5 Ia me ko m…®soghan mark…®. K…® men nguazir otevitam is…® ia danighan kogham. Bar puvat…®. K…® fom…®ra Seir…®n M…®ghs…®am isa Ison ovavir boribagh anigha g…®fa.
\v 6 Eght…® ia men kantrin aven, dagheba ko d…®pabara, ia dagh ives.‚Äô
\p 
\v 7 ‚ÄúIa bizir kam bak…®n…®ghnighan mark…®. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ia bagha biziba bar dagh amiz…®, da deraghv…®ram otifi. Ia gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim purama a garuir dughiam…®n, a bar deraghav…®ra ia geghuva ian gari. Egha faragha zuir 40plan azenibar ikegha iza dat…®r…®k…®n, a ia ko ikiav…®ra iti, ez…® ia bizitam…®n otevezir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 8 ‚ÄúEz…® e ua d…®kavigha ghua en namakar Seir…®n M…®ghs…®abar borogh…®n itiba, Idomia, me gitaghasa, Elat ko Esiongeber…®n nguibamning bagha zuir tuavir gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n itim ategha, ragha ghua Moap…®n kantrin itir gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n zuir tuavim…®n zui.
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt Jenesis 19:37\x*Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòMoapia me Lot…®n ovavir boriba, ez…® ia paz…® me damuan mark…®. K…® nguibar ekiam Ar isa me ganigha g…®fa, ez…® ia me ko m…®soghan mark…®. K…® men nguazitam is…® ia danighan kogham.‚Äô ‚Äù
\p 
\v 10-11 (Ikiav…®ra Itir God t…®ghar nguazir kam is…® Moapia dan…®ngamin dughiam…®n, gumazamiziba gumazamizir bar gavgavir kaba d…®bora ghaze, ‚ÄúEmia.‚Äù Me fom…®ra nguibar ekiar kam Ar, me an iti. Me Anakian m…®n agharir suiar ruaribar aghungi. Gumazamizir av…®riba, gumazir agharir ruaribar aghungizir kaba, Anakia ko Emia, me ziar kam Refaim me gat…®. Ez…® Refaimian marazi, Moap…®n kantrin itima, Moapia ziar kam Emia, me gat…®.
\v 12 Horia fom…®ra Idom…®n kantrin itima, Ison ovavir boriba me gas…®ghasigha, men kantri inigha a gapia. Kamagh…®ra, Israelia g…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God me gan…®ngizir nguazir kam, inigha a gapia.)
\p 
\v 13 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God e m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra e g…®n Seret…®n Danganir Zarim ab…®gha zui.
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt D…®boboniba 14:28-35\x*Dughiar e Kades Barnean ikegha iza Seret…®n Danganir Zarim abigha izezim, dat…®r…®gh…®n 38plan azeniba. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra, m…®dorozir gumazir e ko Kades Barnean ikegha izeziba, me bar mogh…®ram ariaghire.
\v 15 Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, men apanim gamua ghua bar me ag…®fa.
\p 
\v 16 ‚ÄúM…®dorozir gumaziba bar ariaghirez…® men g…®n,
\v 17 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kamagh…®n na m…®g…®a ghaze,
\v 18 ‚ÄòIa dat…®r…®gh…®n nguibar ekiam Ar, an borogh…®n zuir tuavim…®n otogh Moapian nguazim…®n m…®taghniam abigh an aven mang…®.
\v 19 \x - \xo 2:19 \xt Jenesis 19:38\x*Egh Amonia me Lot…®n ovavir boriba, ia men nguazim…®n borogh…®ra mangam. Nguazir kam k…® a isa me ganigha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® men nguazir katam is…® ia danighan kogham. Eght…® ia bizitam damight…® me atart…® ia me m…®soghan mark…®.‚Äô ‚Äù
\p 
\v 20 (Nguazir as…®zir kam, me uaghan kamagh…®n a d…®bori, ‚ÄúRefaimian nguazim.‚Äù Gumazamizir maba fom…®ram an ike, ez…® Amonia kamagh…®n uaghan me d…®bora ghaze, me ‚ÄúSamsumia.‚Äù
\v 21 Egha me uaghan Anakian m…®n aghuigha ruari. Egha me bar av…®rasemegha gavgaviba men iti. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, bar mogh…®ra me ag…®vaz…®, Amonia nguazir kam inigha a gapia.
\v 22 Kamagh…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Ison adarazigh amiz…®, me dat…®r…®gh…®n Idom…®n M…®ghs…®abagh apiagha iti. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, bar Horia ag…®vaz…®, Idomia men nguazim inigha a gapia.
\v 23 Ez…® Avia, men nguazim ongarir ekiam…®n ikegha ghua Gasan amadaghan saut…®n tu. Ez…® Kritia kamagh…®rama amigha Avian nguazim inigha a gapia.)
\p 
\v 24 Ez…® Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúE Moap gitagha izima Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòIa dat…®r…®gh…®n mang…® Arnon…®n Fanem giregh mang…®. Eght…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Amorian gumazim Sihon, a Hesbon…®n atrivim, k…® a ko an nguazim is…® ian dafarim dar…®gham.
\v 25 K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ikegh mang…® k…® nguibabar gumazamizibar amight…® me bar ian atiatigham. Egh me ian ziam baragh…®va, egh akong bar atiatigham.‚Äô ‚Äù
\s1 Israelia Atrivim Sihon d…®kab…®ra
\r (D…®boboniba 21:21-30)
\p 
\v 26 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúE Kedemot…®n gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n itir dughiam…®n, k…® Hesbon…®n Atrivim Sihon, bagha navir vam…®ran ikiasa akar aghuiba isa abuir gumazir mabagh anigha me amangi.
\v 27 Me ghua otivigha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® en amamangat…®ght…®, e n…®n nguazim abigh tuavimra mangam. En gumazamiziba ragh…®regh agharir guvim o agharir k…®riam…®n mangan kogham. E bigh…®rat…®gh mangam.
\v 28 Guizbang…®ra, e pura dagheba ko d…®paba inian kogham. Bar puvat…®. E dagh ivezam. E pura uan suebar, n…®n nguazim…®n tizimra daru,
\v 29 mang…® Jordan…®n Fanem gir…®gh anebigh nguazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, e dan…®ngasa m…®kemezim…®n otogham. N…® ti oraki, Ison ovavir borir Seir…®n M…®ghs…®abar itiba, ko Moapian gumazir Ar…®n itiba, me kamagh…®ra bar en amamangat…®z…®, e men nguazim abigha ize.‚Äô
\p 
\v 30 ‚ÄúEz…® Atrivim Sihon uan kantri abigh mangan en amamangat…®zir puvat…®. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, e dat…®r…®gh…®n apiaghav itir nguazir kam e a iniasa an Atrivim Sihon gamiz…®, an navim gavgaviz…®, a en akam baraghan aghua.
\p 
\v 31 ‚ÄúEz…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, na m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® oragh! K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Atrivim Sihon ko an nguaziba bar da is…® ian dafarim dar…®gham. Ia pura mang…® da inigh, egh dar apiagh.‚Äô
\v 32 Ez…® Sihon uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, e m…®soghasa Jahas…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®n otifi.
\v 33 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God a isa e gan…®ngiz…® e a d…®kab…®ragha, a ko an otariba ko an adarazi sara bar me m…®soghez…® me bar ariaghire.
\v 34 Ez…® dughiar kamra, e an nguibaba bar da inigha, bar adagh as…®ghas…®ki. Egha men gumaziba ko, amiziba ko boriba sara m…®soghez…® me ariaghirez…®, tav ua itir puvat…®.
\v 35 Ez…® e uari bagha men bulmakauba ko men bizir nguibabar aven itiba bar da ini.
\v 36 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, en amamangat…®z…®, e Arnon…®n Danganir Zarim…®n m…®riam…®n aven itir nguibam Aroer…®n ikegha ghua Gileat…®n nguazim…®n otivigha men nguibar kaba bar dagh as…®ghas…®ki. E zuima, nguibar kaba av…®nizir d…®vazir tam e gamiz…®, e aven mangasa iburazir puvat…®.
\v 37 Dughiar kam…®n, e Amonian nguazim, ko Jabok…®n Fanem…®n borogh…®n itir danganiba, ko m…®ghs…®aba itir danganibar aven itir nguibaba, ko danganir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, e mangasa en anogorogheziba, e dar borogh…®n ghuzir puvat…®.‚Äù
\c 3
\s1 Israelia Atrivim Ok ab…®ra
\r (D…®boboniba 21:31-35)
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt D…®boboniba 21:33-35\x*Egha Moses ua Israelia m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúKantri Basan a not…®n amadaghan iti, ez…® e dat…®r…®gh…®n an zuir tuavim…®n zuima, Basan…®n Atrivim Ok uan adarazi ko otivigha e m…®soghasa izi. Me Edrein nguibam…®n borogh…®n kamagh…®n ami.
\v 2 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, na m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® an atiatingan mark…®. A ko an gumazamiziba ko, an nguazim, k…® bar da isa ia ganigha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia d…®kavigh, arazir ia faragha Amorian Atrivim Sihon gamizim, ia a damu. Sihon, a faragha Hesbon gativagha an gari.‚Äô
\p 
\v 3 ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, Atrivim Ok ko an gumazamiziba en dafarim gat…®z…®, e me m…®soaghar…®ghiz…® me bar ariaghire. Men tav ua itir puvat…®.
\v 4 E dughiar kam…®n an nguibaba bar ada inigha, tam ataghiz…® a itir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®. Atrivim Ok, Basan…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ikia, egha Argop…®n danganim gatifa. Dughiar kam, e Argop…®n danganim…®n itir nguibar ekiar 60pla, e bar mogh…®ra ada ini.
\v 5 Nguibar ekiar kaba, da av…®nizir d…®vaziba, da bar ekevegha m…®temegha gavgafi. Ez…® d…®vazibar tiar akaba bar gavgaviz…®, me ain…®n igugunibar da ap…®ri. Ez…® nguibar dozir d…®vaziba puvat…®zir bar av…®riba, da Atrivim Ok…®n nguazir as…®zibar iti.
\v 6 E nguibaba bar dagh as…®ghasigha, gumazamiziba ko boriba, bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Arazir e Hesbon…®n Atrivim Sihon, gamizimra, e me gami.
\v 7 Egha men bulmakauba ko, nguibabar biziba bar, e uari bagha da ini.
\p 
\v 8 ‚ÄúE dughiar kam…®n, arazir kamra, e Amorian Atrivir kamning, Sihon ko Ok, e aning…®n nguaziba bar da ini. Nguazir kaba, da Jordan…®n Fanem…®n aruem anadi nagh…®n iti. Da saut…®n amadaghan Arnon…®n Fanem…®n ikegha ghua not…®n amadaghan Hermon…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n tu.
\v 9 Ez…® Saidonia, Hermon…®n M…®ghs…®am ziar kam a gar…®si, ‚ÄòSirion.‚Äô Ez…® Amoria, ziar kam a gar…®gha ghaze, ‚ÄòSenir.‚Äô
\v 10 E m…®ghs…®abar orazibar itir danganir zaribar itir nguibaba bar ada isava, Gileat…®n nguaziba ko Basan…®n nguaziba isa ghua Saleka ko Edrein nguibamning…®n tu. Nguibar kaba, da bar Atrivim Ok…®n nguazim…®n itima e bar mogh…®ram ada ini.‚Äù
\p 
\v 11 (Atrivim Ok, a Refaimbar atrivir abuananam. An aremeght…® an eghuamin boksiam, me dag…®am…®n an ingari. Boksiar kam…®n ruarim, a 4 mitan tuz…®, an arozim, 2 mitan tu. Dag…®ar boksiar kam, an Amon kantrin Raban nguibam…®n ikiav…®ra iti.)\f + \fr 3:11 \ft Hibrun akam vez…®n kam deragha a m…®geir puvat…®. Gumazir maba kamagh…®n akam giragha an osiri, ‚ÄúAn dakozim, me ain…®n an ingari. Dakozir kam…®n ruarim, a 4 mitan ghu.‚Äù Ez…® vez…®n kam…®n akar abuananam, akar kam, ‚Äúboksiar kam ikiav…®ra ikia iti,‚Äù a dughiar e dat…®r…®gh…®n itim m…®geir puvat…®. A dughiar Moses ak…®nafarim kam osirizim m…®gei.\f*
\s1 Ruben Ko Gat…®n anabamning…®n adarasi, Jordan…®n Fanem…®n // aruem anadi nagh…®n apia
\r (D…®boboniba 32:1-14)
\p 
\v 12 Moses kamagh…®n Israelia m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúE nguibar kaba inigha g…®vagha, k…® nguazir kabar maba Ruben ko Gat…®n anabamning…®n adarazigh an…®ngi. Men nguazim, Arnon…®n Fanem…®n borogh…®n itir nguibam Aroer, a nguazir not…®n amadaghan itim. Egha uaghan k…® Gileat…®n itir m…®ghs…®aba itir danganim…®n nguazir akuar mam ko an nguibaba me gan…®ngi.
\v 13 Egha k…® Gileat…®n nguazir akuar igharazim ko Basan…®n nguazim bar a isa Manasen anabar me tuirazimning…®n mam gan…®ngi. Atrivim Ok faragha Basan…®n nguazim gativagha an gari. Danganir kam, me ziam Argop a gar…®si. An aven itir nguibaba, k…® bar da isa Manasen adarazigh an…®ngi. Me fom…®ra Basan m…®g…®a ghaze, a Refaimian nguazim.
\p 
\v 14 ‚ÄúEz…® Jair, a Manasen adarazir gumazir mam. A g…®n Argop…®n danganim bar mogh…®ram a ini, nguazir kam me ziam Basan a gar…®si. Nguazir kam ghua Gesur ko Makan nguazim…®n m…®taghniam…®n tu. A uab…® uan ziam nguibar kabagh ar…®ki. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazamiziba nguibar kabav g…®av…®ra ikia iza dat…®r…®gh…®n ghaze, kar Jair…®n nguibaba.
\p 
\v 15 ‚ÄúMakiria, me Manasen anabam…®n marasi, ez…® Gileat…®n nguazim, k…® a isa me gan…®ngi.
\v 16 Ez…® Ruben ko Gat…®n anabamning…®n adarasi, k…® Gileat…®n ikegha ghua Arnon…®n Fanem…®n tuzir nguazim isa me gan…®ngi. Men m…®taghniam saut…®n ikegha ghua Arnon…®n Faner torimra tu. Ez…® men nguazir aruem anadi nagh…®n itim…®n m…®taghniam ghua Jabok…®n Fanem…®n tu. Ez…® Jabok…®n Fanem, an Amon…®n kantrin m…®taghniam.
\v 17 Ez…® men m…®taghniar aruem uaghiri nagh…®n itim, a Jordan…®n Fanem…®n tu. Men m…®taghniam not…®n amadaghan Galilin D…®par Akarem…®n ikegha ghua, Amangs…®zim Itir D…®pam…®n saut…®n amadaghan tu. Kar Amangs…®zim Itir D…®par Akarer aruem anadi nagh…®n, Pisgan M…®ghs…®am…®n borogh…®n itir nguazim.
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 3:18-20 \xt Josua 1:12-15\x*‚ÄúEgha k…® dughiar kamra, kamagh…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God, en God, Jordan…®n Fanem…®n itir nguazir aruem anadi nagh…®n itim isa ia gan…®ngi, eght…® ia a dapiam. Dat…®r…®gh…®n ian m…®dorozir gumaziba uan m…®dorozir biziba inigh. Eght…® ia me amadaght…®, me uan Israelian namakabar faragh Jordan…®n Fanem giregh anebigh mang…®, men akuraght…® me nguaziba iniam.
\v 19 Eght…® ian amuiba ko boriba nguibar ekiar k…® ia gan…®ngizim…®n ia m…®zuam ik…®. K…® fo ian bulmakauba ko sipsipba bar av…®raseme, da uaghan ian nguibar ekiam…®n ia m…®zuam ik…®.
\v 20 Ia mang…® uan namakabar akurvagh mang…®t…®, dughiar me nguazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God me dan…®ngasa m…®kemezim iniamim otogham. Kar, aruem uaghiri nagh…®n amadaghan Jordan…®n Fanem…®n itir nguazim. Ia me atagh…®raghan mark…®, egh me ko ik…® mang…® dughiar Ikiav…®ra Itir God me damut…®, me derav…®rama uan nguazim dapiagh an avughsam, mati ia uan nguazim…®n apiaz…® mok…®n. Egh ia g…®n, uamategh uan nguazir k…® ia gan…®ngizim…®n mang…®.‚Äô
\p 
\v 21 ‚ÄúEgha k…® g…®n kamagh…®n Josua m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God en God, Atrivim Ok ko Atrivim Sihon gamizir biziba n…® dar ganigha g…®fa. God kamagh…®ra atrivir igharazir ia m…®sogh men nguaziba inamibar amuam.
\v 22 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, a uab…® ia bagh me ko m…®sogh…®va ian akurvagham. Kamagh…®n, ia men atiatingan mark…®.‚Äô ‚Äù
\s1 God, kantri Kenan…®n mangasa Moses…®n amamangat…®zir puvat…®
\p 
\v 23 \x - \xo 3:23-27 \xt D…®boboniba 27:12-14; God…®n Araziba 32:48-52\x*Egha Moses kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúDughiar kam…®n k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, pamten a ko m…®g…®a ghaze,
\v 24 ‚ÄòO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, nan Ekiam, k…® fo, n…® bizir ekiar n…® damuamiba, n…® dar otevir muziariba nan akakasi, k…® n…®n ingangarir gumazim. Ua god…®n igharazitam overiam ko nguazim…®n itir puvat…®, egh a bizir ekiar n…® amigha g…®vazir kabar amuan kogham.
\v 25 K…® n…®n azai, n…® nan amamangat…®ght…®, k…® mang…® Jordan…®n Fanem gir…®gh vong…®n mang…®, egh nguazir aghuir kam…®n gan…®va m…®ghs…®aba itir danganir aghuibar gan…®va, uaghan Lebanon…®n itir m…®ghs…®am…®n ganam.‚Äô
\p 
\v 26 ‚ÄúEz…® puvat…®. Ian os…®mt…®zim bang…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, nan atara egha uan kuarim dukuagha ikia ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® uan akam dukuagh, egh bizir kam bagh nan azangan mark…®.
\v 27 N…® mang…® Pisgan M…®ghs…®am bar an ghuam…®n ghuavanabogh, vong…®n not…®n amadaghan gan…®va, saut amadaghan gan…®va, aruem anadi nagh…®n gan…®va, aruem ghuaghiri nagh…®n gan. N…® Jordan…®n Fanem abigh vong…®n mang…®gh nguazir kam…®n mang…®ghan kogham. Bar puvat…®gham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® deraghv…®ra danganir kabar gan.
\v 28 Josua uab…® gumazamiziba inigh fanem abigh vong…®n mangam, eght…® me nguazir n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n garir kam inigh a dapiam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® bar deraghv…®ra Josuan sure damu, egh gavgavim an n…®ghn…®zim dan…®ngigh.‚Äô
\p 
\v 29 ‚ÄúEz…® dughiar kam…®n e Betpeor…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®n danganir zarim…®n iti.‚Äù
\c 4
\ms1 Moses, Israelia m…®g…®a ghaze, // me God…®n Arazibar g…®n mang…®
\mr (Sapta 4--11)
\s1 Moses, God…®n Akar Gavgavibar g…®n mangasa Israelia m…®keme
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Moses kamagh…®n Israelia m…®gei, ‚ÄúO Israelia, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia gan…®dir arazir God ifongezir kaba ko bizir a damuasa ia m…®kemezir kaba, ia bar derav…®ra dar g…®n mang…®. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a ian inazir afeziabar God, a nguazir kam isa ia gan…®di. Ia nguazir kam…®n mang…® a dapiagh deraghv…®ra ikiasa a ifonge, kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia an arazibar suigh gavgavigh dar g…®n mang…®.
\v 2 \x - \xo 4:2 \xt Akar Mogomem 22:18-19\x*K…® ia gan…®dir Akar Gavgavir kaba, da guizbang…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God…®n Akar Gavgaviba, ez…® ia uam akar igharazitam dagh is…®n dar…®ghan mark…®. Egh ia an an…®ngizir akar otevitam anengaran mark…®. Ia Akar Gavgavir kaba bar dar g…®n mang…®.
\v 3 \x - \xo 4:3 \xt D…®boboniba 25:1-9\x*Ia uari Ikiav…®ra Itir God Peor…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n amizir bizir kam…®n ganigha g…®fa. Gumazamizir av…®rim danganir kam…®n ikia asem Bal…®n ziam fema, bizir kam bang…®n God ian tong…®n bar me gas…®ghas…®ki.
\v 4 Ez…® ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, an g…®n zuir adarazira, ia dat…®r…®gh…®n ikia kati.
\p 
\v 5 ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, nan God, na m…®kemezir arazir a ifongeziba ko bizir a damuasa ia m…®kemeziba, k…® dar ian sure gami. Ia dat…®r…®gh…®n mang…® nguazir kam inigh a dapiagh, egh bar dar g…®n mang…®.
\v 6 Ia bar guizbang…®ra adar g…®n mang…®t…®, ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamiziba kamagh…®n fogh suam, ia n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba ikia egha fofozir av…®riba iti. Ia nan arazir k…® ifongezir kabav k…®mt…®, gumazamiziba da baragh kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòGumazamizir ik…®zir gavgavir kam…®n itiba, me fofozim ikia egha bizibagh n…®ghn…®gha deragha dagh ami.‚Äô
\p 
\v 7 ‚ÄúIa ik…®zir igharazibagh n…®ghn…®gh, me purama ekevegha gavgafi, ez…® men asetam men borogh…®ra itir puvat…®. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, e an deir dughiabar, a bar en borogh…®ra ikia en akurvasi.
\v 8 K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ian sure gamizir arazir kaba, da arazir God ifongeziba ko bizir a damuasa e m…®kemeziba bar deragha vorogh…®ra zui. Ez…® ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamiziba, men araziba ko bizir me amiba, en Arazir aghuibar m…®n zuir puvat…®.
\v 9 Ia nguazir kam…®n itir dughiam, ia uari bagh deraghv…®ra gan, egh bizir ganigha g…®vaziba ia zurara dughiabar da bak…®n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®. Bar markiam. Ia dar uan boriba ko ovavir boribagh eghan mang…®v…®ra ik…®.
\v 10 Ia Sainain M…®ghs…®am…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n damazim…®n tuivigha ikezir dughiam g…®n…®ghn…®gh. Dughiar kam…®n a na m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® gumazamiziba bar men diaght…® me iz…® uari akufagh. Eght…® k…® uan akam…®n men sure damut…®, me nguazir kam…®n ikiamin dughiam…®n, me nan atiating nan apengara ikiam. Egh me uaghan uan boribar sure damut…®, me uaghan nan apengan ikiam.‚Äô
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 4:11-12 \xt Ua Me Ini 19:16-18; Hibru 12:18-19\x*‚ÄúGod m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®, ia m…®ghs…®am…®n borogh…®n ghuegha, an apengan zarim…®n tuivighav ikia gari, m…®ghs…®am isia avivzariaba b…®gha p…®n ghuavanaga overiam…®n suighasava amima, ghuariar bar p…®zim m…®ghs…®am avara.
\v 12 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God avir kam…®n aven ikia ia m…®geima, ia an akaba barasi. Egha ia gumazitam…®n nedazim…®n garir puvat…®gha pura m…®g…®r…®g…®ar k…®nim barasi.
\v 13 \x - \xo 4:13 \xt Ua Me Ini 31:18; 34:28; God…®n Araziba 9:10\x*A dughiar kam…®n uan Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavibar gun ia m…®kemegha dar g…®n mangasa ia m…®gei. Egha a dag…®ar akuar pumuning…®n Akar Gavgavir kaba osiri. Kar, an Akar Gavgavir 10pla.
\v 14 \x - \xo 4:14 \xt Ua Me Ini 21:1\x*Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uaghan arazir a ifongeziba ko bizir a damuasa ia m…®kemeziba, a ian sure damuasa Akar Gavgavim…®n na m…®keme. Ia nguazir dat…®r…®gh…®n iniamin kam, ia a dapiagh egh dar g…®n mang…®.‚Äù
\s1 Israelia asebar g…®n mangan kogham
\p 
\v 15 Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, Sainain M…®ghs…®am…®n avim…®n aven otogha m…®geir dughiam…®n, ia gumazitam…®n nedazim…®n garir puvat…®, ia pura tiarir k…®nim barasi. Kamagh…®n, ia deragh uari bagh gan…®va,
\v 16-18 \x - \xo 4:16-18 \xt Ua Me Ini 20:4; Ofa Gami 26:1; God…®n Araziba 5:8; 27:15; Rom 1:23\x*egh asetam…®n marvir guatam…®n ingaran mark…®. Ia kamagh…®n damigh…®va, arazir kuratam damigham. Ia marvir guar kaba ak…®ran mark…®, gumazim o amizim, as…®ziba, kuaraziba, kuruziba, osiriba, egh ia marvir guar kabar amight…® da ian godbar m…®n ikiam.
\v 19 Ia ti overiam…®n itir bizir kabar gari, aruem, iak…®nim ko m…®koveziba. Ia uari bagh ganigh, bizir kaba ian navir averiabagh ekut…®, ia teviba ap…®r dar ziaba fam. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ik…®zir igharazibar amamangat…®z…® me bizir kabar ziaba fe. Eght…® ia kamagh…®n damuan kogham.
\v 20 \x - \xo 4:20 \xt Ua Me Ini 19:5; God…®n Araziba 7:6; 14:2; 26:18; Taitus 2:14; 1 Pita 2:9\x*Ez…® ian Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Isip…®n kantrin ia inigha ian akua ize. Mati gumazim avir bar puv…®ra isim…®n aven uan borim iniz…® mogh…®n, kamagh…®ra a ia inigha izegha ia gamiz…®, ia an gumazamizibaram otifi, mati ia dat…®r…®gh…®n iti mok…®n.
\v 21 \x - \xo 4:21 \xt D…®boboniba 20:12\x*Ia bang…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a nan an…®ngaghe. Egha kamagh…®n a pamten na m…®g…®a ghaze, k…® Jordan…®n Fanem abigh mang…® nguazir aghuir kam…®n aven mangan kogham. Nguazir kam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God dat…®r…®gh…®n ia dan…®ngam.
\v 22 K…® Jordan…®n Fanem abigh vong…®n mang…®ghan kogham. Puvat…®gham. K…® danganir kamnagh…®ra ik…®va ovegham. Eght…® ia fanem gir…®gh vong…®n mang…® nguazir aghuir kam iniam.
\v 23 Ia deraghv…®ra uari bagh gan, egh Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God ia koma amizir kam bak…®n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®. Ia an akabar g…®n mang…® egh uari bagh asebar marvir guabar ingaran mark…®.
\v 24 \x - \xo 4:24 \xt Hibru 12:29\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, a uab…®ra guizbang…®ra God. A ian amamangat…®ght…®, ia asetam…®n ziam fan kogham. God avir bar puv…®ra isim…®n m…®n iti, egh uan apanibar atar men isigham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia kamagh…®n damuan mark…®.
\p 
\v 25 ‚ÄúEgh ia g…®n nguazir kam dughiar ruarim…®n an ik…®v…®ra ik…®, egh boriba bat…®t…® ian ovavir borir g…®n otivamiba, bizitabar nedazibar m…®n marvir guatabar ingaran mark…®. Ia kamagh…®n damu arazir kuram damigham. Arazir kam Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n damazim…®n derazir puvat…®, egha a gami a bar an…®ngaghe.
\v 26 Ia oragh, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n overiam ko nguazim…®n diaz…®, aning orazi k…® akar gavgavir kam…®n ia m…®gei. Ia God…®n akam batogh egh derav…®ra uari bagh gan. God bar zuam…®ra nguazir kam…®n ia batuegham. Ia Jordan…®n Fanem…®n vong…®n nguazir ia dat…®r…®gh…®n iniamin kam, ia dughiar ruarim…®n an ikeghan kogham. Puvat…®gham. Ia bar mogh…®rama ar…®m…®ghiregham.
\v 27 \x - \xo 4:27-28 \xt God…®n Araziba 28:36\x*Egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ia aghamsight…® ia tintinibar mang…® kantrin igharazibar ikiam, egh ian gumazamizir av…®rim ar…®m…®ghireght…® vabara ikiam.
\v 28 Egh ia kantrin kabar ik…® marvir guar gumaziba temeba ko dag…®abar ingarizibar ziaba fam. Nedazir kaba, bizibar garir puvat…®gha, biziba barazir puvat…®gha, apir puvat…®gha, bizibar mughuriaba barazir puvat…®.
\v 29 \x - \xo 4:29 \xt Jeremaia 29:13\x*Egh ia dughiar kam…®n ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God bagh iz…®s…® navim d…®kavam. Ia uan navir averiam ko duam…®n aven a buris…® bar gavgavigh, a batogh bar an borogh…®ra izam.
\v 30 Egh ia os…®mt…®zir ekiam ik…®t…®, bizir kurar kaba ia bativt…®, ia navibagh iragh uamategh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God bagh mang…® an akam…®n g…®n mangam.
\v 31 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, a God…®n apangkuvim itim. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a pura ia atagh…®ragh ia gas…®ghasighan kogham. Egh an Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir a uab…® ian inazir afeziaba ko amizir kam g…®n amadaghan kogham.
