\v 24 ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God, en God, uan gavgavir ekiam ko angazangarim en akagha avim…®n aven ikia e m…®gei. Ez…® e dat…®r…®gh…®n fo, dughiar mabar God gumazim ko m…®k…®mt…® an aremeghan kogham, an angam…®ra ik…®v…®ra ikiam.
\v 25 E bizir tizim bagh dat…®r…®gh…®n ovengam? Avir ekiar kam ti e gas…®ghasigham. E ti Ikiav…®ra Itir God baraght…® an e m…®k…®mt…®, e ar…®ghiregham.
\v 26 Nguazir kam…®n gumazitam ti Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n tiarim barazi an avim…®n aven ikia m…®kemez…®, an angam…®ra en m…®n ikiav…®ra ikez ti?
\v 27 E kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, Moses n…®rara ua rogh…®ra mang…®, egh akar Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, m…®k…®mamiba na da baregh ua iz…®v e m…®k…®m. Eght…® e da baregh dar g…®n mangam.‚Äô
\p 
\v 28 ‚ÄúEz…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian akar kaba baregha kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄòK…® gumazamizibar akaba barazi da dera.
\v 29 Nan ifongiam, me zurara n…®ghn…®zir kamra ik…® nan apengan ik…® zurara nan Akar Gavgavibar g…®n mang…®. Eght…® men ingangariba deraght…®, men ovavir boriba, zurara deraghv…®ra ikiam.
\v 30 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® mang…® me m…®k…®mt…®, me uamategh uan purirpenibar mang…®.
\v 31 Eght…® Moses, n…® kagh na ko ik…®t…®, k…® uan Akar Gavgaviba ko arazir k…® ifongeziba ko bizir k…® damuasa me m…®k…®mamiba is…®, n…® dan…®ngam. Eght…® n…® deraghv…®ra men sure damut…®, me nguazir k…® me dan…®ngamim…®n ik…®va deraghv…®ra dar g…®n mang…®.‚Äô ‚Äù
\p 
\v 32 Egha Moses Israelia m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, en God, e gan…®ngizir akaba ko arazir kaba, ia derav…®ra uari bagh gan…®va, egh dar g…®n mang…®. Ia ighuigh agharir guvim o agharir k…®riam…®n mangan mark…®.
\v 33 Ia tuavir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ian akazir kamra bar deraghv…®ra an g…®n mang…®t…®, bizir ia amiba bar deraghv…®ram otivam. Eght…® ia dughiar ruarim…®n nguazir ia dat…®r…®gh…®n iniamin kam…®n ikiam.‚Äù
\c 6
\s1 God…®n Akar Gavgavir bar ekiar faraghav…®ra zuim
\p 
\v 1 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, ian sure damuasa na m…®kemezir Akar Gavgaviba, arazir God ifongeziba ko bizir a damuasa ia m…®kemeziba. Ia mang…® nguazir ia dat…®r…®gh…®n iniamim dapiagh, egh akar kaba bar dar g…®n mang…®.
\v 2 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamaghsua ifonge, ia ko ian boriba ko men borir men g…®n otivamiba, ia angam…®ra itir dughiam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n atiating, arazir a ifongeziba ko an Akar Gavgavir a ia gan…®diba, ia dar g…®n mang…®v…®ra ik…®. Ia kamagh…®n damuva, ia dughiar ruarim…®n nguazir kam…®n ikiam.
\v 3 O Israelia, ia oragh! Ia deraghv…®ra ik…®s…®, ia akar kaba baregh, egh deraghv…®ra dar g…®n mang…®. Ia kamagh…®n damu, egh ia nguazir aghuim…®n ikiam, nguazir kam a bar dera, ez…® biziba bar an ikiava derav…®ram aghui. Egh ia bar av…®rasemegh bar gavgavight…®, ingangarir ia damuamiba, da deraghv…®ram otivam, mati Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian inazir afeziabar God, ia m…®kemez…® mok…®n.
\p 
\v 4-5 \x - \xo 6:4-5 \xt Matyu 22:37; Mak 12:29; 12:30; Luk 10:27\x*‚ÄúO Israelia, ia derav…®ram oragh. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a bar uab…®ra en God. Eght…® ia bar uan navir averiaba ko uan duaba ko uan gavgaviba sara bar a gifongegh.
\v 6 \x - \xo 6:6-9 \xt God…®n Araziba 11:18-20\x*K…® ia gan…®dir akar kaba, ia da is…® uan navir averiabar arigh, egh dagh n…®ghn…®ghv…®ra ik…®.
\v 7 Egh dughiar ia uan boriba ko d…®penim…®n ikia avughsiba, ko dughiar ia me ko tuavibar zuiba, ko ia dakuasa m…®siabar itir dughiaba, ko dughiar ia m…®siabar d…®kaviba, ia zurara akar kaba dar men sure damuv…®ra ik…®.
\v 8 Egh akar kaba ak…®nafarim…®n ada osirigh, da is…® uan agharibar arigh da uan guabagh ikegh, egh da g…®n amangan mark…®.
\v 9 Egh akar kaba uan d…®penibar tiar akabar ak…®niba, ko nguibaba av…®nizir d…®vazibar tiar akabar da osirigh.‚Äù
\s1 Israelia God…®n akaba bar adar g…®n mangam
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 6:10 \xt Jenesis 12:7; 26:3; 28:13\x*Egha Moses kamagh…®n m…®gei ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, en God, en inazir afeziaba, Abraham, Aisak, Jekop, ko akam ak…®righa ghaze, A nguazitam is…® ia dan…®ngam. Nguazir kam, nguibar ekiar aghuiba an iti. Nguibar ekiar kaba, ia uari dar ingarizir puvat…®.
\v 11 Eght…® bizir aghuir av…®riba ian d…®penibagh izevegham. Bizir kaba ia fom…®ra da isa uan d…®penibagh ar…®ghizir puvat…®. Eght…® mozir d…®par ia fom…®ra kuizir puvat…®ziba ik…®t…®, wain…®n azeniba ko oliv…®n azenir ia ingarava oparizir puvat…®ziba ikiam. Eght…® ia an aven ik…® damasa ifongezir daghebar am…® bar izevegham.
\v 12 Egh, ia deraghv…®ra uari bagh gan. Ia fo, ia Isip…®n kantrin ikia pura ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar m…®n itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ia inigha ian akuava azenan ize. Eght…® ia a g…®n amangan mark…®.
\v 13 \x - \xo 6:13 \xt Matyu 4:10; Luk 4:8\x*Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, an atiating an apengara ik…® an ziamra fam. Egh ia uan akaba gavgavim dar an…®ngs…®, an ziamra d…®pon akar d…®k…®r…®zim damu.
\v 14 Egh ian borogh…®n itir gumazamizibar aseba, ia dar ziaba fan mark…®.
\v 15 Ia kamagh…®n fogh, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ia ko iti, ez…® gumazamiziba asebar g…®n zuima, God…®n navim me bagha bar ikufi. Eght…® ia asebar ziaba f…®t…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ian atar, mati avim bizibar isia da gevi mogh…®n, ia ag…®vaght…®, ia ua nguazir kam…®n ikian kogham.
\p 
\v 16 \x - \xo 6:16 \xt Ua Me Ini 17:1-7; Matyu 4:7; Luk 4:12\x*‚ÄúEgh ia uan Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, an araziba tuis…®gh a g…®foghs…® an gavgavim bagh azangan mark…®, mati ia Masan danganim…®n amiz…® mok…®n.
\v 17 Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, m…®kemezir Akar Gavgaviba, ko akar a ia gan…®ngiziba, ko arazir a ifongeziba, ia dar g…®n mangasa, a ia m…®g…®a ghaze, ia guizbang…®ra bar adar g…®n mang…®.
\v 18 Ia arazir aghuir Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n deraziba, ia dar amu, eght…® bizir ia damuamiba bar deraghv…®ram otivam. Eght…® nguazir aghuir Ikiav…®ra Itir God ia dan…®ngasa ian inazir afeziaba ko akam ak…®rizir kam, ia an aven mang…® a iniam.
\v 19 Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ia koma akam ak…®riz…® mogh…®ra, ia uan apanibav sogh me batuegham.
\p 
\v 20 ‚ÄúDughiar g…®n izamim…®n, ian boriba iz…® kamagh…®n ian azangam, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God, en God, akar ia gan…®ngizir kaba, ko arazir a ifongeziba, ko bizir a damuasa ia m…®kemezir kaba, dar m…®ngarim manmak…®n? Ia ti fo?‚Äô
\v 21 Eght…® ia kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòE Isip…®n kantrin atrivim…®n ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uab…® uan gavgavim…®n uam e ini.
\v 22 E bar guizbang…®ra, uari uan damazibar garima, a mirakel…®n igharagha gariba ko d…®gavir kuram gamir arazaraziba, Isipia ko, men atrivim ko, an gumazir ekiaba, me gami.
\v 23 Egha a Isip…®n kantrin e inigha azenan ize, eght…® a en inazir afeziaba ko akam ak…®rizir nguazim e dan…®ng…®s…®, e inigh mang…® e dan…®ngam.
\v 24 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, arazir a ifongezir kabar g…®n mangasa e m…®keme, eght…® e an atiating an apengara ikiam. E kamagh…®n damut…®, a en kantrin aven deraghv…®ram e geghuv en gant…®, e deraghv…®ra ikiam, mati e dat…®r…®gh…®n iti mok…®n.
\v 25 Egh e Akar Gavgavir kaba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God…®n damazim…®n dar g…®n mang…®t…®, God, e m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, a kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, e an damazim…®n dera.‚Äô ‚Äù
\c 7
\s1 Israelia, kar God ua baghav…®ra m…®sevezir ik…®zim
\r (Ua Me Ini 34:11-16)
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 7:1 \xt Aposel 13:19\x*Moses ua kamagh…®n Israelia m…®gei:
\p ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, en God, e inigh nguazir e ikiamin kam…®n mang…®s…®, a nguazir kam…®n itir ik…®zir av…®riba batuegh ia inigh izam. Ia mang…® nguazir kam inis…® an aven mang…®t…®, a ian faragh mang…®, 7plan ik…®zir gavgaviba me batuegham. Men gavgaviba ko gumazamizibar d…®bobonim bar, ian gavgaviba ko d…®bobonim gafira. Ik…®zir kabar kara, Hitia, Girgasia, Amoria, Kenania, Peresia, Hivia, ko Jebusia.
\v 2 Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, me is…® ian dafarim dat…®ght…®, ia bar me m…®soght…® me bar ar…®m…®ghiregh. Egh ia men apangkuv me ko akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavitam damuan bar mark…®.
\v 3 Egh ia me ko guiviba ikarvaghs…® akam ak…®ran mark…®. Ia uan guiviba is…® men otaribar ar…®ght…®, me men ikian mark…®. Eght…® ia men guiviba init…®, me ian otaribar ikian mark…®.
\v 4 K…® fo, me men ik…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ategh saghon ik…®, men asebar ziaba fam. Ian boriba kamagh…®n damut…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian atar, egh zuam…®ra ia gas…®ghasigham.
\v 5 \x - \xo 7:5 \xt God…®n Araziba 12:3\x*Ia gumazamizir kaba ko poghan mark…®. Bar mark…®. Ia kamagh…®n damu. Ia me ofabar amuasa tuer biziba, ko men ofa gamir dakoziba ap…®rarigh, men dag…®ar guarir d…®ghoriba itiba bar da m…®sarar…®kigh. Egh temer guarir aser amizim Aseran nedazim itiba ok…®va marvir guabar apongt…® da isi.
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 7:6 \xt Ua Me Ini 19:5; God…®n Araziba 4:20; 14:2; 26:18; Taitus 2:14; 1 Pita 2:9\x*‚ÄúIa Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, guizbang…®ra ua baghav…®ra m…®sevezir gumazamiziba. Nguazim…®n gumazamiziba bar men tong…®n, a ua baghav…®ra iarara am…®sefe. Ez…® ia an gumazamizibara, a bar ia gifonge.
\p 
\v 7 ‚ÄúIa Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizibar m…®n av…®rasemeght…®, a ia gifuegh ua bagh ia am…®s…®vam. Puvat…®, ian d…®bobonim a bar sufi.
\v 8 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, bar ia gifuegha, ian inazir afeziaba ko amizir akar d…®k…®r…®zim g…®n…®ghn…®gha an g…®n zui. Egha bizir kam bagha a ian akuragha ua ia ini. Ia pura ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar m…®n Isip…®n kantrin atrivim…®n apengan itima, a uan gavgavir ekiam…®n ia inigha azenan ize.
\v 9 \x - \xo 7:9-10 \xt Ua Me Ini 20:5-6; 34:6-7; D…®boboniba 14:18; God…®n Araziba 5:9-10\x*Ia derav…®ra bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a guizbang…®ra God, egha zurara uan Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavibar g…®n ghua bizibagh ami. Egha gumazamizir av…®rir an Akar Gavgavibar g…®n ghua a gifongeziba, a men apangkuv, kamagh…®ra mang…®v…®ra ikiam.
\v 10 Egha a gifongezir puvat…®zir gumazamiziba, a men arazir kam ikarvagha zuam…®ra ivezir kuram me gan…®ga me gas…®ghas…®si.
\v 11 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God…®n Akar Gavgavir kaba, kar arazir God ifongeziba ko bizir a damuasa ia m…®kemeziba, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n da isa ia gan…®di. Eght…® ia bar deraghv…®ra dar g…®n mang…®.‚Äù
\s1 Gumazamizir God…®n Akar Gavgavibar g…®n zuiba, a deraghv…®ra me damuam
\r (God…®n Araziba 28:1-14)
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 7:12-16 \xt God…®n Araziba 11:13-17\x*Moses kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa bizir k…® damuasa ia m…®kemeziba baragh deragh dar g…®n mang…®t…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir a fom…®ra ian inazir afeziaba ko amizim…®n g…®n mang…®va bar ian apangkuvigham.
\v 13 A bar ia gifuegh derav…®ra ia damut…®, ia borir av…®riba bat…®t…®, ian adarazi bar av…®rasemegham. Egh a ian azeniba deragh dar amight…®, ian witba ko bali ko wain…®n ikar…®ziba ko oliv…®n temeba, da ov…®zir av…®riba ikiam. Egh deragh ian bulmakauba ko sipsipbar amut…®, da nguzir av…®riba batam. Eght…® ia, nguazir a fom…®ra ia dan…®ngasa ian inazir afeziaba ko akam ak…®rizim, ia an aven ik…®t…®, God deragh ia damu nguazir kam…®n itir bizir aghuiba is…® bar ia dan…®ngam.
\v 14 God bar derav…®ra ia gami mogh…®n, a nguazir kam…®n ik…®ziba bar, men tong…®n ik…®zir igharazitam, ian m…®n deragha me gamizir puvat…®. Ian amiziba, ko ian bulmakaun amebaba, tam pura ikian kogham, me bar mogh…®ra otam.
\v 15 Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, deraghv…®ra ian gant…® ar…®mariar guar igharagha garitaba ia bativan kogham. Egh ar…®mariar kurar ia Isip…®n ikia ganizir katam uam ia bativan kogham. Ar…®mariar kaba, da ian apanibara bativam.
\v 16 Eght…® ik…®zir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, ian dafarim dar…®ghamiba, ia bar mogh…®ra me ag…®fagh. Egh ia me ko men asebar ziaba fan mark…®. Ia men asebar ziaba f…®, mati ia as…®zim azuazim…®n aven ghu, egh arazir kam bang…®n ia ar…®m…®ghiregham. Kamagh…®n, ia tong men apangkuvan mark…®. Bar mark…®.
\p 
\v 17 ‚ÄúIa ik…®zir kabar gan kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, me bar av…®rasemegha, men gavgavim e gafira. Eght…® e me gas…®ghas…®ghs…® iburaghburegham.
\v 18 Puvat…®, ia men atiatingan mark…®. Ia bizir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, Isip…®n atrivim ko an gumazamizibagh amizibagh n…®ghn…®gh.
\v 19 Egh ia ar…®mariar bar kurar ia Isip…®n uari uan damazibar ganizibagh n…®ghn…®gh. Egh uaghan mirakelba ko d…®gavir kuram gamir arazarazir God amizibagh n…®ghn…®gh. Ia bar fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God uan dafarim…®n ingangarir ekiabagh amigha Isip…®n kantrin aven ia inigha ize, ia bizir kabagh n…®ghn…®gh. Eght…® ik…®zir ia dat…®r…®gh…®n atiatiba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, arazir kamagh…®ra garim…®n me damu bar me gas…®ghas…®gham.
\v 20 Eght…® men tarazi ian ar…® mang…® mueght…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, apizir gumazamiziba apiba amang…®t…®, da mang…® atiatir ekiam me dan…®ng…®va me gas…®ghas…®gham.
\p 
\v 21 ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, gavgavir bar ekiam ikia e ko iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia ik…®zir kabar atiatingan mark…®. A gavgavir bar ekiam iti, eght…® gumazamiziba bar an atiatingam.
\v 22 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ian faragh mang…® aghumra ik…®zir kaba batogh me amang…®t…®, me ar…® mangam. Eght…® ia zuam…®ra me gas…®ghasighan kogham. Ia zuam…®ra me gas…®ghasight…®, as…®zir atiaba av…®rasemegh otivigh iz…® ia m…®soght…® ia ar…®m…®ghiregham.
\v 23 Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ian apanibar amight…® me bar atiatigh ik…®v…®ra ik…® mang…®t…®, dughiar ia bar me d…®kab…®ragh me ab…®namim otogham.
\v 24 God uaghan men atriviba is…® ian dafaribar arigham. Eght…® ia me m…®soght…®, me ar…®m…®ghireght…®, gumazamiziba me g…®n amadagham. Ia me m…®soghamin dughiam…®n, gumazitam ian anogoreghan kogham. Ia bar me m…®sogh…®rarigham.
\p 
\v 25 ‚ÄúIa bar men asebar marvir guabar apongt…® da isigh. Egh men silva ko gol…®n me uan asebar marvir guabar kurtibagh ifongan mark…®. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, a bar aser kabar marvir guabar aghua. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia bizir kaba inian mark…®. Ia da inight…® da ti azuazim…®n m…®n, ian suight…® ia ar…®m…®ghiregham.
\v 26 Egh ia aser kabar marvir guatam inigh uan d…®penibar aven izan mark…®. Ia tam inigh izeght…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, dagh gas…®ghas…®zi mogh…®n ia gas…®ghas…®gham. Aser kaba da bizir bar kuraba, ez…® God bar dar aghua. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia dar aghuagh bar ak…®riba ighegh dagh asaragh.‚Äù
\c 8
\s1 Israelia nguazir aghuim iniam
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Moses kamagh…®n Israelia m…®gei:
\p ‚ÄúAkar gavgavir k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia gan…®dir kaba, ia bar derav…®ra dar g…®n mang…®. Ia kamagh…®n damuva, derav…®ra ik…® ot…® bar av…®rasemegham. Ia uaghan mang…® nguazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God ian inazir afeziabar an…®ngasa me ko akam ak…®rizim…®n aven mang…®, a inigh an ikiam.
\v 2 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, a 40plan azenibar ian faragha ghua ia inigha gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim garui. Ia bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®ghv…®ra ik…®. A dughiar kam…®n ian navir averiabagh fofoghasa, ia an Akar Gavgavibagh n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra iti, o puvat…®. Ia uari fer arazim ag…®vagh, an apengan ikiasa, an os…®mt…®zir maba ia gan…®ngi.
\v 3 \x - \xo 8:3 \xt Ua Me Ini 16:1-35; Matyu 4:4; Luk 4:4\x*Ia uari fer arazim ag…®vasa, a ia ataghiz…®, m…®tiriam ian azi. Egha a daghem mana, isa ia gan…®ngiz…® ia aneme. Dagher kam, ia a g…®fozir puvat…®, ez…® ian inazir afeziaba uaghan fom…®ra a g…®fozir puvat…®. A ghaze, a kamagh…®n damight…® ia fogh suam, e gumazamiziba daghebara dam…®va dar gavgavim…®n ikian kogham. Puvat…®. Me Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®geir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba bar dar g…®n mang…®va, ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim iniam.
\v 4 Ez…® ia 40plan azenir kabar arua izima, ian korotiaba b…®aghirezir puvat…®. Ez…® ian dagariba uaghan ian bezir puvat…®.
\v 5 \x - \xo 8:5 \xt Aghuzir Akaba 3:12; Hibru 12:6\x*Ia kamagh…®n fogh, afeziam uan borim ak…®ra an sure gami mogh…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ia ak…®rm…®gha ian sure gami.
\v 6 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ia m…®kemezir bizibar amu, egh an atiati an apengara ik…® an Akar Gavgavibar g…®n mang…®.
\p 
\v 7 ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ian akua kantrin bar aghuir kam bagha zui. Nguazir kam, a faner ekiaba ko mozir d…®paba itima, d…®par maba nguazim…®n apengan ivemara, egha danganir zariba ko m…®ghs…®ar dozibar otiva afora dar izaghiri.
\v 8 Ez…® nguazir kam dagher av…®riba an otifi, wit ko bali, wain…®n ov…®ziba, pomigranet…®n ov…®ziba, figh…®n ov…®ziba, oliv…®n ov…®ziba, ko, hanin eborim, da bar mogh…®ra an otifi.
\v 9 Eght…® nguazir kam…®n, m…®tiriaba ian aghan koght…®, ia bizitam…®n oteveghan kogham. Ez…® nguibar kam…®n dag…®aba, ain ko kapa dar aven iti, eght…® ia m…®ghs…®ar kabagh kuva da iniam.
\v 10 Egh bizir ia damasa ifongeziba, ia bar ada iniam. Egh ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, kantrin aghuir a ia gan…®ngizir kam bagh an ziam f…® a m…®nabam.‚Äù
\s1 Israelia, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bak…®n…®ghn…®ghan kogham
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 8:11-16 \xt Hosea 13:5-6\x*Egha Moses kamagh…®n Israelia m…®gei:
\p ‚ÄúIa uari bagh derav…®ra gan, egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God bak…®n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®. Ia ti kamagh…®n damuva, ia God…®n Akar Gavgaviba ko bizir a damuasa ia m…®kemeziba ko, arazir a ifongeziba ia da abigham, kar arazir bar kuram.
\v 12 Ia g…®n dagher damamin aghuir av…®riba ik…®, egh d…®penir bar aghuibar ingar…®va dar aven ikiam,
\v 13 egh sipsipba ko bulmakauba, gol ko silva ko, bizir aghuiba, da bar av…®rasemegham.
\v 14 Ia dughiar kam…®n, uari f…®va akaba batogh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, a bak…®n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®. Ia ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar m…®n Isip…®n kantrin itima, a ua ia inigha azenan ize.
\v 15 Egh a uab…® ian faragha ghua gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganir kurar ekiar kam…®n ghu. Danganir kam kuruziba ko tuighakar imezir kuraba itiba an iti. Egha danganir kam a bar m…®s…®ngiz…®, d…®paba an puvat…®. Ez…® God dag…®ar bar gavgavir mam gamiz…®, d…®pam an otogha izaghirima ia aneme.
\v 16 Egha danganir kam…®n a manan daghem ia gan…®ngiz…® ia aneme. Manan dagher kam, ia ko ian inazir afeziaba fom…®ram anemegha a g…®fozir puvat…®. A kamagh…®n ifonge, ia uari ab…®nigh an apengara ikiam. Egh a kamagh…®n foghasa, ia ti an akabar g…®n mang…® biziba bar dar amuam, o puvat…®gham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, an os…®mt…®ziba ia bagha da amadi. Egh a g…®n bizir bar aghuiba is…® ia dan…®ngam.
\v 17 Eght…® ia kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, e bizir aghuir kaba uan gavgavim…®n dagh amiz…®, da otifi. Puvat…®.
\v 18 \x - \xo 8:18 \xt Aghuzir Akaba 10:22; Hosea 2:8\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, a uab…® gavgavim ia gan…®dima, ia bizir av…®riba isi. An arazir a ia gamir kabar m…®ngarim kamak…®n, a ian inazir afeziaba ko amizir Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha kamagh…®n amua dat…®r…®gh…®n ghuav…®ra iti.
\v 19 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ia a g…®n amadagh asebar g…®n mang…® dar ziaba fan mark…®. K…® ikiangs…®zir gavgavim ia gan…®ga ghaze, ia akar kam baraghan aghuagh, egh kamagh…®n damuva, ia guizbang…®ra ar…®m…®ghiregham.
\v 20 Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n tiarim baraghan aghuaght…®, a ik…®zir igharaziba ian damazim…®n dagh as…®ghas…®ghiz…® mogh…®n, a uaghan ia gas…®ghasigham.‚Äù
\c 9
\s1 Israelia, God…®n akam batoke
\p 
\v 1 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n Israelia m…®gei:
\p ‚ÄúO Israelia, ia oragh! Ia bar dughiar ovezim…®n Jordan…®n Fanem gir…®gh vong…®n mangam. Ia mang…® ganigh, ik…®zir ekiaba, men gavgavim ian gavgavim gafira, ia men nguazim iniam. Me nguibar ekiar av…®riba itima, da av…®nizir d…®vaziba bar ghuavanaga overiam…®n suira.
\v 2 Ez…® Anak…®n ik…®zir ekiabar gumazamiziba bar ekevegha, gavgavigha agharapaniba sarama aghungi. Ez…® ia men eghaghanim baregha fo, gumazitam me m…®sogh me ab…®raghan kogham.
\v 3 Ia dat…®r…®gh…®n uari uan damazibar gant…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, avir bar puv…®ra isim…®n m…®n ian faragh mangam. Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…®, akar d…®k…®r…®zir ia bagha amizim…®n g…®n mang…®, ian faragh mang…® men gavgaviba bar da ab…®nigham. Eght…® g…®n ia me m…®sogh bar zuam…®ra me gas…®ghasigham.
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 9:4 \xt Ofa Gami 18:3; 18:24-30; God…®n Araziba 12:31; 18:9; 18:14\x*‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, me batuegh g…®vaght…®, ia uan navir averiabar kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam mark…®, ‚ÄòGod ti en garima, e an damazim…®n bar dera, ez…® a en arazir aghuir kam bang…®n nguazir aghuir kam isa e gan…®ngi.‚Äô N…®ghn…®zir kam a guiz…®n n…®ghn…®zim puvat…®. Bar guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ik…®zir kabar gumazamizibar garima, me arazir kurar av…®ribagh ami, kamagh…®n amiz…®, a me batueghasava ami.
\v 5 Ia kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, ia uan navir averiabar aven bar deragha, arazir God…®n damazim…®n zuezibagh ami. Puvat…®, ik…®zir igharazir kabar gumazamiziba, me arazir bar kurabagh ami, kamagh…®n God me batuegham. Egha uaghan, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, uan akar d…®k…®r…®zir ian inazir afeziaba, Abraham, Aisak, Jekop, ko amizim…®n g…®n mangasa ifonge. Kamagh…®n, a me batueght…®, ia men nguazim iniam.
\v 6 Ia kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, ia gumazamizir God…®n damazim deraziba. Kamagh…®n amiz…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ian arazir aghuiba ikarvagha ivezir aghuim…®n m…®n nguazir aghuir kam ia gan…®di. Bar puvat…®. Guizbang…®ra, ia gumazamizir navir bar gavgaviba itiba, egha ia an akaba baraghan aghua.
\p 
\v 7 ‚ÄúIa bizir kam gin…®r…®gh, egh deraghv…®ram a g…®n…®ghn…®gh: Ia gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ikia Ikiav…®ra Itir God gamiz…®, a ian an…®ngaghe. Ia fom…®ra Isip ategha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, ia dughiar ruarir kam…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam batoghav…®ra iti.
\v 8 Ia fom…®ra, Sainain M…®ghs…®am…®n borogh…®n ikia, Ikiav…®ra Itir God gamiz…®, a bar an…®ngaghegha atam ia gas…®ghas…®ki.
\v 9 \x - \xo 9:9 \xt Ua Me Ini 24:18\x*Ez…® k…® dag…®ar akuar kamning iniasa m…®ghs…®am…®n ghuavanabo. Kar, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ia koma amizir Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n osizirim itir dag…®ar akuar pumuning. Dughiar kam…®n, k…® 40plan arueba ko d…®magaribar m…®ghs…®am…®n ikia, d…®patam ko daghetam amezir puvat…®.
\v 10 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, dag…®ar akuar kamning isa na gan…®ngi. Dag…®ar akuar kamning, ia m…®ghs…®am…®n borogh…®n uari akuvagha itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God avim…®n aven ikia, ia m…®kemezir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba, a uab…® aning…®n ada osiri.
\p 
\v 11 ‚ÄúK…® 40plan arueba ko d…®magaribar m…®ghs…®am…®n p…®n iti. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n osizirim itir dag…®ar akuamning isa na gan…®ngi.
\v 12 Egha a kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…®n gumazamizir n…® Isip…®n kantrin inigha azenan izeziba, me arazir kurar bar av…®rim gami. Egha me zuam…®ra ak…®rim ragha nan akabagh asaragha, uari bagha bulmakaun nedazir mam gol…®n an ingari. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® zuam…®ra d…®kavigh m…®ghs…®am ategh mag…®r…®.‚Äô
\p 
\v 13 ‚ÄúEgha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ua na m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòGumazamizir kaba k…® men gara me g…®fo, me na baraghan aghuagha nan akam batoke.
\v 14 Ez…® k…® bar me gas…®ghasight…® gumazitam ua me g…®n…®ghn…®ghan kogham. K…® kamagh…®n me damigh, g…®n n…® damight…®, n…® ik…®zir gavgavir bar av…®rim…®n afeziam…®n otoght…®, ik…®zir kam…®n d…®bobonim ko gavgavim, bar gumazamizir kurar kabar d…®bobonim ko gavgavim gafiragham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® nan anogoroghan mark…®.‚Äô
\p 
\v 15 ‚ÄúKamagh…®n, k…® d…®kavigha dag…®ar akuar Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim itimning, uan dafarimning…®n aning…®n suiragha, m…®ghs…®am…®n uaghiri. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, avir ekiam m…®ghs…®am…®n dafogha isima, an m…®zariaba ak…®z…®r…®gha ghuavanadi.
\v 16 K…® izaghir…®gha g…®vagha garima, ia guizbang…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, an akaba ak…®rim ragha dagh asara. Egha ia uari bagha gol…®n bulmakaun igiar mam…®n nedazim…®n ingarigha g…®fa. Arazir kam…®n, ia arazir kuram gamigha zuam…®ra tuavir Ikiav…®ra Itir God ian akazim ataki.
\v 17 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® ian damazibar, dag…®ar akuar kamning…®n suiragha aning akuniz…®, aning ira bar m…®saraghire.
\v 18 Egha g…®n k…® uamategha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n ghua nguazim…®n fuagha, uan guam nguazim m…®tuagha ir…®ghav iti. K…® 40plan arueba ko d…®magaribar kamagh…®ra ikia, egha d…®patam ko daghetam amezir puvat…®. K…® fo, ia arazir kuram Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n a gamua, a gamiz…®, a puv…®ra ian atari, ez…® k…® ia bagha kamagh…®n ami.
\v 19 \x - \xo 9:19 \xt Hibru 12:21\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God, bar ian an…®ngaghegha ia g…®vasa n…®ghn…®si, kamagh…®n k…® atiatingi. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, faragha amiz…® mogh…®n, ua nan azangs…®zim baraki.
\v 20 Dughiar kam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uaghan bar puv…®ra Aron…®n an…®ngaghegha, a m…®sueght…® an aremeghasava ami. Ez…® k…® faragha amiz…® mogh…®n, Aron ko ia bagha God ko m…®geima, a nan azangs…®zim ikara.
\v 21 Ia bulmakaun kam…®n ingarigha arazir kuram gami. Ez…® k…® bulmakau inigha ghua a isa avim m…®k…®ni. Egha k…® bar a anem…®saragharigha, a m…®rm…®righa an avereniba inigha da isa, m…®ghs…®am…®n ivemara uaghirir daghurir d…®pam m…®k…®ni.
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 9:22 \xt Ua Me Ini 17:7; D…®boboniba 11:3; 11:34\x*‚ÄúIa Masa, ko Tabera ko Kibrot Hatavan itir dughiabar, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God gamiz…®, a bar ian an…®ngaghe.
\v 23 \x - \xo 9:23 \xt D…®boboniba 14:1-10; God…®n Araziba 1:21; 1:26; Hibru 3:16\x*Ia faragha ghua Kades Barnean itima, a ia m…®g…®a ghaze, Ia mang…® nguazir a ia dan…®ngamin kam…®n aven mang…® a dapiam. Ez…® ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n itir puvat…®gha, an akam…®n g…®n mangan aghuagha a batoke.
\v 24 K…® fom…®ra ia ko ingara ia inigha izezir dughiam…®n ikegha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, k…® bar ia g…®fo, ia gumazamizir God…®n akaba batoziba.
\p 
\v 25 ‚ÄúIan arazir kuram bang…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar ia gas…®ghas…®ghasava amima, k…® 40plan arueba ko d…®magaribar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n nguazim…®n fuagha uan guam nguazim m…®tuagha ir…®ghav ikia,
\v 26 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, nan Ekiam, ga uaning, n…® uan gumazamizibagh as…®ghas…®ghan mark…®. N…® uab…® uan gavgavim…®n gumazamizir kaba Isip…®n kantrin me inigha azenan ize. N…® uan gavgavir ekiam…®n men akuragha ua me inigha g…®fa.
\v 27 N…® uan ingangarir gumaziba, Abraham, Aisak ko, Jekop, me g…®n…®ghn…®gh, akaba batozir gumazamizir kabar arazir bar kurar kabagh n…®ghn…®gh da ikarvaghan mark…®.
\v 28 N…® kamagh…®n damight…®, Isipia ti kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, gumazamizir kaba inigha nguazir me dan…®ngasa me ko akam ak…®rizim, bagh mangan iburaghburaki. Puvat…®, God gumazamizir kabar aghuagha, aremeghasa, me inigha gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ghu.
\v 29 Mevzika, gumazamizir kaba n…® ua baghav…®ra me am…®sefe. Egha n…® uan gavgavir ekiam…®n Isip…®n kantrin me inigha azenan ize. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® me gas…®ghas…®ghan mark…®.‚Äô ‚Äù
\c 10
\s1 Moses namba 2…®n dughiam…®n // Akar Gavgavir 10pla ini
\r (Ua Me Ini 34:1-10)
\p 
\v 1 Egha Moses Israelia m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚Äú40plan arueba ko d…®magariba g…®vaz…®ma, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ua kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® dag…®ar akuar faragha d…®tuzir pumuning…®n m…®rara ua pumuning atugh, egh aning inigh na bagh m…®ghs…®am…®n anang. Egh ter araritaba aghoregh boksiam…®n ingarigh.
\v 2 Eght…® k…® dag…®ar akuar kamning, akar k…® faragha dag…®ar akuar n…® inigha ghua b…®ghizimning…®n osiriziba, aning…®n da osiram. K…® akaba osirigh g…®vaght…® n…® aning is…® boksiam darugh.‚Äô
\p 
\v 3 ‚ÄúEgha k…® temer akas…®n boksiar mam…®n ingarigha, dag…®ar faragha dutuz…®mning…®n m…®rara dag…®ar akuar pumuning atugha, aning inigha ua m…®ghs…®am…®n ghuavanabo.
\v 4 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, dag…®ar akuar kamning…®n, faragha uan akaba osiriz…® mogh…®n, ua da osiri. A uan 10plan Akar Gavgaviba osiri, a faragha dughiar ia m…®ghs…®am…®n apengan uari akuvagha itim…®n, an avim…®n aven ikia akar kabara ia m…®keme, a dat…®r…®gh…®n uam ada osiri. Egha a dag…®ar akuar kamning isa na gan…®ngi.
\v 5 Ikiav…®ra Itir God na m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, k…® uamategha izaghira dag…®ar akuar kamning isa Boksiar k…® ingarizim…®n aven aning at…®. Ez…® dag…®ar akuamning Boksiam…®n aven ikia iti.‚Äù
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 10:6 \xt D…®boboniba 20:28; 33:38\x*Egha g…®n Israelia Jakanian gumazamizibar mozir d…®paba ategha, Moser…®n nguibam…®n ghue. Aron kagh aremez…®, me an kuam isa mozim gat…®. Ez…® an otarim Eleasar, an danganim inigha, ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim…®n iti.
\v 7 Egha me kagh d…®kavigha Gugodan danganim…®n ghuegha, g…®n ghua Jotbatan danganim…®n ghu. Kar danganir daghurir d…®par av…®riba itim.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 10:8 \xt D…®boboniba 3:5-8\x*Me faragha Sainain M…®ghs…®am…®n borogh…®n itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiar kam…®n ganasa, Livain anabam…®n gumazibav sefe. Gumazir kaba, me ofa gamir ingangarim damu, egh gumazamizibav k…®m suam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, bar deraghv…®ra me damuam. Livaiba dughiar kam…®n ikegha ingangarir kam gamua iza dat…®r…®k…®n.
\v 9 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Livain anabam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God nguazir as…®zitam me gan…®ngizir puvat…®. A nguaziba Israelian anabar igharazibagh an…®ngi, ez…® Livaiba puvat…®. Livain anabam, men bizir aghuir Ikiav…®ra Itir God me gan…®ngizim, a kamak…®n, me ofa gamir ingangaribar amuam, mati Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, faragha akam me bagh anek…®riz…® mok…®n.
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 10:10 \xt Ua Me Ini 34:28\x*Moses Israelia m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® 40plan arueba ko d…®magaribar m…®ghs…®am…®n p…®n iti, mati k…® faragha amiz…® mok…®n. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, nan azangs…®zim uam a baraki. Egha ia gas…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®.
\v 11 Egha a kamagh…®n na m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® d…®kavigh gumazamizibar faragh mang…®, nguazir k…® me dan…®ngasa men inazir afeziaba koma akam ak…®rizim iniam.‚Äô ‚Äù
\s1 Arazir God ifongeziba
\p 
\v 12 Moses ua kamagh…®n Israelia m…®gei, ‚ÄúO Israelia, ia oragh. K…® ian azai, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God ifongezir arazir aghuir manaba ia dar amuam? Arazir kaba: Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n atiating…®va an apengara ik…®, egh an akaba bar dar g…®n mang…®. Egh a gifuegh, egh bar uan navir averiaba ko duaba sara bar akongegh an ingangarim damu.
\v 13 Egh an Akar Gavgaviba ko arazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God ifongeziba, k…® ian akurvaghasa dat…®r…®gh…®n ia m…®gei, ia bar dar g…®n mang…®, egh deraghv…®ra ikiam.
\v 14 Ia oragh, overiar bar p…®n itim, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God nanam. Ez…® nguazim ko an itir biziba da uaghan an bizibara.
\v 15 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian inazir afeziaba, uan navir averiam…®n aven bar me gifongegha, ua bagha ik…®zir igharazibar tong…®n ia am…®sevegha, uaghan ian ovavir boriba am…®sefe. A ua baghav…®ra ia ginabaz…®, ia dat…®r…®gh…®n an gumazamizibara.
\v 16 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia uan navir averiabar aven akaba batozir arazim atugh a batokegh, mati gumaziba m…®karzir mogomebar inibar ghori.
\v 17 \x - \xo 10:17 \xt Aposel 10:34; Rom 2:11; Galesia 2:6; Efesus 6:9; 1 Timoti 6:15; Akar Mogomem 17:14; 19:16\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, god…®n ifavariba ko bizir bar gavgaviba itibagh afira. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a bar ekevegha bar gavgaviz…®, biziba bar an gavgavim…®n atiatigha an apengan iti. Gumazir ziam itim, o gumazir ziam puvat…®zim, an arazir vam…®ran g…®n ghua men araziba tuis…®si. A kot…®n aven gumazamiziba atagh…®razi, me an n…®ghn…®zim g…®ghasa dag…®aba a gan…®dir puvat…®.
\v 18 Egha amizir paba ariaghireziba a deraghav…®ra me gamuava, borir afeziaba ariaghireziba a uaghan deraghv…®ra me gami. Egha ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizir en tong…®n itiba, a me gifuegha dagheba ko korotiaba me gan…®di.
\v 19 Ia faragha, ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizibar m…®n Isip…®n kantrin ike. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia uaghan ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizibagh ifongegh.
\v 20 Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, an atiating an apengan ik…®, egh an ziamra f…®. Egh an porogh gavgavigh, an ziamra d…®pon ia uan akar d…®k…®r…®zibar amu.
\v 21 Anar…®ra, a ian God, kamagh…®n ia an ziam f…®. Ia uari bizir ekiar igharagha garibar gari, a ian akurvaghasa dagh ami.
\v 22 \x - \xo 10:22 \xt Jenesis 15:5; 22:17; 46:27\x*Ian inazir afeziar 70pla, merara Isip…®n ghue. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, ia gamiz…® ia overiam…®n m…®kovezibar m…®n bar av…®raseme.‚Äù
\c 11
\s1 God ziar ekiam iti
