\s1 God, asebar ziaba fan Israelian anogoroke
\p 
\v 29 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa mang…® ik…®zir igharazir kabar nguazibar aven mangamin dughiam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ian faragh mang…® bar me gas…®ghasigham. Eght…® ia men nguazibar apiam.
