\v 32 \x - \xo 12:32 \xt God…®n Araziba 4:2; Akar Mogomem 22:18-19\x*‚ÄúEgh bizir k…® ia m…®kemezir kaba ia bar mogh…®ra dar amu. Egh akar igharazitam inigh uam akar kabagh isafuraghan mark…®, egh akar katam atagh…®raghan mark…®.‚Äù
\c 13
\p 
\v 1-2 ‚ÄúEght…® akam inigha izir gumazitam o irebabar m…®ngariba ab…®zir gumazitam iz…® ia geku suam, K…® fogha g…®fa mirakel…®n kam guizbang…®n otivam. Egh men tav, ia faragha ziaba fezir puvat…®zir asebar ziaba f…®s…®, ia m…®k…®mam.
\v 3 Eght…® da guiz…®n otivt…®, ia an akar kam baraghan mark…®. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ian araziba tuis…®gh foghasa, ia navir averiaba ko duabar guizbang…®ra a gifongez, o puvat…®. Egha a gumazir kaba ataghiz…® me iza ia gekuasava ami.
\v 4 Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n atiating an apengan ik…®, egh an g…®n mang…®. Egh ia an Akar Gavgaviba baragh dar suiragh gavgavigh, dar g…®n mang…® an ziam f…®.
\v 5 Egh ia akam inigha izir gumaziba ko, irebabar m…®ngariba ab…®zir gumazir kaba bar me m…®sueght…®, me ar…®m…®ghiregh. Ia fom…®ra Isip…®n kantrin ikia ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar m…®n itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God ia inigha Isip…®n azenan ize. Gumazir kamagh amiba, kar gumazir kuraba. Egh ia God bagh…®v…®ra ikiasa, me aghua. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me ia geku ia damight…®, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n g…®n zuir tuavim ategh an saghon ikiam. Kamagh…®n, ia gumazir kabav sueght…® me ar…®ghireght…®, arazir kurar kam g…®vagham.
\p 
\v 6 ‚ÄúEght…® ian namakatam, o aveghbuatam, o ian otaritam o ian guivitam, o ian amuir ia bar ifongezim, o ian roroar bar aghuim, a modogh ia geku, aghumra aser ia ko ian inazir afeziaba fom…®ra fezir puvat…®zibar ziaba f…®s…® ia m…®k…®mt…®, ia an akam baraghan mark…®.
\v 7 Nguazir kam…®n gumazamizir ian borogh…®n itiba ko ian saghuiam…®n itiba, bar mogh…®ra aser kabar ziaba fe.
\v 8 Ia gumazir kamagh…®n amibar apezeperir akaba baraghan mark…®, ia ak…®rim me gasaragh. Ia men akurvaghan mark…®. Egh ia apangkuvir arazim…®n me damuan mark…®.
\v 9 Gumazim o amizim kamagh…®n ia damut…®, ia a m…®sueght…®, an aremegh. N…® faragh uan dafarim…®n dag…®abar a ginivight…®, g…®n gumazamiziba bar dag…®abar a ginivam.
\v 10 Ia fom…®ra Isip…®n kantrin ikia ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar m…®n itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God ia inigha Isip…®n azenan ize. Egh me ia gekut…® ia God…®n akam…®n g…®n mangan kogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia dag…®abar me ginivt…®, me ar…®m…®ghiregh.
\v 11 Ia me m…®sueght…®, me ar…®m…®ghireght…®, Israelia bizir kam baregh atiating…®va uam arazir kurar katam damuan kogham.
\p 
\v 12-13 ‚ÄúIa Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, ia dan…®ngamin nguibar ekiabar ik…®v oraght…®, me kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, Gumazir kurar maba nguibar ekiar kam…®n itir gumazamizibar n…®ghn…®zibagh ekua ghaze, E asebar ziaba fam. Kar aser e faragha ziaba fezir puvat…®ziba.
\v 14 Ia kamagh…®n akar vaveba baregh, egh deraghv…®ram akar kam…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghs…® pamtem…®n ingar. Eght…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar bar kurar kam a guizbang…®ra ik…®t…®,
\v 15 kamagh…®n, ia nguibar kam…®n itir gumazamiziba ko men bulmakauba sara m…®sogh…®rarigh, men nguibar kam ko an itir biziba bar dagh as…®ghas…®kigh.
\v 16 Egh ia men biziba bar ada inigh, nguibam…®n torimra da akufagh. Egh ia nguibar kam daboroght…® an itir biziba bar isi ofan m…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God dan…®ng. Eght…® nguibar kam ikuvigh ik…® kamagh…®ra ik…®t…®, gumazitam uam an ingar anesaraghan kogham.
\v 17 Ia uari bagh nguibar kam…®n bizitam inian mark…®. Ia avim ateght…®ma a bar dar isigh. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uan an…®ngazim ategh, ian apangkuvigham. Egh a ian inazir afeziaba ko akar d…®k…®r…®zim gamiz…® mogh…®n, ia damight…® ian d…®bobonim ghuavanabogham.
\v 18 Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, an tiarim baragh…®va, an Akar Gavgavir k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia m…®geir kaba deragh dar g…®n mang…®va, an damazim…®n arazir aghuibar amut…®, a bizir aghuir kaba ia bagh dar amuam.‚Äù
\c 14
\s1 Israelia, ik…®zir igharazibar m…®n ariaghirir gumazamiziba bagh azian mark…®
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 14:1 \xt Ofa Gami 19:28; 21:5\x*Moses kamagh…®n Israelia m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, a ua baghav…®ra ia ginabaz…® ia an boriba. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ian gumazitam aremeght…® ia a bagh aziva, ik…®zir igharaziba ami mogh…®n, uan m…®karzibar ghor, egh m…®nedevir ar…®zibagh isan mark…®.
\v 2 \x - \xo 14:2 \xt Ua Me Ini 19:5-6; God…®n Araziba 4:20; 7:6; 26:18; Taitus 2:14; 1 Pita 2:9\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God nguazir kam…®n ik…®zibar tong…®n ia inigha ua baghav…®ra ia am…®sefe. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia an gumazamizibara.‚Äù
\s1 God…®n damazim…®n as…®zir // m…®z…®r…®ziba ko zueziba
\r (Ofa Gami 11:1-4)
\p 
\v 3 Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, as…®zir kabav g…®a ghaze, Da ikuviz…® an adar aghuagha, dar aman ian anogoroke.
\v 4 As…®zir kaba, ia dar am…®: bulmakau ko sipsip, meme,
\v 5 ko dia, sipsip…®n atiaba, memen atiaba, ko m…®ghs…®am…®n itir as…®zir atiar igharaziba, ia dar tuzibar am…®.
\v 6 As…®zir kabanang: Dar soroghafariba puzir pumuning ikia, aning uaning tuiragha iti, egha da bulmakaubar m…®n grazibar am…®t…®, ia dar am…®.
\v 7 Ez…® bulmakaubar m…®n graziba apir as…®ziba, dar soroghafariba puzir pumuning ikia, aning uaning tuiragha itir puvat…®, kamagh…®n ia bar dar aman mark…®. As…®zir kamagh…®n gariba: kamelba, ko ivarareba, ko igh…®aba, ia dar amam mark…®. Da bulmakaubar m…®n graziba apava, soroghafarir puziba bigha pumuning itir puvat…®. Ia kamagh…®n fogh, as…®zir kamagh…®n amiziba da God…®n damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®. An adar aman ian anogoroke.
\v 8 Ia dabar aman mark…®. Dar soroghafariba puzir pumuning ikia, aning uaning tuiragha ikia, bulmakaubar m…®n graziba apir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n, ia fogh, daba da nan damazim…®n m…®ze. Egh ia dar gant…® da ar…®ghir…®t…®, ia dar kuabar suighan mark…®. Bar markiam. Da nan damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 9 ‚ÄúEgh ongarim…®n osiriba ko d…®pam…®n osiribar tong…®n, osirir naziaba ko sighiaba itiba, da bizir kaba uaghara ik…®t…® ia dar am…®.
\v 10 Egh osiriba ko bizir muziarir ongarim…®n itiba, da naziaba ko sighiaba uaghara puvat…®ght…®, ia kamagh…®n fogh, Da God…®n damazim…®n m…®ze.
\p 
\v 11 ‚ÄúEgh kuarazir God…®n damazim…®n zueziba, ia dar am…®.
\v 12-18 Egh ia kuarazibar tong…®n kuarazir kamagh garibar aman mark…®. Kuarazir kaba, taragiaba, m…®gh…®aba, isaba, kotkotba, poneba, ongarim…®n kuaraziba, beniba, d…®pam…®n mughamiziba, aghunabar ekiaba ko, kina aghunababa.
\p 
\v 19 ‚ÄúEz…® apizir av…®ziba itiba, da bar bizir m…®z…®r…®ziba, kamagh…®n ia dar aman mark…®.
\v 20 Apizir igharazir av…®ziba ikia God…®n damazim…®n zueziba, ia dar am…®.
\p 
\v 21 \x - \xo 14:21 \xt Ua Me Ini 23:19; 34:26\x*‚ÄúEgh as…®zir puram ariagh…®riba, ia dar aman mark…®. Ia ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizir ian tong…®n itibar an…®ngt…® me dar am…®. Egh ia pura nguibam getiagha aruir gumazamizibar amamangat…®ght…®, me ia da dagh ivez dar am…®. Ia guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, a ua baghav…®ra ia am…®sevezir gumazamiziba.
\p ‚ÄúIa memen oter eborim is…®, m…®nem gingegh, memen amebar kam…®n nguzim…®n tuzim is…®, m…®ner kam…®n anevighan mark…®.‚Äù
\s1 Ia 10plan bizibar tong…®n vam…®ra is…® God dan…®ngam
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 14:22-29 \xt Ofa Gami 27:30-33; D…®boboniba 18:21\x*Moses kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúDagher ia zurara uan azenibar isiba, ia da ab…®gh 10plan pozibav k…®nigh, dar pozir vam…®ra anet…®ght…® a ik…®.
\v 23 Egh g…®n ia da inigh mang…® danganir Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan ziam f…®s…® m…®s…®vamim…®n danganim…®n dar at…®gh. Egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n, ia baliba ko wain, ko oliv…®n temer borem, kar ia faragha inigha izezir dagher kabar naba ia dar am…®. Egh ia danganir kam…®n uan bulmakau ko sipsip…®n nguzir ivariabav sogh, egh dar am…®. Ia kamagh…®n damuva, zurara Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God an atiating…®va an apengan ikiamin arazim…®n fofozim iniam.
\v 24 Ia bar saghon ik…®, egh dagher aghuir Ikiav…®ra Itir God ia gan…®ngizir kaba, ia dar 10plan pozibar da tuiragh dar pozitam inigh danganir a uan ziam f…®s…® m…®s…®vamin kam…®n da ater mangan iburagh,
\v 25 dagher kaba amadaght…® gumazitam dagh ivesegh. Eght…® ia g…®n dag…®ar kaba inigh God…®n ziam fer danganim…®n mang…®.
\v 26 Egh dag…®ar kabar ia bizir ifongezir kabagh ivez, kar bulmakaun tuziba ko sipsip…®n tuziba, wain ko wain…®n d…®par gavgaviba. Egh ia God uan ziam fasa m…®sevezir danganir kam…®n, uan boriba ko Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n damazim…®n, ia dagher kabar am…® egh bar akongegh.
\p 
\v 27 ‚ÄúIa Livaibagh fo, me uari nguazitaba inizir puvat…®. Ian nguibabar aven itir Livaiba, ia dughiar ekiar kabar, me g…®n…®ghn…®gh men akurvagh.
\p 
\v 28 ‚ÄúIa zurara, azenir m…®kezim…®n vaghvagh, uan azenibar otivir dagheba ab…®gh 10plan pozibav k…®nigh, dar pozir vam…®ra inigh mang…® uan nguibar ekiam…®n aven itir dagheba ar…®zir d…®penir ekiabar dar ar…®gh.
\v 29 Livaiba ia me g…®fo, me uari nguazitaba inizir puvat…®. Egha uaghan ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamiziba ko, borir afeziaba ariaghireziba, ko amizir odiarir paba ariaghireziba, me uaghan ia ko iti. Gumazamizir kaba me uaghan iz…® uan ifongiabar dagheba iniam. Ia kamagh…®n damut…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, deragh ia damut…® ian biziba bar derav…®rama otivam.‚Äù
\c 15
\s1 Bizim inigha uam a ikarvaghamin arazim ag…®vamin azenim
\r (Ofa Gami 25:1-7)
\p 
\v 1 Egha Moses ua Israelia m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúNamba 7…®n azenim, kar bizibar ghuavim ikarvazim agevir azenim.\f + \fr 15:1 \ft Arazir kam kamak…®n, gumazitam n…®n dag…®aba inigha akam ak…®ra ghaze, a g…®n ua n…®n dag…®aba ikarvagham. Eght…® azenibar mang…®t…® azenir namba 7 otogh…®va, eght…® n…® a m…®k…®mt…® an a ikarvaghan mark…®.\f*
\v 2 Ia kamagh…®n damu, gumazim uan namakam da pura dag…®am inigh, eght…® azenir namba 7, an namakar kam a m…®k…®m suam, N…® uam a ikaravaghan mark…®. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uab…® kamagh…®n e m…®gei, E dag…®abar ghuaviba, dag…®aba ikarvaghamin os…®mt…®ziba, namba 7…®n azenim…®n, e da g…®n amangam.
\v 3 Eght…® ik…®zir igharazitam…®n gumazitam ia da pura biziba inight…®, ia bizir kaba ikarvaghs…® an d…®m. Egh ia uari uan namakaba inizir biziba ikarvaghs…® men azangan mark…®.
\p 
\v 4 ‚ÄúIa oragh, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, nguazir a dat…®r…®gh…®n ia gan…®dir kabar aven, a deraghv…®ra ia damuam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ian tav, bizitam…®n oteveghan kogham.
\v 5 Ia derav…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n Akar Gavgavir k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia gan…®diba, dar suiragh bar dar g…®n mang…®t…®, a deraghv…®ra ia damuam.
\v 6 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, akam ak…®riz…® mogh…®n, a bar deraghv…®ra ia damuam. Eght…® ik…®zir av…®riba pura ia da biziba iniam, eght…® ia men bizitam puram a inighan kogham. Egh ia ik…®zir av…®ribagh ativagh men gant…®, me ia gativaghan kogham.
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 15:7-8 \xt Ofa Gami 25:35\x*‚ÄúEght…® namakatam, nguazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, dat…®r…®gh…®n ia gan…®dir kam…®n nguibatam…®n ik…®, bizitam…®n otevegham, ia ak…®rim ragh a gasan mark…®. Egh ia uan biziba m…®gh…®n dar suighan mark…®.
\v 8 Ia an apangkuv, egh pura uan dafariba kuigh, bizir an oteveziba ia da is…®va a dan…®ng.
\v 9 Ia kamagh…®n paz…® n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, biziba ikarvaghamin azenim a rogh…®ra izegha g…®fa, egh uan namakam…®n akurvaghs…® uan biziba m…®gh…®n dar suighan mark…®. Egh ia dag…®aba a dan…®ngan aghuaght…®, gumazir kam ian arazir kam bagh Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®k…®m…®va arangt…®, ia God…®n damazim…®n os…®mt…®zim ikiam.
\v 10 A ian azangs…®zir biziba, ia bar da is…® a dan…®ngight…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ian ingangariba bar dar amut…®, da deraghv…®ram otivam.
\v 11 \x - \xo 15:11 \xt Matyu 26:11; Mak 14:7; Jon 12:8\x*E Israelia, en tarazi zurara bizibar otevegham. Ez…® kamagh…®n k…® ghaze, ia onganarazibagh amir gumazamizibar apangkuv men akurvagh deraghv…®ra me damu.‚Äù
\s1 Israelia ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar amuamin arazim
\r (Ua Me Ini 21:1-11)
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 15:12-18 \xt Ofa Gami 25:39-46\x*Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Israelian gumazitam ingangarir gumazir k…®nitam…®n m…®n a givezeght…®, a ian ingangaribar amu mang…®, 6plan azenibar tugh. Egh namba 7…®n azenim…®n, ia aneteght…® a mang…®.
\v 13 Eght…® a ian ingangarim ateght…®, ia pura nguibam…®n anemangan mark…®.
\v 14 Ia bizir aghuir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God ia gan…®ngizir kaba, kar sipsipba, witba, ko wain…®n d…®paba ia da is…® a danight…® a mang…®.
\v 15 Ia uaghan pura ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar m…®n Isip…®n ike. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ua ia iniz…®, ia ua f…®riagh…®re. Ia bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh. K…® bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha Akar Gavgavir kaba ia gan…®ga ia m…®gei.
\p 
\v 16 ‚ÄúEght…® ingangarir gumazir k…®nim suam, ‚ÄòK…® bar uan gumazir dapanim gifuegha, an amuim ko boribagh ifuegha, me atagh…®raghan aghua.‚Äô
\v 17 Eght…® ia a inigh mang…® uan d…®penim…®n ter ararir tiar akam…®n m…®riam…®n itim…®n anesaragh, egh d…®konir tam inigh, an kuarim okoreght…®, a ian ingangarir gumazir k…®nimra ik…® mang…®va ovegham. Ia arazir kamra uan ingangarir amizir k…®nitam, uaghan a damigh.
\p 
\v 18 ‚ÄúIngangarir gumazir k…®nir kam 6plan azenibar ian ingariz…®, ia an ingangarim…®n ivezir muziarim a ganigha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n, ia uan ingangarir gumazir k…®nim damight…® a f…®righ…®r…®ghs…®, bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh os…®man kogham. Ia kamagh…®n damut…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ian ingangaribar amight…® da bar derav…®ram otivam.‚Äù
\s1 Sipsip ko bulmakaun nguzir ivariam
\p 
\v 19 \x - \xo 15:19 \xt Ua Me Ini 13:12\x*Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa uan bulmakauba ko sipsipbar nguzir apurir ivariaba, bar ada m…®sevegh, da is…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, a dan…®ngigh. Eght…® bulmakaun kaba ingangaribar amuan mark…®, egh uaghan ia sipsip…®n kabar ar…®zibagh isan mark…®.
\v 20 Egh ia zurara azenibar vaghvagh uan amuiroghboriba ko, as…®zir kaba inigh, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan ziam f…®s…® m…®s…®vamin danganir kam…®n mang…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n damazim…®n as…®zir kabar am…®.
\v 21 Eght…® bulmakaun kam o sipsip…®n kam…®n m…®karzim ikuvigham, kar an dafarim o an suem ik…®ragham, o an damazimning okavigham, o a ar…®mariar kurar igharazim ikiam, eght…® ia a inigh, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, bagh ofa damuan mark…®.
\v 22 Ia as…®zir atiaba api mogh…®n, uan nguibabara as…®zir kamagh garim am…®va aneg…®fagh. Ia God…®n damazim…®n zue o m…®ze, ia as…®zir kam pura bar anemegh.
\v 23 \x - \xo 15:23 \xt Jenesis 9:4; Ofa Gami 7:26-27; 17:10-14; 19:26; God…®n Araziba 12:16; 12:23\x*Egh ia as…®zir katam…®n ghuzitam bar aneman mark…®. Ia d…®pam…®n m…®n nguazim…®n a fugh.‚Äù
\c 16
\s1 God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam G…®n…®ghn…®ghamin Isam
\r (Ua Me Ini 12:1-20)
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 16:1-8 \xt Ofa Gami 23:5-8; D…®boboniba 28:16-25\x*Egha Moses kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa Abip…®n iak…®nim…®n,\f + \fr 16:1 \ft Abip…®n iak…®nim, kar Israelia iak…®nir faragha zuim. Iak…®nir kam, an en iak…®nimning Mas ko Epril, aning…®n otifi. Iak…®nir kam…®n ziar igharazim, ‚ÄúNisan.‚Äù\f* azenibar zurara isar kam damu. Ia fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God fom…®ra Abip…®n iak…®nim…®n d…®magarir mam…®n, Isip…®n kantrin ua ia ini. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia zurara God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam G…®n…®ghn…®ghamin Isam damuva, bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh an ziam f…®.
\v 2 Ia mang…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uan ziam f…®s…® m…®s…®vamin danganim…®n otivigh, uan bulmakau o sipsip…®n tam m…®suegh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God bagh ofa damu. Egh ia God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam g…®n…®ghn…®gh as…®zir tuzibar am…®.
\v 3 Ia isar kam damu, egh yis itir bret aman mark…®. Ia 7plan aruebara yis puvat…®zir bret am…®. Ia fo, ia fom…®ra zuam…®ra Isip atagh…®raghasa amua yis puvat…®zir bret ame. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia bret…®n kam am…®va, dughiar ia Isip…®n os…®mt…®zim…®n ikia an ategha izezim g…®n…®ghn…®gh. Ia bizir kam zuraram a g…®n…®ghn…®ghv…®ra ik…® mang…®t…® ian ovever dughiam otogham.
\v 4 Yis Puvat…®zir Bret…®n Isam Damuamin Dughiam…®n, ia yis taba ateght…®, da ian d…®penibar ikian mark…®. Egh an aruer faragha zuim…®n, ia ofa damuamin as…®zibar am…® mang…®, d…®magarir kamra bar ada g…®fagh. Eght…® dar naba ik…® mang…® am…®mzaraghan otivan mark…®.
\p 
\v 5 ‚ÄúIa God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam g…®n…®ghn…®ghamin ofa bagh as…®ziba inigh nguibar Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God ia gan…®ditam…®n aven dav soghan mark…®.
\v 6 Ia Israelia Gitazir Dughiam g…®n…®ghn…®ghamin ofa bagh as…®ziba inigh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God uan ziam f…®s…® m…®s…®vamin danganir kamra adav sogh. Ia fo, aruem uaghiri dughiam…®n ia Isip ategha azenan ize. Kamagh…®ra amiz…®, ia guarat…®zim…®n as…®zibav sogh dughiar kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh.
\v 7 Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God uan ziam f…®s…® m…®s…®vamin danganir kamra, as…®zir kaba tu dar am…®. Egh am…®mzaraghan ia uan purirpenibar mang…®.
\v 8 Ia 6plan aruebara yis puvat…®zir bret am…®. Egh namba 7…®n aruem, ia uari akuvagh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God an ziam f…®. Egh dughiar kam…®n ia ingangaritam bar a damuan mark…®.‚Äù
\s1 Azenibar Dagher Igiaba Asiamin Dughiam…®n Isar Ekiam
\r (Ua Me Ini 34:22; Ofa Gami 23:15-21)
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 16:9-12 \xt D…®boboniba 28:26-31\x*Egha Moses me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa azenibar dagher ov…®ziba aghorir aruer faragha zuim…®n ikegh, ia wighba meng mang…® namba 7 wigh…®n tugham.
\v 10 Egh namba 7 wigh…®n aruer abuananam, kar Azenibar Dagher Igiaba Asiamin Dughiam…®n Isar Ekiam. Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God ia gan…®ngizir daghebar d…®bobonim…®n m…®rara, uan ifongiam…®n g…®n mang…®, da tuiragh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God bagh ofa damuva a bagh bar akongegh.
\v 11 Egh ia uan otariba ko guiviba ko, ian ingangarir amiziba ko gumaziba, ko Livaiba ko ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizir ian tong…®n itiba, ko borir afeziaba ariaghireziba ko, amizir paba ariaghireziba, ia bar mogh…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God uan ziam f…®s…® m…®seveghamin danganim…®n mang…®, uari akuvagh an damazim…®n a bagh bar akongegh.
\v 12 Ia fom…®ra pura ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar m…®n Isip…®n ike. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh arazir God ifongeziba deraghv…®ra dar amu.‚Äù
\s1 Averpenibar Ikiamin Dughiar Ekiaba
\r (Ofa Gami 23:33-34)
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 16:13-15 \xt D…®boboniba 29:12-38\x*Egha Moses ua ghaze, ‚ÄúIa azeniba bar, balin afeziba am…®s…®va wain…®n ov…®ziba m…®rm…®right…®, g…®n Averpenibar Ikiamin Dughiar Ekiam otoght…®, ia averpenibar aven ik…® bar akongegh mang…®t…®, aruer namba 7 otogham.
\v 14 Dughiar kam…®n, ia bar mogh…®ra bar akongegham. Ia uan otariba ko guiviba ko, ian ingangarir gumazamiziba ko, Livaiba ko ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizir ian tong…®n itiba, ko borir afeziaba ariaghireziba, ko amizir paba ariaghireziba,
\v 15 ia bar mogh…®ra mang…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uan ziam f…®s…® m…®s…®vamin danganim…®n otifigh. Egh uari akuvagh dughiar ekiar kam damu Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n ziam f…®. God ian azeniba ko bizir maba sara, deraghv…®ra dar amuam, kamagh…®n, ia bizir kam bagh bar akongegh ik…® mang…®t…®, namba 7 aruem otogham.
\p 
\v 16 ‚ÄúEght…® Ia azeniba vaghvagh dar dughiar 3plan, ian gumazibara d…®kavigh, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, uan ziam f…®s…® m…®s…®vamin danganim…®n iz…®, an damazim…®n otivigh an ziam f…®. Dughiar 3plan kaba kamak…®n, Yis Puvat…®zir Bret…®n Isam Damuamin Dughiam, ko Azenibar Dagher Igiaba Asiamin Dughiam…®n Isar Ekiam, ko Averpenibar Ikiamin Dughiar Ekiam. Ia bar vaghvagh dafarir k…®nibar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n izan mark…®.
\v 17 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God bizir aghuir av…®riba ia gan…®ngi. Ia dagh n…®ghn…®gh uan biziba tuiragh a dan…®ng.‚Äù
\s1 Kotiabar araziba
\p 
\v 18 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIan anababa vaghvagh, nguibar Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God ia gan…®dir kabar aven, jasba ko ingangarir gumazir igharazitaba am…®sefegh. Eght…® gumazir kaba guiz…®n arazibar g…®n mang…®, deraghv…®ra gumazamizibar m…®g…®r…®g…®aba tuis…®gh.
\v 19 \x - \xo 16:19 \xt Ua Me Ini 23:6-8; Ofa Gami 19:15\x*E fo, dag…®ar gumaziba jasba apezepera me gan…®diba, da gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba itibagh ami, me damazir okav…®r…®zibar m…®n iti. Egha arazir kam uaghan gumazir aghuarir os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®zibar kotiam gas…®ghas…®si. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazitam me apezeper kotiam gifar…®s…®, dag…®aba me dan…®ngt…®, me dag…®ar kaba inian mark…®. Me guiz…®n arazim g…®ghan mark…®. Me kotiam…®n aven paz…® gumazitam…®n akurvagh…®va, igharazitav d…®kab…®nan kogham. Me guiz…®n arazim…®n g…®n mang…® gumazamiziba bar me tuis…®gham.
\v 20 Ia zurara guiz…®n arazimra g…®n mang…®, egh guizbang…®ra m…®k…®m. Egh ia nguazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ia gan…®dir kam…®n dapiagh ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.
\p 
\v 21 \x - \xo 16:21 \xt Ua Me Ini 34:13\x*‚ÄúEgh ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God bagh ofa gamir dakozim…®n ingar, egh an borogh…®n temer guarir aser amizim Aseran nedazim itim asan mark…®.
\v 22 \x - \xo 16:22 \xt Ofa Gami 26:1\x*Egh ia dag…®ar guarir d…®ghoriba itiba asaragh asem…®n ziam fan mark…®. Bizir kamning bar ikuviz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God bar aning…®n aghua.‚Äù
\c 17
\p 
\v 1 Egha Moses kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa bulmakaun apuritam, o sipsip…®n duatam m…®karzim…®n ititam inigh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God bagh ofa damuan mark…®. Ikiav…®ra Itir God arazir kam bar an aghua.
\p 
\v 2 ‚ÄúEgh dughiar tabar ian nguibar Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God ia gan…®dibar aven, ian tong…®n itir gumazitam o amizitam Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim abigh, kamagh…®n an an damazim…®n arazir kuram gami.
\v 3 \x - \xo 17:3 \xt Ua Me Ini 22:20\x*A Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar Gavgaviba abigh, egh god…®n igharazibar ziaba fam. Kar, aruem ko iak…®nim ko m…®koveziba, a dar ziaba f…® dar g…®n mangam.
\v 4 Ia gumazim o amizir arazir kurar kam gamim…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam baregh, derav…®ra m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim bagh ruiva a batogh. Eght…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam a guizbang…®ra, eght…® ia fogh suam, kar bar arazir kuram Israelian tong…®n oto,
\v 5 eght…® ia gumazir kam o amizir kam inigh nguibam…®n azenan mang…®, dag…®abar a ginivight…® an aremegh.
\v 6 \x - \xo 17:6 \xt D…®boboniba 35:30; God…®n Araziba 19:15; Matyu 18:16; 2 Korin 13:1; 1 Timoti 5:19; Hibru 10:28\x*Egh gumazamizir pumuning o 3pla an gant…®, an arazir kuram damut…®, me an gun m…®keght…®, me dag…®abar a ginivight…® an aremegh.
\v 7 \x - \xo 17:7 \xt 1 Korin 5:13\x*Ia uarir tong…®n arazir kurar kam ag…®vs…®, gumazamizir an gari an arazir kurar kam gamiziba, me faragh dag…®aba is…® a giniv. Eght…® g…®n igharaz darazi dag…®abar a ginivt…® an aremegh.
\p 
\v 8 ‚ÄúDughiar tabar os…®mt…®zir ian nguibabar otiviba bar ekeveght…® jasba da tuis…®ghan iburagham. Os…®mt…®zir kamagh…®n gariba, gumazir mam mam…®n apanim gamigha a m…®soghez…® an areme, gumaziba uan nguaziba ko d…®peniba bagha uarir an…®ngazi, o gumaziba uariv sogha, igharazibar m…®karzibagh as…®ghas…®si. Eght…® jasba bizir kaba tuis…®ghan iburaght…®, ia danganir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uan ziam f…®s…® m…®s…®vamin kamra mang…® an ziam f…®.
\v 9 Egh uan os…®mt…®ziba is…® Livain ofa gamir gumaziba ko, jas…®n dat…®r…®gh…®n kotiaba baraziba, me danight…® me ian os…®mt…®ziba ak…®r.
\v 10 Egh danganir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, m…®seveghamin kam…®n me kot…®n n…®ghn…®ziba ia dan…®ngt…®, ia me m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra bizibar amu.
\v 11 Ia men n…®ghn…®zir me ia gan…®dir kaba inigh, egh bar adar g…®n mang…®.
\v 12 Egh gumazitam jas, o God…®n ofa gamir gumazitam batuegham, ia gumazir kam m…®sueght…® an aremegh. Ia kamagh…®n damuva Israelian arazir kurar kam batuegham.
\v 13 Eght…® gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra arazir kam baregh bar atiatigham. Egh gumazitam uam arazir kamagh garitam damuan kogham.‚Äù
\s1 Atrivim…®n arazibar m…®g…®r…®g…®am
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 17:14 \xt 1 Samuel 8:5\x*Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa nguazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, ia dan…®ngamin kam inigh g…®vagh a dapiagh, egh ia gumazamizir igharazibar m…®n n…®ghn…®gh suam, atrivitam ti e gativagh en ganam.
\v 15 Egh dughiar kam…®n, ia teght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uab…® ian tong…®n atrivim…®n ik…®s…® ian gumazitam am…®sefegh. Ia uan ifongiam…®n gumazitam am…®s…®van mark…®. Ia kantrin igharazitam…®n gumazitam am…®seveght…®, a ian atrivim…®n ikian mark…®. A uab…® ian gumazitam am…®seveght…®, a ian atrivim…®n ik…®.
\v 16 \x - \xo 17:16 \xt 1 Atriviba 10:28; 2 Eghaghaniba 1:16; 9:28\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ghaze, an gumazamiziba ua Isip…®n mangan an aghua. Kamagh…®n, atrivim uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ameght…®, me uam hoziar av…®ribagh ives…® Isip…®n mangan mark…®.
\v 17 \x - \xo 17:17 \xt 1 Atriviba 10:14-22; 10:27; 11:1-8; 2 Eghaghaniba 1:15; 9:27\x*Atrivim amuir av…®ribar ik…®s…® n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, egh uaghan gol ko silvan av…®ribar pozim m…®k…®nan mark…®. Da a damut…®, an ak…®rim ragh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, gasaragham.
\v 18 An atrivim…®n otogh, egh Ak…®nafarir R…®ghizir God…®n Akar Gavgaviba ititam inigh, egh Livaibar damazim…®n an m…®rara ua bagh Ak…®nafarir R…®ghizir igharazir tam…®n deragh an osirigh.
\v 19 An ak…®nafarir r…®ghizir kam uab…®n borogh…®ram anet…®gh, egh dughiabar zurara an akabar gan. Kamagh…®n, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n atiating an Araziba ko, arazir a ifongezibar g…®n mangam.
\v 20 Egh kamagh…®n a uab…® uan ziam fan kogh, egh Israelian igharaz darazi ab…®nan kogham. Egh a God…®n Akar Gavgaviba ategh ighuigh agharir guvim o agharir k…®riam…®n mangan mark…®. A kamagh…®n damu azenir av…®ribar atrivim…®n ikiam. Eght…® g…®n an ovavir boriba an danganim inigh atirivibar otiv mang…®v…®ra ikiam.‚Äù
\c 18
\s1 Ofan naba ofa gamir gumaziba dar amam
\p 
\v 1 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúLivain anabam…®n ofa gamir gumaziba, Israelian marazi nguaziba iniz…® mogh…®n me nguazitam inian kogham. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, m…®kemez…® mogh…®n gumazamiziba uan bizir aghuiba God dan…®ngt…® Livaiba da iniam.
\v 2 \x - \xo 18:2 \xt D…®boboniba 18:20\x*Israelian igharaz darazi, nguaziba isi mogh…®n, me nguazitam inian kogham. Livain anabam, men bizir aghuir Ikiav…®ra Itir God me gan…®ngizim, a kamak…®n, me ofa gamir ingangaribar amuam, mati Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, faragha akam me bagh anek…®riz…® mok…®n.
\p 
\v 3 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam God…®n ofa damus…® bulmakaun apuritam ko sipsip m…®suegh, egh as…®zir kabar gurir tuziba ko, koviam ko akaguar tuziba ko an navir averiam…®n aven itir bizibar tuziba is…®, ofa gamir gumazibar an…®ngigh.
\v 4 Egh ia uan faragha m…®sevezir wit ko balin ov…®ziba, ko wain ko oliv…®n borem ko sipsip…®n ar…®ziba inigh ofa gamir gumazibar an…®ngigh.
\v 5 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ian anababar tong…®n, ofa gamir ingangarim damuasa Livain anabam…®n adarazira, me am…®sefe. Eght…® men ovavir boriba zurara ingangarir kam damu mang…®v…®ra ikiam.
\p 
\v 6 ‚ÄúEght…® Livain gumazitam ifuegh, egh uan nguibar Israel…®n nguazim…®n aven itim ategh mang…®, danganir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, m…®seveghamin kam…®n mangam.
\v 7 Egh a Ikiav…®ra Itir God, an God…®n ofa gamir ingangarim damu, mati ofa gamir gumazir igharaziba zurara Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n ingangarir kam gami mok…®n.
\v 8 Ofa gamir gumaziba vaghvagh dagher magh ghueziba inigh. Egh bizir igharazir a dag…®aba bagh amadazim…®n dag…®aba, a uaghan ua bagh dar suiragh.‚Äù
\s1 God aghuazir arazir bar kurar maba
\p 
\v 9 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa nguazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, ia gan…®dir kam…®n otivigh, egh ik…®zir kabar gumazamiziba amir arazir kurabar g…®n mangan mark…®. Kar arazir bar kurar God aghuaziba.
\v 10-11 \x - \xo 18:10-11 \xt Ua Me Ini 22:18; Ofa Gami 19:26; 19:31\x*Ia uan otariba ko guivibav sogh ofaba tuer dakozim gis…®n avim…®n me tuan mark…®. Egh ia, ariaghirezir gumazamizibar duabar gavgavim…®n amodogh…®n g…®n otivamin bizibar gun m…®geir arazim, ko kukunir gumaziba amir arazim, ko akar mogomebar gun m…®geir arazim, ko akuzibagh amir arazim, ko akavsiabagh amir arazim, ko duar kuraba ko m…®geir arazim, ko imezibagh amir arazim, ko gumazamizir ovengezibar duaba ko m…®geir arazim, ia bar arazir kabar amuan mark…®.
\v 12 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, a gumazamizir arazir kurar kabagh amiba, a bar men aghua. Ez…® gumazamizir ik…®zir igharazir kabar itiba, ia men borogh…®ra izamin dughiam…®n, a bizir kam bang…®n, me batuegham.
\v 13 \x - \xo 18:13 \xt Matyu 5:48\x*Ia arazir kurar kaba bar ada atakigh, egh ia guizbang…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n g…®n mang…®.‚Äù
\s1 God akam inigha izir gumaziba amangasa akam ak…®ri
\p 
\v 14 Egha Moses ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazamizir ia dat…®r…®gh…®n men nguazim iniasava amir kaba, me kukunir gumazibar akaba baragha dar g…®n ghua, duar kurabar arazibagh ami. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, arazir kabar amuan ian anogoroke.
\p 
\v 15 \x - \xo 18:15 \xt Aposel 3:22; 7:37\x*‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, a ian tong…®n, ia bagh gumazitam am…®seveght…®, a nan m…®n akam inigha izir gumazim…®n otogham. Eght…® ia an akaba baragh dar g…®n mangam.
\p 
\v 16 ‚ÄúIa Sainain M…®ghs…®am…®n borogh…®n uari akuvagha itir dughiam…®n, ia bar atiatigha, kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, ‚ÄòE Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God an ganigh ar…®m…®ghiregham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, e uam an tiarim baraghan aghua. Egha e uaghan avir ekiar God aven itir kam…®n ganan aghua.‚Äô
\v 17 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, na m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòMen m…®g…®r…®g…®am, bar guizbang…®ra.
\v 18 K…® men tong…®n men tav am…®sevegham, eght…® a n…®n m…®n, akam inigha izir gumazim…®n otogham. Eght…® k…® uan akam is…® a danight…® an akar k…® dan…®ngamiba bar da is…® gumazamiziba bar me m…®k…®mam.
\v 19 \x - \xo 18:19 \xt Aposel 3:23\x*Eght…® akam inigha izir gumazir kam nan ziamra akam akunam. Eght…® gumazamizir an akam batoziba, k…® ivezir kuram me dan…®ngam.
\v 20 Eght…® akam inigha izir gumazitam, nan akar k…® a gan…®ngizir puvat…®zitam akunam, o a asetam…®n ziam…®n gun m…®k…®mam, an ovengam.‚Äô
\p 
\v 21 ‚ÄúEght…® ia manmagh fogh suam, ‚ÄòAkam inigha izir gumazir kam…®n akar a kurir kam, a ti Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n izi, o puvat…®?‚Äô
\v 22 Ia akar a kurir kam kamagh…®n a g…®fogh. Akam inigha izir gumazir kam Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam…®n akam akunt…®, bizir a m…®kemezim otoghan koght…®, akar a m…®geir kam Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n izezir puvat…®. Akam inigha izir gumazir kam uan n…®ghn…®zim…®n akam akuri. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia an atiatingan mark…®.‚Äù
\c 19
\s1 Nguibar ekiar gumazamiziba // ar…® mang…® mongamiba
\r (D…®boboniba 35:9-28; Josua 20:1-9)
\p 
\v 1 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, nguazir ia gan…®dir kam…®n ik…®ziba bar me gas…®ghsigh g…®vagh, men nguibaba ko d…®peniba bar ada inigham. Eght…® ia deraghv…®ra dar apiagh,
\v 2-3 egh nguazir kam 3plan distrighbar da b…®kigh. Egh distrigh…®n kabar vaghvagh mongamin nguibar ekiatam am…®sefegh, eght…® nguibar ekiar kaba, da danganir gumazamiziba ar…®mang…® derav…®ra ikiamba. Egh tuavibar ingaright…®, da nguibar ekiar kabar mang…® dar otifigh. Eght…® gumazamiziba tuavir kabar ar…® mang…® nguibar ekiar kabar otivigh derav…®ra ikiam. Eght…® g…®n gumazitam igharazitav purama a m…®sueght…® an aremeght…®, a mang…® nguibar kabar tam…®n aven mang…® modogh ikiam.
\v 4 Gumazim uan anav…®ra os…®mt…®ziba an puvat…®gh purama a m…®sueght…® an aremeght…®, an ar…® mang…® nguibar ekiar 3plan kabar tam…®n mang…®gh deraghv…®ra ikiam.
\v 5 Egha uaghan, gumazir pumuning ruarim…®n temeba oka ghua, mav…®n sobiam asiaghir…®gha an namakam m…®soghez…® an areme, an ar…® mang…® mongamin nguibar ekiar katam…®n aven man…®gh deragh ikiam.
\v 6 Eght…® mongamin nguibar ekiar vam…®ra ik…®, kamagh…®n deraghan kogham. Nguibar ekiar vam…®ra ik…® bar saghon mar ik…®t…®, gumazim uan anav…®n ovevem ikarvaghs…®, bar an…®ngaghegh pamtem ar…®mangamin gumazir kam…®n g…®nt…®gh, tuavim…®n puram an suiragh a m…®sueght…® an aremegham. Gumazir kam, guizbang…®ra, os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®. A uan anav…®n apanim gamua a m…®soghez…® an aremezir puvat…®. Sobiamrama asiaghir…®gha anem…®soghez…® an areme.
\v 7 Bizir m…®ngarir kam bagha k…® mongamin nguibar ekiar 3pla am…®s…®vasa ia m…®keme.
\p 
\v 8 ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, a nguazir kabar m…®taghniabagh is…®vagh, nguazir ekiaba is…® ia dan…®ngam, mati a fom…®ra ian inazir afeziaba ko akam ak…®riz…® mok…®n.
\v 9 Eght…® ia dughiar kam…®n mongamin nguibar ekiar 3pla uam ada am…®sefegh. Egh Akar Gavgavir k…® ia m…®kemeziba bar a dar amu, egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ia bar a gifongegh, zurara an arazibar g…®n mang…®t…®, a nguazir ekiar kaba bar ada is…® ia dan…®ngt…®, ia ua mongamin nguibar ekiar 3pla uam ada am…®sefegh.
\v 10 Egh ia nguazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ia gan…®dir kam…®n ik…®, egh gumazir os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®zir tam m…®sueght…® an aremeghan mark…®, egh ia os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®gham.
\p 
\v 11 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam bar uan namakam…®n aghuagh, egh modogh ik…®va, egh a m…®sueght…® an aremeght…®, ana ar…® mongs…® mang…® mongamin nguibar ekiar kabar tam…®n aven mang…®ght…®,
\v 12 an nguibam…®n gumazir dapaniba, nguibar ekiar a ghua modozim…®n gumazir dapanibar azaraght…® me uam anemadaght…®, a uan nguibam…®n iz…®. Eght…® me uam a is…® gumazir aremezim…®n adarazir dafarim dat…®ght…®, me a ikaragh a m…®sueght…® an aremegh.
\v 13 Ia an apangkuvan mark…®. Bar mark…®. Israelian aven gumazir os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®ziba pura me m…®sozi me ariaghirir arazim iti. Ia kamagh…®n damu egh os…®mt…®zir kam ag…®vagh derav…®ra ikiam.‚Äù
\s1 Ababanir Israelia fom…®ra uan nguazibar m…®taghniabar at…®ziba
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 19:14 \xt God…®n Araziba 27:17\x*Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God ia gan…®dir nguazir kaba, me fom…®ra dar m…®taghniaba arigha dar abaraz…® da kamagh…®ra iti. Eght…® ia uan namakabar nguazir m…®taghniaba ua dagh is…®vagh mangan mark…®.‚Äù
\s1 Kotiam…®n aven gumazitam os…®mt…®zim is…® gumazir igharazim gasan mark…®
\p 
\v 15 \x - \xo 19:15 \xt D…®boboniba 35:30; God…®n Araziba 17:6; Matyu 18:16; Jon 8:17; 2 Korin 13:1; 1 Timoti 5:19; Hibru 10:28\x*Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir vam…®ra gari, gumazir igharazim arazir kuram gamiz…®, a kotiam…®n aven bizir kam…®n gun m…®gei, eght…® gumazir kotiam barazim, gumazir kam…®n akam baraghan mark…®. Eght…® gumazir arazir kuram…®n gara an gun m…®geibar d…®bobonim, a gumazir pumuning o pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n ik…®t…®, ia gumazir kam is…® kot dat…®ght…®, gumazir kaba an gun kotiam m…®k…®mam.
\p 
\v 16 ‚ÄúEgh gumazitam, gumazir igharazim gas…®ghas…®ghs…® a gifar suam, an arazir kuram gami,
\v 17 egh aning v…®rara God…®n ziam fer danganimra mang…®gh. Eght…® ofa gamir gumaziba ko jas…®n dat…®r…®gh…®n ingangarir kam gamiba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n aning…®n akaba tuis…®gham.
\v 18 Egh jasba deraghv…®ram aning…®n akaba tuis…®gh. Egh me deragh fogh suam, gumazir uan namakam isa kot gat…®zim a ifara pura akam a gasi,
\v 19 eght…® ia ivezir kuram is…® gumazir kotiam gifara m…®geim dan…®ng, mati ivezir kurar a uab…® uan namakam dan…®ngasa ifongezim. Ia kamagh…®n damu, egh arazir kurar kam uarir tong…®n a batokegh.
\v 20 Eght…® gumazamiziba bar bizir kam…®n akam bar a baregh atiatigh, egh deragh uari bagh ganam. Eght…® gumazitam uam arazir kamagh…®ra garitam damuan kogham.
\v 21 \x - \xo 19:21 \xt Ua Me Ini 21:23-25; Ofa Gami 24:19-20; Matyu 5:38\x*Ia ifavarir gumazitam…®n apangkuvan mark…®. A uan anav…®ra aremeghs…® a ifongegham, a uab…® uaghan aremegham. Egh a uan anav…®n damazim, o atarim, o agharim o suem gas…®ghas…®ghs…® ifongeght…®, me uaghan kamagh…®ram a ikaragh.‚Äù
\c 20
\s1 M…®dorozibar araziba
\p 
\v 1 Egha Moses m…®g…®a ghuav…®ra ikia ghaze, ‚ÄúIa uan apaniba ko m…®sogh mang…® gant…® men karisba ko hoziaba, ko men m…®dorozir gumaziba, ian d…®bobonim gafiraght…®, ia men atiatingan mark…®. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n Isip…®n ia inigha ian akua izezim, a ia ko iti.
\v 2 Ia m…®dorozim fors…® ofa gamir gumazitam faragh iz…® m…®dorozir gumazibar guam…®n tugh kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m,
\v 3 ‚ÄòO Israelia, ia oragh. Ia m…®dorozim bagh dat…®r…®gh…®n mangam. Egh ia mang…® apanibar gan…®va atiating aghariba ian am…®raght…® ia okam n…®ghn…®gh puram akongan mark…®.
\v 4 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, a ia ko zui. A m…®dorozir kam…®n aven ik…® ian akuragh m…®soght…®, ia uan apaniba ab…®nigham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia atiatingan mark…®.‚Äô
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 20:5-7 \xt Luk 14:18-20\x*‚ÄúEght…® m…®dorozir gumazibar dapaniba kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòGumazitaba ti kagh ikia d…®penir igiabar ingarigha, egh deragh dar amus…® t…®ghar God ko m…®k…®mam? Gumazir kamagh…®n amiba ik…®, egh uamategh d…®penibar mang…®. Me m…®dorozim…®n oveght…®, gumazir igharaziba men d…®penir igiaba iniam.
\v 6 Ez…® gumazitaba ti kagh ikia wain…®n azenir igiaba oparigha, egh dar wain…®n d…®paba t…®ghar da iniam? Gumazir kamagh…®n amiba ik…®, egh uamategh uan d…®penibar mang…®. Me m…®dorozim…®n oveght…®, gumazir igharaziba men wain…®n ov…®zir igiaba iniam.
\v 7 Ez…® gumazitaba ti kagh ikia uari bagh amuibagh inamigha, egh t…®ghar men ikiam? Gumazir kamagh…®n amiba ik…®, egh uamategh uan nguibabar mang…®. Me m…®dorozim…®n oveght…®, gumazir igharaziba men amuibar ikiam.‚Äô
\p 
\v 8 ‚ÄúEgh m…®dorozir gumazibar dapaniba ua kamagh…®n, uan m…®dorozir gumazibav k…®m suam, ‚ÄòGumazitaba ti kagh ikia m…®soghan atiatia egha agoa ikiama? Ian tina kagh ikia kamagh…®n ami, a uamategh uan nguibam…®n mang…®. A kamagh…®n damu m…®dorozir gumazir igharazibar amut…®, me uaghan atiatingam.‚Äô
\v 9 Egh me m…®dorozir gumazibav kemegh g…®vagh, egh me m…®dorozir gumazir okoruabar faragh mangamin gumazir dapaniba am…®sefegh.
\p 
\v 10 ‚ÄúIa d…®vazir gavgavim av…®nizir nguibar ekiatam ko m…®soghs…® an borogh…®ra mang…®, egh faragh nguibar kam…®n itir gumazamiziba kamagh me m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòM…®doroziba markiam. Ia uan nguibam is…® puram en dafarim dat…®gh.‚Äô
\p 
\v 11 ‚ÄúEght…® me ian akam…®n amamangat…®gh, egh ia bagh d…®vazibar tiar akar ekiaba kuigh, egh ian apengan ik…® kalabuziar gumazamizibar m…®n pura ingangarim damu.
\v 12 Egh nguibar ekiar kam…®n gumazamiziba ian amamangat…®ghan kogh, ia ko m…®soghs…® damut…®, ian m…®dorozir gumaziba nguibar ekiar kam av…®nizir d…®vazir gavgavim bar anek…®arugh.
\v 13 Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, ian amamangat…®ght…®, ia nguibar ekiar kam iniam. Ia a inigh g…®vagh, an aven itir gumazibara, bar me m…®sueght…® me ar…®m…®ghiregh.
\v 14 Ikiav…®ra Itir God nguibar ekiar kam ia ganigha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia nguibar kam…®n amiziba, ko boriba ko bulmakauba ko as…®zir igharaziba, ko uan apanibar bizir igharazir nguibar kam…®n itiba sara, ia uari bagh da inigh.
\v 15 Ia kamagh…®ra nguibar ekiar ian nguazim…®n saghon itibar amu. Nguibar ekiar kaba, da ian borogh…®n itir ik…®zibar nguibaba puvat…®.
\p 
\v 16 ‚ÄúEgh ia nguazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ia dan…®ngamin kam…®n nguibatam inigh g…®vagh, egh an itir gumazamiziba ko as…®ziba sara bar dav sueght…® da ar…®m…®ghiregh.
\v 17 Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God ia m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, Hitia ko Amoria, Kenania, ko Peresia, Hivia ko Jebusia, ia bar me kuavaremegh.
\v 18 Ia bar me m…®sueght…® me ar…®ghireght…® deragham. Me ik…® uan arazir kurar uan asebar ziaba fava amir arazibar ian sure damuam. Me kamagh…®n damu ia gekut…®, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God ategh, arazir kurar a bar aghuazibar amuam.
\p 
\v 19 ‚ÄúIa nguibatam inis…® m…®sogh dughiar bar ruarim…®n anev…®nigh ik…®, egh sobiabar nguibar kam…®n borogh…®n itir temer beba okan mark…®. Temeba ian apaniba puvat…®. Ia dar ov…®zibar amam, egh dagh as…®ghas…®ghan mark…®.
\v 20 Egh ia temer igharaziba ok…®va uarir akurvagh m…®soghamin bizibar ingarigh m…®dorozim damu apaniba ab…®nigh, egh nguibar kam uari bagh a iniam.‚Äù
\c 21
\s1 Gumazir purama ariagh…®ribar os…®mt…®zim ak…®ramin arazim
\p 
\v 1 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa gumazir kuatam…®n gant…® a nguazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God ia gan…®dim…®n danganitam…®n ir…®gh…®v ik…®t…®, ia foghan kogham, tina a m…®soghez…® ana areme,
\v 2 eght…® ia kamagh…®n damu. Ian gumazir dapaniba ko jasba mang…®, nguazir gumazir kuam ir…®ghav itim ko nguibar an borogh…®ra itibar tizim…®n ababanim damu ganigh.
\v 3 Eght…® kuar kam…®n borogh…®ra itir nguibar kamra, an gumazir dapaniba, me bulmakaun amebar igiar ingangaritam gamizir puvat…®zitam am…®sefegh.
\v 4 Egh me bulmakaun kam inigh faner datir puvat…®zim…®n borogh…®ra mang…®. Egh nguazir otevir gumazitam an ingarizir puvat…®gha, bizitam akaraz…® puvat…®zim…®n, bulmakaun kam…®n tuem ap…®righ.
\v 5 Livain anabam…®n ofa gamir gumaziba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, uan ingangarim damuasa me am…®sevez…®, ingangarir kam iti, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam…®n gun gumazamizibav k…®mt…®, God deragh me damuam. Eght…® gumazim igharazitav m…®sueght…® an aremeght…®, me an kotiam baragham. Kamagh…®n, me uaghan d…®kavigh danganir kam…®n mang…®.
\v 6 Eght…® gumazir kuam iti nagh…®n an borogh…®ra itir nguibar kam…®n gumazir dapaniba, me d…®pam inigh uan dafariba bulmakaun kuam gis…®n da ruegh.
\v 7 Egh me kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòE gumazir kam m…®soghez…® an aremezir puvat…®. E an ovevem…®n ganizir puvat…®gha a m…®soghezir gumazitam g…®fozir puvat…®.
\v 8 O Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® Isip…®n kantrin en akuragha uam e inigha ize, ez…® e Israelia e n…®n gumazamizibara. N…® en arazir kuraba g…®n amadagh. Gumazir kam os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®z…®, me purama a m…®soghez…® an areme. Eght…® n…® an ovever kam…®n os…®mt…®zim ateght…® an en tong…®n ikian markiam.‚Äô Eght…® kamagh…®ra God gumazir kam…®n ghuzim…®n os…®mt…®zim, ag…®vagham.
\v 9 Kamagh…®n, ia uarir tong…®n os…®mt…®zir kam batogh, egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir aghuim damight…®, a suam, Gumazir kam…®n ovevem…®n os…®mt…®zim, a ian itir puvat…®.‚Äù
\s1 Israelia m…®dorozim…®n aven inizir amiziba
\p 
\v 10 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa apanibav soghs…® mang…®t…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ian akuraght…® ia m…®dorozim…®n uan apaniba ab…®nigh, men tarazi is…® ia uan ingangaribar amus…®, kalabuziabar m…®n ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar me at…®gh.
\v 11 Eght…® ian tav men tong…®n amizir dirir aghuitam…®n ganigh an ik…®s…® n…®ghn…®gham.
\v 12-13 Egh n…® amizim inigh uan d…®penim…®n mang…®. Egh aneteght…®, a uan afeziam ko amebam bagh azi mang…® bar uan dapanir ar…®ziba ap…®righ, uan dafarir puzibar ghoregh, egh kalabuziam…®n m…®n ingangarir amizir k…®nim…®n itir dughiam…®n aghuizir korotiaba suegh, iak…®nir vam…®ra n…®n d…®penim…®n ik…®va azi. Eght…® n…® g…®n an ik…®.
\v 14 N…® a inigh izegh a ko dakuigh g…®vagh, egh dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® kamagh…®n a g…®n…®ghn…®ghan kogham, a pura nan ingangarir amizir k…®nim. Egh n…® anemadaght…® gumazitam a givezan kogham. N…® an aghuagh, egh aghums…®zir ekiam a dan…®ngam. Kamagh…®n, n…® puram anemadaght…® a f…®righ…®r…®gh mang…®.‚Äù
\s1 Afeziam aremeght…® otarir ivariam biziba iniam
\p 
\v 15 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei ‚ÄúGumazitam amuir pumuning…®n ik…®, tam bar a gifuegh, igharazim…®n aghuagham. Eght…® amuir a bar ifongezir puvat…®zim faragh a bagh otarir ivariam bateght…®, g…®n amuir igharazim uaghan otarim bategham.
\v 16 Eght…® g…®n gumazir kam uan biziba tuiragh boribar an…®ngs…® n…®ghnigh, biziba is…® amuir a bar ifongezim…®n otarir ivariam dan…®ng…®va, egh amuir an aghuazim…®n otarir ivariam…®n anogoroghan mark…®. Bar markiam.
\v 17 Otarir ivariaba zurara biziba isi mogh…®n, afeziam uan biziba abigh 3plan pozibav k…®nigh, egh pozir pumuning is…® guiz…®n otarir ivariam dan…®ngigh. Guizbang…®ra, otarir ivariar kam…®n amebam, an pam deragha a gifongezir puvat…®, ez…® otarir kam, kar gumazir kam…®n faraghav…®ram otozir otarim. Kamagh…®n, an otarir ivariam…®n m…®n afeziam…®n biziba iniam.‚Äù
\s1 Borir akam batogheziba
\p 
\v 18 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam otarir tam ik…®t…®, otarir kam zurara akaba batogh amebam ko afeziam…®n akaba baragh dar g…®n mangan koght…®, me ivezir kuram a dan…®ngt…®, a uaghan aning bareghan kogham.
\v 19 Eght…® an amebam ko afeziam a inigh uan nguibar ekiam…®n gumazir dapaniba bagh mang…®t…®, me a is…® kot dat…®gh.
\v 20 Egh an amebam ko afeziam gumazir dapanibav k…®m suam, ‚ÄòGan otarim akaba batogha gan akaba barazir puvat…®. A zurara puv…®ra apava, wain…®n d…®paba apa onganighav arui.‚Äô
\v 21 Eght…® dat…®r…®gh…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumaziba dag…®aba is…®va a giniv…®ra ik…®t…® an aremegh. Ia kamagh…®n damu, arazir kurar kam batueght…®, a ian tong…®n ikian kogham. Eght…® Israelian gumazamiziba bar bizir kam…®n ganigh egh atiatingam.‚Äù
\s1 Akar Gavgavir maba
\p 
\v 22 Egha Moses ua kamagh m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam arazir bar kuram damut…®, bizir kam bagh me a m…®sueght…® an aremegh, eght…® me an kuam is…® temem…®n aneguragham,
\v 23 \x - \xo 21:23 \xt Josua 10:26-27; Jon 19:31; Galesia 3:13\x*eght…® me an kuam ateght…®, a guragh ik…® mang…®t…® am…®nim dutughan mark…®. Gumazir ter ighuvim…®n duiba God ghaze, me gumazir kuraba. Ia gumazir kuam an aremezir aruemram a inigh mang…® mozim dat…®gh. Puvat…®ght…®, nguazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God ia gan…®dir kam an damazim…®n bar m…®zegham.‚Äù
\c 22
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 22:1-4 \xt Ua Me Ini 23:4-5\x*‚ÄúEgh ia uan namakam…®n bulmakau o sipsip…®n gant…® a d…®vazim ategh azenan pura tintinibar darut…®, ia aneteght…® a kamagh…®ra daruan kogham. Puvat…®. Ia uam a inigh namakar kam bagh mang…®.
\v 2 Eght…® bulmakau o sipsip…®n ghuavim…®n d…®penim bar saghon ik…®t…®, o ia foghan kogham, kar tinan bulmakau ko sipsip, eght…® ia a inigh uan d…®penim…®n mang…®. Eght…® g…®n, bulmakaun o sipsip…®n kam…®n ghuavim a buri iz…®t…®, ia a dan…®ngigh.
\v 3 Egh ia uan namakam…®n donki, o an nir av…®zim, o an bizir igharazibar apigh, arazir kamra damuva, an akurvagham.
\p 
\v 4 ‚ÄúEght…® ian namakam…®n donki, o bulmakaun tam tuavim…®n ir…®gh…®v ik…®t…®, ia aneteght…® a kamagh…®ra ikian mark…®. Puvat…®. Ia uan namakam…®n akuragh uam a feght…® a tugh.
\p 
\v 5 ‚ÄúEght…® amiziba, gumazibar korotiabar aghuan mark…®. Eght…® gumaziba, amizibar korotiabar aghuan mark…®. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, gumazamizir arazir kabagh amiba, me gifongezir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®.
\p 
\v 6 ‚ÄúEght…® ia kuarazir m…®konitam…®n gant…® a temem…®n ikiam, o nguazim…®n ikiam, eght…® kuarazir amebam aroriabagh is…®n ikiam, o nguziba ko ik…®t…®, ia kuarazir amebar kam inian mark…®.
\v 7 Ia uari bagh kuarazir nguziba iniva, kuarazir amebam ateght…® a mang…®. Ia kamagh…®n damuva dughiar ruarim…®n nguazir kam…®n ik…®t…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, bizir aghuir av…®riba ia dan…®ngam.
\p 
\v 8 ‚ÄúEgh ia d…®penir igiam…®n ingar, egh d…®penim…®n p…®n itir avughsamin danganim…®n m…®riabar, b…®rir oteviba asegh. Eght…® g…®n gumazitam an ik…® nguazim gir…®gh aremeghan kogham, kamagh…®n ia os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®gham.
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 22:9-11 \xt Ofa Gami 19:19\x*‚ÄúIa wain…®n azenim…®n aven dagher igharazitaba oparan mark…®. Ia kamagh…®n damigh, wain…®n ikar…®zibar ov…®ziba ko dagher igharaziba sara dar aman mark…®. Ia bar ada inigh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n mang…®, a dan…®ngigh.
\p 
\v 10 ‚ÄúIa uan azenim…®n ingars…®, ia bulmakau ko donki v…®rara uaning gikeght…®, aning nguazim ab…®zir ain…®n otevim kurvaghan mark…®.
\p 
\v 11 ‚ÄúMarazi tret…®n sipsip…®n ar…®zibar r…®ghiziba ko tret…®n bizir igharazir aghuibar r…®ghiziba, v…®rara da isa iniba nuavigha korotiaba isami, ez…® ia korotiar kabar aghuan mark…®.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 22:12 \xt D…®boboniba 15:37-41\x*‚ÄúIa tret…®n dueviar d…®g…®rir aghuiba itiba inigh korotiar ruarim…®n 4plan m…®kebabar puegh ada isamigh.‚Äù
\s1 Gumazamiziba God…®n damazim…®n zuezir arazibar amu
\p 
\v 13 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam amuim…®n ik…®va, a ko dakuigh, egh g…®n an aghuagh,
\v 14 egh g…®n ifar puram akaba a gas…® ak…®rim ragh a gasaragham. Egh kamagh m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòK…® amizir kam…®n ikia, egha fo, a faragha gumazir igharazim koma akui.‚Äô
\p 
\v 15 ‚ÄúGumazir kam kamagh…®n damight…®, guivir kam…®n amebam ko afeziam inir a gumazim koma avaragha akuizim inigh nguibar ekiam…®n tiar akam…®n mang…®, gumazir dapanibar akagh. Eght…® me uari inir kam…®n ganigh fogham, a faragha gumazitam koma akuizir puvat…®.
\v 16 Eght…® amizim…®n afeziam kamagh…®n gumazir dapanibav k…®m, ‚ÄòK…® uan guivim isa gumazir kam gan…®ngiz…® an an iti. Egha a dat…®r…®gh…®n akar ifavaribar a gamuava an aghua.
\v 17 Egha gumazir kam a gifara a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAmizir k…® itir kam k…® kamagh…®n a g…®fo, a faragha gumazir igharazir mam koma akuava arazir m…®z…®r…®zibagh ami.‚Äù Ez…® ia inir avagha akuir kam…®n gant…®, a ian akagh suam, nan guivim gumazitam ko akuiz, o puvat…®.‚Äô Egha a inir kam gumazir dapanibar damazim…®n nguazim…®n a ghuara.
\v 18 Eght…® gumazir dapaniba amizir kam…®n pam inigh ivezir kuram…®n m…®n benir gavgavim…®n a ifozorogh.
\v 19 Gumazir kam, Israelian amizir igiar aghuir mam aghums…®zim a gan…®ngi. Kamagh…®n, gumazir kam 1,000 kina is…®va guivir kam…®n afeziam dan…®ngigh. Eght…® amizir kam gumazir kam…®n amuimra ik…® mang…® aremegham. Eght…® gumazir kam uam a batoghan mark…®. Bar mark…®.
\p 
\v 20 ‚ÄúEght…® inir avagha akuir guivim…®n afeziam akazir kam, guizbang…®ra an arazir aghuir an amizim…®n gun m…®k…®man koght…®,
\v 21 eght…® nguibam…®n gumazir dapaniba amizim inigh an afeziam…®n d…®penim…®n tiar akam…®n azenan mang…®t…®, an nguibam…®n gumazibara dag…®abar a giniv mang…®t…® an aremegh. A bar aghums…®zir arazir kuram en gumazamizibar tong…®n a gami. A poroghamim gamizir puvat…®zir dughiam…®n uan afeziam…®n d…®penim…®n ikia tintinibar gumazir maba koma akua arazir kuram gami. Ia kamagh…®n damu egh ia arazir kurar kam ag…®vagham.
\p 
\v 22 ‚ÄúEgh ia gant…®, gumazim, gumazir igharazim…®n amuim ko dakuight…®, ia v…®raram aning m…®sueght…® aning aremegh. Ia kamagh…®n damu egh Israelian tong…®n arazir kurar kam ag…®vagham.
\p 
\v 23 ‚ÄúEgh ia gant…®, gumazitam amizir me gumazir igharazim…®n ikiasa a bagh inabazim, nguibar ekiam…®n aven a batogh a ko arazir kuram damight…®,
\v 24 ia aning inigh nguibam…®n azenan mang…®, dag…®abar aning ginivight…® aning aremegh. Amizim nguibar ekiam…®n aven ikia, uab…®n akurvaghasa deir puvat…®, kamagh…®n a uaghan aremegham. Gumazir kam amizir me pam…®n ikiasa m…®sevezim ko arazir aghums…®zibagh ami. Kamagh…®n an aremegham. Ia kamagh…®n damu egh ian tong…®n itir arazir kurar kam ag…®vagham.
\p 
\v 25 ‚ÄúEght…® amizir me pam…®n ikiasa inabazim, a nguibam…®n borogh…®n ikian koght…®, gumazitam an suiragh arazir kurabar a damight…®, me gumazir kamra m…®sueght…® an aremegh.
\v 26 Arazir kurar kam, a gumazim gumazir igharazim m…®soghez…®, an aremezir arazim ko magh ghu. Amizim uab…®, ovevem iniamin arazir kuratam gamizir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia bizitam…®n amizim damuan mark…®.
\v 27 Gumazir kam nguibam…®n azenan arazir kuram…®n amizir kam gami. Ez…® amizim uab…®n akurvaghasa deima, akurvaghamin gumazamizitaba ikezir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 28 \x - \xo 22:28-29 \xt Ua Me Ini 22:16-17\x*‚ÄúEght…® ia gant…® gumazitam amizir igiar me patam…®n ikiasa inabazir puvat…®zitam…®n suiragh a ko dakuigh,
\v 29 an amizir kam…®n afeziam 500 kinan a givezegh, egh amizim…®n ikiam. Gumazir kam, amizir kam…®n suiragha arazir kuram a koma a gami. Kamagh…®n, gumazim amizir kam a batueghan kogham. Amizir kam an ik…® mang…®, an aremeghamin dughiam…®n tugham.
\p 
\v 30 \x - \xo 22:30 \xt Ofa Gami 18:8; 20:11; God…®n Araziba 27:20\x*‚ÄúEght…® gumazim uan afeziam…®n amuim…®n ikian kogh, a ko daku arazir kuram…®n a damuan mark…®. A kamagh…®n damu, aghums…®zir ekiam is…® uan afeziam dan…®ngam.‚Äù
\c 23
\s1 Gumazamizir taba, God…®n gumazamizibar tong…®n ikian kogham
\p 
\v 1 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam, me an m…®karzir mogomem am…®sararigham, o bar anetught…®, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gumazamizibar tong…®n ikian kogham.
\p 
\v 2 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam, amizim ko uaning…®n itir puvat…®gha, a koma akua borim a gan…®ngi, eght…® amizim oteghamin borir kam, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gumazamizibar tong…®n ikian kogham. Eght…® an ovavir borir g…®n otivamiba me uaghan zurara Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gumazamizibar tong…®n ikian kogham.
\p 
\v 3 \x - \xo 23:3-5 \xt Nehemia 13:1-2\x*‚ÄúEght…® Amonia ko, Moapia ko, men ovavir borir g…®n otivamiba, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gumazamizibar aven ikian kogham.
\v 4 \x - \xo 23:4 \xt D…®boboniba 22:1-6\x*Bizir kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n. E Isip atagh…®razir dughiam, me daghetaba ko d…®pataba inigha iza en akurazir puvat…®. Me Balam givese, eght…® a God ko m…®k…®mt…®, an e gas…®ghas…®gham. Balam a Beor…®n otarim, egha Aram…®n nguazim…®n itir nguibar ekiam Petor…®n gumazim.
\v 5 \x - \xo 23:5 \xt D…®boboniba 23:7--24:9\x*Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, Balam…®n akam baraghizir puvat…®. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, bar ia gifonge. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a ian akurvaghasa an akar kurar an e gamizir kam g…®raz…®, a ghua akar aghuim…®n oto.
\v 6 Kamagh…®n, ia zurara gumazamizir kaba deragh ik…® biziba bar av…®rasemeghs…®, ia men akurvaghan mark…®.
\v 7 Eght…® Idomia ko Isipia, ia ko ik…®t…®, ia paz…® me g…®n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®. Guizbang…®ra, Idomia ian ik…®zibar m…®n iti. Ia fom…®ra, gumazamizir pura guighav itibar m…®n Isip…®n kantrin ike, kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia men aghuaghan mark…®.
\v 8 Eght…® men g…®n otivamin az…®ziba, merara Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gumazamizibar tong…®n ikiamin tuavim iti.‚Äù
\s1 M…®dorozir gumaziba itir danganim, God…®n damazim…®n zuegh ik…®
\p 
\v 9 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa m…®dorozim bagh mangamin dughiam, ian m…®dorozir gumaziba arazir kuraba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n me itir danganim…®n dar amuan mark…®.
\v 10 Eght…® gumazitam d…®mangan daku mang…® irebam…®n gant…®, d…®pam an m…®karzir mogomem…®n otoght…®, a danganir me itim ategh, azenan mang…®gh ik…®.
\v 11 Egh guarat…®zim…®n a mang…® deragh ruegh, eght…® aruem mag…®r…®ght…®, a ua danganir me itim…®n aven iz…®.
\p 
\v 12 ‚ÄúEght…® m…®dorozir gumaziba m…®s…®gh daviam…®n danganim, danganir me itim…®n azenan ik…®.
\v 13 Egh m…®dorozir gumaziba davis…® azenan mang…® uari bagh toribagh kus…® itaziba inigh da sara mang…®. Egh me torim g…®kuigh, egh davigh g…®vagh ua torim apemegh.
\v 14 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, zurara ia ko ia itir danganim…®n ik…®, egh ian akurvaght…® ia uan apaniba ab…®nam. Kamagh…®n, ia itir danganim God…®n damazim…®n zurara zuegh ik…®. Ia God…®n damazim…®n bizitam damight…® a God…®n damazim…®n m…®zeght…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ak…®rim ragh ia gasaragham.‚Äù
\s1 Arazir igharazir maba
\p 
\v 15 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIngangarir gumazir k…®nitam pura uan gumazir dapanim…®n ar…® mang…®, iz…® uab…®n akurvaghs…® ian azangs…®gham, eght…® ia uam an gumazir dapanim bagh anemangan mark…®.
\v 16 Egh a mang…® ian nguibatam…®n ik…®s…® ifuegh, a mang…®. Ia paz…®va a damuan mark…®.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 23:17 \xt Ofa Gami 19:29\x*‚ÄúIsraelian gumazamiziba, ia asebar ziaba fer d…®penibar aven, tuavim…®n amiziba ko tuavim…®n gumazibar m…®n otivigh asebar ziam famin arazim…®n g…®n mang…®, dag…®aba bagh tintinibar gumaziba ko amiziba ko dakuan mark…®.\f + \fr 23:17 \ft D…®penir Kenania uan asebar ziaba febar aven, gumazamiziba dar ghua tuavir gumaziba ko tuavir amizir aseba fer d…®penir kabar ingariba isa me koma akui. Men n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim kamak…®n, me arazir kam damu asebar ziaba f…®t…®, aseba men azenibar amut…® da dagher av…®riba ik…®, egh uaghan men as…®zibar amut…®, da nguzir av…®riba batam.\f*
\v 18 Ia uaghan, tuavir amizim o tuavir gumazim…®n arazir kam damigh…®va arazir kam…®n dag…®aba inigh, egh g…®n dag…®ar kaba is…® uan akar d…®k…®r…®zir Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko amizim, anek…®rs…® iz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, an D…®penim…®n aven mangan mark…®. Bar guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God arazir kam ko an dag…®aba, sara bar dar aghua.
\p 
\v 19 \x - \xo 23:19-20 \xt Ua Me Ini 22:25; Ofa Gami 25:36-37; God…®n Araziba 15:7-11\x*‚ÄúEght…® ia uan namakam ateght…® a ian dag…®aba pura da inigh, egh m…®k…®m suam, a g…®n ua da ikarvagham. Eght…® ia dag…®atam uam a gis…®n ua dat…®gh a inian mark…®. Eght…® me n…®n dagheba o bizir igharazitaba pura da inigh, uam da ikarvaghs…® m…®k…®mt…®, ia dagh is…®n bizitaba ua da inis…® men azangs…®ghan mark…®.
\v 20 Ia ik…®zir igharaziba ateght…®, me pura ian biziba inigham, eght…® ia dagh is…®n dag…®ataba ua da ini. Eght…® ian namakaba, ia me da dag…®aba inian mark…®. Ia arazir aghuir kam…®n g…®n mang…®t…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, nguazir ia dat…®r…®gh…®n mang…® dapiamin kam…®n aven, ian bizir ia damuamiba bar, a bizir aghuibar ia damuam.
\p 
\v 21 \x - \xo 23:21 \xt D…®boboniba 30:1-16; Matyu 5:33\x*‚ÄúEght…® ia akar d…®k…®r…®zitam Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, ko a damigh, egh ia zuam…®ra a damight…® an otogh. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian d…®k…®r…®zir akar kam g…®n amadaghan kogham. Ia akar d…®k…®r…®zir kam damight…®, a zuam…®ram otoghan koght…®, ia God…®n damazim…®n os…®mt…®zim iti.
\v 22 Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko akar d…®k…®r…®zim damighan kogh, egh ia os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®gham.
\v 23 Egh ia uari uan ifongiabar g…®n mang…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God bagh akar d…®k…®r…®zim damigh, egh guizbang…®ra an g…®n mang…®.
\p 
\v 24 ‚ÄúEgh ia mang…® uan namakam…®n wain…®n azenim…®n aven mang…®, egh ia uan ifongiabar an azenim…®n wain…®n ov…®zibar am…®, egh ia uari bagh da is…® ak…®rabar aghuigh da inigh mangan mark…®.
\v 25 Egh ia mang…® namakam…®n wit…®n azenim…®n aven mang…®, egh dafaribar wit…®n ov…®zibagh eku ada ini dar am…®. Egh ia wit aghorir sabam…®n dar ghoran mark…®.‚Äù
\c 24
\s1 Gumazim amuim batuegh, amuir igiam iniamin arazim
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 24:1 \xt Matyu 5:31; 19:7; Mak 10:4\x*Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazitam amizitam…®n ik…®, egh g…®n an arazir a ifongezir puvat…®zim…®n ganigh, an am…®ragh…®va, egh amuir ik…®zim ag…®vamin ak…®nafarim osirigh, amizir kam danigh anemadaght…® a mang…®.
\v 2 Eght…® amizir kam mang…® gumazir igharazim…®n ik…®t…®,
\v 3 gumazir kam uaghan an aghuagh…®va, uaghan amuir ik…®zim ag…®vamin ak…®nafarim osirigh a danigh anemadaght…® a mang…®. O an par namba 2 ti areme,
\v 4 eght…® an par faragha an ikezim uam an ikian mark…®. A kamagh…®n fogh, amizir kam an damazim…®n m…®zez…®, an an ikian kogham. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, arazir kam bar an aghua. Ia nguazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God ia gan…®dir kam…®n mang…®gh, egh arazir kurar kam damuan mark…®.‚Äù
\s1 Arazir maba
\p 
\v 5 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazim amizim inigha igiamra an ik…®t…®ma, me m…®dorozir gumazibar ingangarim o gavman…®n ingangarir ekiaba bagh anemangan mark…®. An azenir vam…®ran amuim ko pura nguibam…®n ik…®, egh uan amuim…®n navim damut…®, a deragh.
\p 
\v 6 ‚ÄúIa gumazir igharazim amamangat…®ght…® a pura ia da bizim inight…®, ia an bizitam…®n suiraght…® a ian dafarim…®n ik…®t…®, a fogh, bizir a ia da inizim a uam a ikarvagham. Egh ia an wit…®n ov…®ziba m…®rm…®rir dag…®am inian mark…®. Ia an ingangaribagh amir bizir kaba inight…®, a ua bagh daghebar amuan kogham.
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 24:7 \xt Ua Me Ini 21:16\x*‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam mang…® uan Israelian tav okemegh a damight…®, a puram an ingangarir gumazir k…®nim…®n ikiam, o anemadaght…® gumazir igharazim a givezeght…®, an an ingangarir gumazir k…®nim…®n ik…®t…®, ia gumazir kamagh…®n amizim m…®sueght…® an aremegh. Ia kamagh…®n damigh, arazir kurar kam ia uan tong…®n aneg…®vagham.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 24:8 \xt Ofa Gami 13:1--14:54\x*‚ÄúEght…® duar kurar muziarir av…®riba pura ian m…®karzibar otivt…®, ia deraghv…®ra Livain anabam…®n ofa gamir gumaziba ia m…®k…®mamin biziba bar adar amigh. Egh akar gavgavir k…® me gan…®ngiziba, ia bar dar g…®n mang…®.
\v 9 \x - \xo 24:9 \xt D…®boboniba 12:10\x*Ia Isip ategha azenan izir dughiam…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, Miriam gamizir bizim g…®n…®ghn…®gh.
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 24:10-13 \xt Ua Me Ini 22:26-27\x*‚ÄúIa namakam…®n amamangat…®ght…® a pura ia da dag…®aba inigh, a uan korotiam dag…®ar kaba uam a da ikarvaghamin ababanim…®n m…®n anet…®gh, eght…® ia puram an d…®penim…®n aven mang…®, an korotiar kam inian mark…®.
\v 11 Ia an d…®penim…®n azenan m…®zuam ik…®, eght…® gumazir kam uab…®, d…®penim…®n aven korotiar kam inigh azenan izam.
\v 12 Egh gumazim onganarazibar amu ik…®, uan ikarvazir ababanim bagh, uan inir ekiam ia danight…®, ia inir kam…®n suiragh anevan mark…®.
\v 13 Aruem ghuaghirir dughiamra, ia an inim inigh iz…® uam a dan…®ngigh, eght…® a d…®mangan dakus…® uan m…®karzim avam. Eght…® gumazir kam ia m…®nabaght…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ian arazibagh ifuegham.
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 24:14-15 \xt Ofa Gami 19:13\x*‚ÄúEght…® ian ingangarir gumazim, kar ian anav…®ra o ik…®zir igharazim…®n gumazir ian nguibam…®n aven itim, an onganarazibar amut…®, ia paz…®va a damuan mark…®.
\v 15 Ia guarat…®zibar zurara gumazir kam amir ingangariba bagh an ivezim a dan…®ng. A dag…®aba otevegha da bagha gara pura iti. Ia dag…®aba a danighan koght…®, a ian gun Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n m…®k…®m…®va arangt…®, ia God…®n damazim…®n os…®mt…®zim ikiam.
\p 
\v 16 \x - \xo 24:16 \xt 2 Atriviba 14:6; 2 Eghaghaniba 25:4; Esekiel 18:20\x*‚ÄúGumazitam…®n borim arazir kuratam damight…®, ia an arazir kuram ikarvaghs…®, an amebam ko afeziam m…®sueght…®, aning aremeghan mark…®. Eght…® kamagh…®ra, amebam ko afeziam arazir kuratam damight…®, ia aning…®n arazir kuram ikarvaghs…®, aning…®n boribav sueght…® me ar…®m…®ghiran kogham, Gumazim arazir kuram damight…®, ia anar…®ra m…®sueght…®, an aremegh.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 24:17-18 \xt Ua Me Ini 23:9; Ofa Gami 19:33-34; God…®n Araziba 27:19\x*‚ÄúIa ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamiziba, ko borir amebaba ko afeziaba ariaghireziba, paz…® me damuva, men bizibagh eku da inian mark…®. Eght…® amizir pam ovengezim, pura ia da dag…®atam inight…®, ia dag…®ar kaba uam ada ikarvaghs…® ababanim damu an korotiam inian mark…®.
\v 18 Ia bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh, ia Isip…®n ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ua ia inigha ia gamiz…® ia f…®riagh…®regha azenan ize. Ia fom…®ra bar pazav…®ra ike, kamagh…®n, k…® Akar Gavgavir kam ia gan…®di.
\p 
\v 19-21 \x - \xo 24:19-21 \xt Ofa Gami 19:9-10; 23:22\x*‚ÄúIa azenibar mang…® witba aghoregh dar ik…®ziba inigh, wit…®n ik…®zir taba ategh, ua mang…® ada inian mark…®. Egh ia mang…® oliv…®n temebar ov…®ziba ko wain…®n ikar…®zibar ov…®ziba faragh da akuvagh, egh g…®n ua mang…® ov…®zir ikiav…®ra itiba uam ada inian mark…®. Ia wit…®n ov…®ziba ko oliv ko wain…®n ov…®ziba ateght…® da ik…®. Eght…® ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamiziba ko borir ameboghfeziaba ariaghireziba, ko amizir paba ariaghireziba, me da iniam. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ian akurvaght…®, bizir ia amiba bar deraghv…®ram otivam.
\v 22 Ia bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh, ia fom…®ra Isip…®n ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar ike. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Akar Gavgavir kaba ia gan…®di.‚Äù
\c 25
\p 
\v 1 ‚ÄúDughiar tabar Israel…®n gumazitamning adarim uaning…®n ik…®t…®, jas aning tuis…®gh fogh suam, aning…®n mav os…®mt…®zim iti, ez…® mav puvat…®.
\v 2 Eght…® jas m…®k…®m suam, me gumazir arazir kuram…®n os…®mt…®zim itir kam ifozoreght…®, jas a is…® dakozim…®n anet…®ght…® me jas…®n damazim…®n a m…®sogh mang…® an amizir arazir kuram…®n d…®bobonim…®n tugham.
\v 3 \x - \xo 25:3 \xt 2 Korin 11:24\x*Me 40plan d…®bobonim…®n apengara a ifozoregham. Me ifozorozir bar av…®ribar a damut…®, a gumazamizibar damazim…®n aghums…®zim inigham.
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 25:4 \xt 1 Korin 9:9; 1 Timoti 5:18\x*‚ÄúBulmakau raiz…®n iniba tuir dughiam…®n, ia an akam ikegh…®va dam…®s…® an anogoroghan mark…®.‚Äù
\s1 Gumazir ovengezim…®n amuiroghboribar ganamin Araziba
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 25:5-6 \xt Matyu 22:24; Mak 12:19; Luk 20:28\x*Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAveghbuar pumuning uaning inigh nguazir otevir mam…®n ik…®t…®, aning…®n tav otariba puvat…®gh aremeght…®, an amuim igharaz darazir tav…®n ikian mark…®. Puvat…®. Ovengezir gumazim…®n aveghbuam an amuir odiarim…®n ik…®va a bagh boriba iniam.
\v 6 Eght…® amizim otarir ivariam bateght…® me a m…®k…®m suam, kar an aveghbuar aremezim…®n otarim. Eght…® an ziam Israelian tong…®n kuvaremeghan kogham.
\v 7 \x - \xo 25:7-10 \xt Rut 4:7-8\x*Eght…® ovengezir gumazim…®n aveghbuam amizir kam…®n ikian aghuaght…®, amizim kot…®n danganim…®n mang…®, nguibam…®n gumazir dapanibar gan, kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòNan ivozim God…®n Araziba e m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, a nan ikian aghua. A nan ik…® uan aveghbuam bagh boritam inight…®, kamagh…®n an ziam Israelian tong…®n kuvaremeghan kogham. Ez…® a nan ikian aghua.‚Äô
\v 8 Eght…® nguibam…®n gumazir dapaniba gumazir kam…®n diaght…® a iz…®t…®ma me pamtem…®n a m…®k…®m. Eght…® a nan ikian aghuaght…®,
\v 9 aveghbuam…®n amuir odiarim mang…® gumazir dapanibar damazim…®n otogh, uan par ivozim…®n dagarir asuatam suegh, an guam giparigh suam, ‚ÄòGumazim uan aveghbuam…®n akuraght…®, an ziam ik…® mang…®v…®ra ikian an aghuaght…®, e arazir kam…®n a damuam.‚Äô
\v 10 Eght…® ia Israelia gumazir kam…®n adarazi ziar kam me dar…®gh, ‚ÄòGumazir me dagarir asuam suezim…®n adarasi.‚Äô ‚Äù
\s1 Arazir igharazir pumuning
\p 
\v 11 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúEght…® gumazitamning uaning m…®sogh mang…®t…®, tav…®n amuim d…®kavigh uan pam…®n akuragh igharaztav…®n m…®karzir mogomem gekuight…®ma,
\v 12 ia amizim…®n apangkuvan mark…®. Ia an dafarim atugh a makunigh.
\p 
\v 13-14 \x - \xo 25:13-16 \xt Ofa Gami 19:35-36\x*‚ÄúGumazamiziba uan bizibagh ives…®, ia bagh iz…®t…®, ia dar os…®mt…®zim ab…®ragh ifar dar d…®bobonim otevegh me dan…®ngan mark…®.
\v 15 Ia deragh dar os…®mt…®zibara gan…®va, guiz…®n dar d…®boboniba me dan…®ng. Egh ia kamagh…®n damuva, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God ia gan…®dir nguazim dughiar ruarim…®n an ikiam.
\v 16 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God gumazir kamagh…®n ifavaribagh amiba, a men aghua.‚Äù
\s1 Israelia bar Amalekia m…®sueght…® me ar…®m…®ghiregh
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 25:17-19 \xt Ua Me Ini 17:8-14; 1 Samuel 15:2-9\x*Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Isip ategha izir dughiam…®n, Amalekia arazir kuram ia gamizir bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh.
\v 18 Dughiar kam…®n ia av…®ghaghegha gavgaviba ian g…®vaz…® ia aghumra izi. Ez…® Amalekia God…®n atiatir puvat…®gha, ian g…®n iza ian g…®rak…®rang…®n aghumra izi daraziv sozi me ariaghire.
\v 19 Kamagh…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God kantrin kam ia dan…®ngigh, egh deragh ia av…®night…®, apanir rogh…®ra itiba ia gas…®ghasighan kogham. Eght…® ia bar Amalekia m…®suegh me kuvaremeght…®, gumazamiziba ua me g…®n…®ghn…®ghan kogham. Ia bizir kam, bak…®n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®.‚Äù
\c 26
\s1 Azenibar faragha asir daghebar ofaba
\p 
\v 1 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa mang…® nguazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ia gan…®dim dapiagh g…®vagh,
\v 2 \x - \xo 26:2 \xt Ua Me Ini 23:19\x*egh ia nguazir kam…®n azenir dagher ia faragh asiamba, da is…® ak…®rabar aghuigh da inigh danganir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God uan ziam f…®s…® m…®s…®vamin kam…®n mang…®.
\v 3 Egh mang…® dughiar kam…®n ofa damuamin ofa gamir gumazim batogh a m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòK…® dat…®r…®gh…®n kamagh…®n fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…®n God, uan akar d…®k…®r…®zim gamiz…® a guizbang…®ram oto. Egha na inigha nguazir e dan…®ngasa a en inazir afeziabav kemezir kam…®n aven ize.‚Äô
\p 
\v 4 ‚ÄúEght…® ofa gamir gumazim ia dam ak…®rabar suiragh, da is…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…®n God…®n, ofa gamir dakozim…®n borogh…®n dar afegh.
\v 5 Eght…® ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n, damazim…®n n…® kamagh…®n m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòNan inazir afeziam an Aramian gumazir mam. A uan nguibam ategha tintinibar arua ghua, egha g…®n uan adarazi inigha ghua Isip…®n kantrin apia. Me av…®rasemezir puvat…®gha ghua Isip…®n apia, egha g…®n me bar av…®rasemegha bar gavgafi.
\v 6 Ez…® Isipia en apangkuvir puvat…®gha bar pazav…®ra e gamua, e gamiz…® e men ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar m…®n ikia bar puv…®ra ingari.
\v 7 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en inazir afeziabar God, e uarir akurvaghasa an diava arai. Ez…® a en ararem baregha uaghan en m…®zaziba ko ingangarir ekiar e amiba ko dughiar kurar e isir kam uaghan an gani.
\v 8 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, guizbang…®ra uan gavgavir ekiam…®n arazarazir gavgavir av…®ribagh amua mirakel…®n igharagha garibagh amua, egha bizir kurar igharazibagh amima da me bativiz…® me bar an atiatingi. Kamagh…®ra a ua Isip…®n kantrin e inigha azenan ize.
\v 9 Egha en akua iza nguazir aghuir kam e gan…®ngi. Nguazir kam a bar deraz…®, dagheba an ikia bar deraghav…®ram aghui.
\v 10 O Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® uab…® na gan…®ngizir nguazir kam…®n, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n dagher faragha otiviziba asigha da inigha izi.‚Äô Ia m…®kemegh g…®vagh, egh dat…®r…®gh…®n ak…®rar kam is…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…®n God…®n damazim…®n ofa gamir dakozim…®n anefagh, egh tevimning ap…®righ an ziam f…®.
\p 
\v 11 ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, n…®n God, n…® ko n…®n amuiroghboribagh an…®ngizir bizir aghuiba, n…® da bagh bar akongegh. Eght…® Livaiba ko ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizir ian tong…®n itiba, ia ko uari akuvagh uaghan bar akongegh Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®nab…®.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 26:12 \xt God…®n Araziba 14:28-29\x*‚ÄúEgh dughiabar zurara namba 3…®n azenibar, n…®n azenibar otivir dagheba, n…® da ab…®gh, 10plan pozibav k…®nigh. Egh pozir vam…®ra is…® Livaiba, ko ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizir ian tong…®n itiba, ko borir afeziaba ovengeziba, ko amizir paba ovengeziba, n…® me dan…®ngigh. N…® kamagh…®n damight…®, n…®n nguibam…®n itir gumazamizir kaba, dagheba iz…®vagham.
\v 13 Eght…® n…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…®n God…®n damazim…®n kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòBizir n…® ifongeziba, k…® da tuiragha g…®vaz…®, n…®n bizitam ua nan d…®penim…®n itir puvat…®. K…® Livaiba, ko ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizir ian tong…®n itiba, ko borir afeziaba ovengeziba, ko amizir paba ovengeziba, k…® dagheba bar me gan…®ngi. K…® Akar Gavgaviba bar dar g…®n ghua, n…® na m…®kezir mogh…®ra, k…® n…®n Akar Gavgavitam g…®n amadazir pu. Bar puvat…®.
\v 14 Gumazitam aremez…® k…® a bagh azia uan azirakar kam akakagha n…®n dagher 10plan pozir kabar tam inigha anemezir puvat…®. Egha dughiar k…® n…®n damazim…®n m…®zezim…®n, k…® n…®n d…®penim…®n itir dagher katam inigha azenan ghuzir puvat…®. Egha k…® n…®n dagher kataba inigha gumazir ovengezibar aseba bagha isatam gamizir puvat…®. O Ikiav…®ra Itir God, nan God, k…® n…®n Akar Gavgaviba bar dar g…®n ghua, n…® dagher kabar amuasa m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, k…® bar dagh ami.
\v 15 N…® uan nguibar aghuim…®n p…®n ik…® v…®n kagh Israelia en gan…®va, deraghv…®ram e damu. Egh uaghan nguazir bar aghuir kam, dagheba an ikia bar deraghav…®ram aghui. N…® derav…®ram a damu. Nguazir kam, n…® fom…®ra e dan…®ngasa en inazir afeziabav keme.‚Äô ‚Äù
\s1 Israelia guizbang…®ra bar God…®n gumazamiziba
\p 
\v 16 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúDat…®r…®gh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, kamagh…®n m…®gei, ia an arazir a ifongeziba ko, bizir a damuasa ia m…®kemeziba bar dar g…®n mang…®. Egh uan navir averiam ko duam…®n aven bar dar suiragh, m…®gh…®ghv…®ra arazir kabagh n…®ghn…®gh, bar dar g…®n mang…®.
\v 17 Ia dat…®r…®gh…®n kamagh…®n m…®keme, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a ian God. Egha ia akam ak…®ra ghaze, ia bar deraghv…®ra an tuavim…®n mangam. Egh ia bar God…®n Akar Gavgaviba ko arazir a ifongeziba ko bizir a damuasa ia m…®kemeziba, ia bar dar amuva, egh an akaba baragh.
\v 18 \x - \xo 26:18 \xt Ua Me Ini 19:5; God…®n Araziba 4:20; 7:6; 14:2; Taitus 2:14; 1 Pita 2:9\x*Ez…®, dat…®r…®gh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God, akam ak…®righa ghaze, a ia iniz…® ia bar an gumazamizibara, ez…® a ia m…®kemez…® mogh…®n bar ia gifonge. Egha a uan Akar Gavgavibar g…®n mangasa ia m…®keme.
\v 19 A ia damight…® ia bar av…®rasemegh egh bar gavgavigh, egh nguazir kam…®n itir ik…®zir igharazir a ingarizibagh afiragham. Eght…® me ian arazir aghuim…®n gan…®va, egh bar akuegh ziar ekiam Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God dan…®ngam. Eght…® an akam ak…®riz…® mogh…®n, ia an gumazamizibara ikiam.‚Äù
\c 27
\ms1 Moses ghaze, Israelia ivezir aghuim o kuram, arazir me amiba bagh a iniam
\mr (Sapta 27--30)
\s1 Me dag…®abar God…®n Akar Gavgaviba osiram
\p 
\v 1 Egha Moses ko Israelian gumazir dapaniba, kamagh…®n gumazamizibav gei, ‚ÄúM…®g…®r…®g…®ar k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia gan…®dir kaba ia bar adar g…®n mang…®.
\v 2 \x - \xo 27:2-8 \xt Josua 8:30-32\x*Ia Jordan…®n Fanem giregh vong…®n mang…® nguazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ia gan…®dir kam…®n mang…®, egh aruer kamra dag…®ar ekiar taba arigh arinir ghurghurim dar aghuigh da avaragh.
\v 3 Ia nguazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God ia gan…®dir kam…®n otivigham, mati ian inazir afeziaba God fom…®ra nguazir kam ia dan…®ngasa me ko akam ak…®riz…® mok…®n. Kar nguazir bar aghuim, ez…® dagheba an ikia bar deraghav…®ram aghui. Ia an otivigh, God…®n Arazir kabar m…®g…®r…®g…®aba bar da is…® dag…®ar kabar da osirigh.
\v 4 Ia Jordan…®n Fanem gir…®gh vong…®n otivigh, dag…®ar kaba Ebal…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n da kuazigh, k…® ia m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, arinir ghurghurim dag…®ar kabar aghuigh da avaragh.
\v 5 \x - \xo 27:5-6 \xt Ua Me Ini 20:25\x*Egh ia dag…®ataba is…® dar afegh, egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God bagh ofa gamir dakozim…®n ingar…®va, gumazir ofa gamir dakozim…®n ingariba, ain…®n sobiam o ain…®n haman, dag…®ar kaba ab…®gh da aghoran mark…®.
\v 6 Ia dag…®ar me d…®ghorezir puvat…®ziba inigh, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God bagh ofa gamir dakozim…®n ingarigh. Egh ia ofa gamir dakozir kamra, a bagh ofan bar isia m…®gh…®riba tu.
\v 7 Egh ia God, ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofabar amu, egh danganir kam…®n ofan kam…®n as…®zir tuzim am…®, egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n damazim…®n bar akongegh.
\v 8 Egh dag…®ar ia arinir ghurghurim aghuizir kabar, ia God…®n Arazibar m…®g…®r…®g…®aba bar deraghv…®ram ada osirigh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 Egha Moses Livain anabam…®n ofa gamir gumaziba ko tuivighav ikia, kamagh…®n Israelia m…®gei, ‚ÄúO Israelia! Ia aghumra ik…® deraghv…®ra nan akam baragh. Ia dat…®r…®gh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n gumazamizibar otivigha g…®fa.
\v 10 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n akaba baragh! Ia an Akar Gavgavir k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia gan…®diba ko arazir a ifongeziba, ia bar dar g…®n mang…®.‚Äù
