\v 11 Egha Moses ua Israelia m…®gei,
\v 12 \x - \xo 27:12 \xt God…®n Araziba 11:29; Josua 8:33-35\x*‚ÄúIa Jordan…®n Fanem giregh vong…®n otivigh g…®vagh, aruer kamra Ikiav…®ra Itir God deragh ia damuamin akaba inis…®, ian anabataba mang…®, Gerisim…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n tuifigh, kar Simeon…®n anabam…®n adarasi, ko Livain anabam…®n adarasi, ko Juda, ko Isakar, ko Josep ko Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarasi.
\v 13 Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God gumazir kurabagh as…®ghas…®ghamin akaba inis…®, ian anabar igharaziba mang…® Ebal…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n tuifigh, kar Ruben…®n anabam…®n adarasi, ko Gat…®n anabam…®n adarasi, ko Aser, Sebulun, Dan, ko Naptalin anabam…®n adarasi.
\v 14 Eght…® Livaiba pamten kamagh…®n Israelia m…®k…®m suam,
\v 15 \x - \xo 27:15 \xt Ua Me Ini 20:4; 34:17; Ofa Gami 19:4; 26:1; God…®n Araziba 4:15-18; 5:8\x*‚ÄòGumazitam asetam…®n marvir guam dag…®am…®n an ingari, o temetam…®n anek…®righam, o ain…®n an ingarigh modogh an ziam f…®t…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God gumazir kam gas…®ghasigham. Bizir kaba, kar gumaziba uari ingarizir biziba, ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, gumazamiziba marvir guabar ziaba fan a bar aghua.‚Äô Eght…® gumazamiziba bar kamagh…®n akam ikaragh suam, ‚ÄòBar guizbang…®ra, God kamagh…®ra damu.‚Äô
