\v 16 \x - \xo 27:16 \xt Ua Me Ini 20:12; God…®n Araziba 5:16\x*‚Äú ‚ÄòGumazim uan afeziam ko amebam…®n ziam gas…®ghasight…®, God uaghan a gas…®ghasigham.‚Äô Eght…® gumazamiziba bar kamagh…®n akam ikaragh suam, ‚ÄòBar guizbang…®ra, God kamagh…®ra damu.‚Äô
