\v 17 \x - \xo 27:17 \xt God…®n Araziba 19:14\x*‚Äú ‚ÄòGumazim uan namakam…®n nguazir m…®taghniam gis…®vaght…®, God a gas…®ghasigham.‚Äô Eght…® gumazamiziba bar kamagh…®n akam ikaragh suam, ‚ÄòBar guizbang…®ra, God kamagh…®ra damu.‚Äô
