\v 18 \x - \xo 27:18 \xt Ofa Gami 19:14\x*‚Äú ‚ÄòGumazitam damazir okav…®r…®zim gifaraght…® a tuavir a zuim ateght…®, God gumazir kam gas…®ghasigham.‚Äô Eght…® gumazamiziba bar kamagh…®n akam ikaragh suam, ‚ÄòBar guizbang…®ra, God kamagh…®ra damu.‚Äô
