\v 19 \x - \xo 27:19 \xt Ua Me Ini 22:21; 23:9; Ofa Gami 19:33-34; God…®n Araziba 24:17-18\x*‚Äú ‚ÄòGumazim ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamiziba, ko borir afeziaba ariaghireziba, ko amizir paba ariaghireziba paz…® me damut…®, God gumazir kam gas…®ghasigham.‚Äô Eght…® gumazamiziba bar kamagh…®n akam ikaragh suam, ‚ÄòBar guizbang…®ra, God kamagh…®ra damu.‚Äô
