\v 20 \x - \xo 27:20 \xt Ofa Gami 18:8; 20:11; God…®n Araziba 22:30\x*‚Äú ‚ÄòGumazim uan afeziam…®n amuim ko dakuight…®, God gumazir kam gas…®ghasigham. Arazir kam afeziam damight…® a bar aghumsigham.‚Äô Eght…® gumazamiziba bar kamagh…®n akam ikaragh suam, ‚ÄòBar guizbang…®ra, God kamagh…®ra damu.‚Äô
