\v 21 \x - \xo 27:21 \xt Ua Me Ini 22:19; Ofa Gami 18:23; 20:15\x*‚Äú ‚ÄòGumazitam poroghamiba uari ko akuir arazim…®n as…®zitam damight…®, God gumazir kam gas…®ghas…®gham.‚Äô Eght…® gumazamiziba bar kamagh…®n akam ikaragh suam, ‚ÄòBar guizbang…®ra, God kamagh…®ra damu.‚Äô
