\v 22 \x - \xo 27:22 \xt Ofa Gami 18:9; 20:17\x*‚Äú ‚ÄòGumazim uan buaramizim ko dakuigham, kar ti an guiz…®n buaramizim, o an afeziam ko amuir igharazim otezir guivim, o an amebam ko par igharazim otezir guivim. God gumazir kam gas…®ghasigham.‚Äô Eght…® gumazamiziba bar kamagh…®n akam ikaragh suam, ‚ÄòBar guizbang…®ra, God kamagh…®ra damu.‚Äô
