\v 23 \x - \xo 27:23 \xt Ofa Gami 18:17; 20:14\x*‚Äú ‚ÄòGumazim uan asamir amebam ko dakuigham, God gumazir kam gas…®ghasigham.‚Äô Eght…® gumazamiziba bar kamagh…®n akam ikaragh suam, ‚ÄòBar guizbang…®ra, God kamagh…®ra damu.‚Äô
