\v 24 ‚Äú ‚ÄòGumazim modogh gumazir igharazim m…®sueght…® an aremegham, God gumazir kam gas…®ghasigham.‚Äô Eght…® gumazamiziba bar kamagh…®n akam ikaragh suam, ‚ÄòBar guizbang…®ra, God kamagh…®ra damu.‚Äô
