\v 26 \x - \xo 27:26 \xt Galesia 3:10\x*‚Äú ‚ÄòGumazitam ak…®nafarim…®n aven itir Araziba bar derav…®ra dar g…®n mangan koght…®, God gumazir kam gas…®ghasigham.‚Äô Eght…® gumazamiziba bar kamagh…®n akam ikaragh suam, ‚ÄòBar guizbang…®ra, God kamagh…®ra damu.‚Äô ‚Äù
\c 28
\s1 God…®n akam…®n g…®n zuir gumazamiziba, a derav…®ra me damuam
\r (Ofa Gami 26:3-13; God…®n Araziba 7:12-26)
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 28:1-14 \xt God…®n Araziba 11:13-17\x*Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n akaba ia bar deraghav…®ra da baregh, egh Akar Gavgavir k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia gan…®dibar g…®n mang…®t…®, God ziar ekiam ia dan…®ng…®va ia damight…® ia bar av…®rasemegh bar gavgavigh, nguazir kam…®n ik…®zir igharazibagh afiragham.
\v 2 Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n akabar g…®n mang…®t…®, a bizir aghuir kaba bar ia dan…®ngam.
\p 
\v 3 ‚ÄúEgh God ian nguibaba ko ian azeniba bar deraghv…®ra dar amuam.
\p 
\v 4 ‚ÄúEgh God borir av…®riba ia dan…®ngt…®, ian azeniba dagheba bar iz…®vaght…®, a bulmakauba ko sipsip…®n av…®riba ia danigham.
\p 
\v 5 ‚ÄúEgh God, ian dagheba aven itir ak…®rar ekiaba ko bret…®n ingarir itarir ekiaba, deragh dar amut…®, da bar izevegham.
\p 
\v 6 ‚ÄúEgh God ia amir ingangaribar amut…® da bar deraghv…®ram otivam.
\p 
\v 7 ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, apanir ia m…®soghs…® izamiba, a ian damazim…®n me d…®kab…®nam. Me tuavir vam…®ran izegh…®va ua tuavir av…®ribar tintinibar aregham.
\p 
\v 8 ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, ingangarir ia amibar amight…® da deraght…®, ian dagheba av…®rasemeght…®, dar ar…®ghamin d…®peniba bar izevegham. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, nguazir ia gan…®dir kam…®n aven, a deraghv…®ra ia damuam.
\p 
\v 9 ‚ÄúIa deraghv…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ia m…®kemez…® mogh…®n an Akar Gavgavibar g…®n mang…®t…®, a ia ko akam ak…®riz…® mogh…®n ia damight…® ia an gumazamizibaram otivigham.
\v 10 Eght…® nguazim…®n ik…®ziba bar ian gan fogham, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan ziam ia gat…®z…®, ia an gumazamizibara, eght…® me ian atiatingam.
\v 11 Eght…® ia nguazir God ia dan…®ngasa ian inazir afeziaba ko akam ak…®rizim…®n ik…®t…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, borir av…®riba, ko bulmakaun av…®riba ko azenibar dagher av…®riba bar ia dan…®ngam.
\v 12 Amozim Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n agharim…®n iti, ez…® an an dughiamra anemadaght…® a izighiram. Eght…® a ian ingangaribar amut…® da deraghv…®ram otivam. Eght…® ia ik…®zir igharaziba, men adarazir amamangat…®ght…®, me pura ia da biziba inigh g…®n ua da ikarvagham. Eght…® ia bizir bar av…®riba ikiam, kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia igharaziba da pura biziba inian kogham.
\v 13 Egh ia zurara deraghv…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n Akar Gavgavir k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia gan…®dibar g…®n mang…®t…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ia damight…®, ia ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamiziba gativagh men gant…®, me ian apengan ikiam, mati ia men dapanim…®n ik…®t…®, me ian puem…®n ikiam. Egh ia zurara bizir av…®riba ik…®va, bizitam…®n oteveghan kogham, mati ia ik…®zir igharaziba bar dar p…®n iti.
\v 14 Egh ia Akar Gavgavir k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n m…®geir kaba dar g…®n mang…®, egh tam ab…®ghan mark…®. Ia asebar ziaba f…®va men ingangarim damuan mark…®. Bar mark…®.‚Äù
\s1 Gumazir God…®n Akar Gavgaviba ab…®ziba, a me gas…®ghasigham
\r (Ofa Gami 26:14-46)
\p 
\v 15 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n Akar Gavgavir k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia gan…®diba ko arazir a ifongeziba batuegh, deragh dar g…®n mangan koght…®, bizir kurar kaba ia bativam:
\p 
\v 16 ‚ÄúGod ian nguibaba ko ian azenibagh as…®ghasight…®, da bar ikuvigham.
\p 
\v 17 ‚ÄúGod, ian dagheba aven itir ak…®rar ekiaba ko bret…®n ingarir itarir ekiabar amut…®, dar aven itir dagheba bar otevegham.
\p 
\v 18 ‚ÄúGod, paz…® ia damuva, borir av…®riba ia danighan kogham. Eght…® ian azeniba bar ikuvight…®, dagher av…®riba ikian kogham. Eght…® ian bulmakauba ko sipsipba ot…® av…®rasemeghan kogham.
\p 
\v 19 ‚ÄúGod ia amir ingangariba bar dar amut…®, tam bar deragh otoghan kogham.
\p 
\v 20 ‚ÄúIa ak…®rim ragh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, gasaragh arazir kuram damut…®, a dughiar bar kuram ia bagh anemadagh, egh bizir ia damuasava amiba, an adar amight…®, da paz…®v otiv, ia damut…® ia okam n…®ghn…®gh bar osemegham. Egh ian arazir kuraba bang…®n, an os…®mt…®ziba ia dan…®ngt…®, ian apaniba bar ia gas…®ghasigh bar zuam…®ra ia ag…®vagham.
\v 21 Egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God ar…®mariar igharagha garir av…®riba ia bagh da amangight…®, da iz…® ia damu mang…®t…®, ia bar nguazir ia iniamin kam…®n ik…® bar ar…®m…®ghireght…®, ian tav ua ikian kogham.
\v 22 Dughiar kam…®n, an ar…®mariar igharagh garir kuraba ia bagh da amang…®t…®, da ian m…®karzibar otivam. Kar, m…®karziba ber ar…®mariam, ko m…®karziba puv…®ra fer ar…®mariam, ko m…®karziba arugharughamin ar…®mariar kuram. Eght…® God aruem damut…® a bar gavgavigham. Egh an am…®nir puv…®ra fem amadaght…®, a iz…® ian dagher azeniba dar amut…® da bar m…®sigh bar ikuvigham. Eght…® bizir kurar kaba ian ik…® mang…®t…® ia bar ar…®ghiregham.
\v 23 Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God amozim…®n anogoreght…® a izan koght…®, ian nguazim bar m…®sigh dag…®abar m…®n gavgavigham.
\v 24 Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, amozim otegh…®vk…®night…® a nguazir m…®nemeniam ko gigim…®n m…®n otoght…®, am…®nir dafam da is…® ian nguazim…®n izighir…® mang…®t…®, ia bar kuvaremegham.
\p 
\v 25 ‚ÄúEght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian apanibar amamangat…®ght…®, me ia d…®kab…®ragham. Ia me ko m…®soghs…® tuavir vam…®ran mang…®va, egh men ar…® tuavir av…®ribar tintinibar mangegham. Eght…® nguazir kam…®n ik…®ziba bar dar gumazamiziba ian gant…®, bizir kurar kaba ia bativt…®ma, me d…®gavir kuram damuam.
\v 26 Ia ar…®ghireght…®, kuaraziba ko as…®zir atiaba iz…® ian kuabar am…®t…®, gumazir me damut…® me atiating ar…® mangamiba puvat…®gham.
\v 27 Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Isipia gamiz…® mogh…®n, okabar amut…®, da ian m…®karzibar otivam. Eght…® a duar gavgavibar amut…®, da tintinibar ian m…®karzibar otivam. Eght…® duar muziarir av…®riba ian m…®karzibagh iz…®vagh puv…®ra ia g…®z…®ghz…®ght…®, ia uarir an…®ng…®v…®ra ikiam. Eght…® ar…®mariar kaba ak…®right…®, ia ua deraghamin tuaviba puvat…®gham.
\v 28 Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ia damight…®, ian tarazi bar onganight…®, tarazir damaziba okavight…®, tarazi okam n…®ghn…®gham.
\v 29 Egh ia aruer ar…®zim…®n gumazir damazir okavizim…®n m…®n punpunigh daru pura suighsuigh tuavim buri egh tam batoghan kogham. Eght…® bizir ia amiba tam…®n daghetam deragh otoghan kogham, mati gumazim m…®tarmem…®n aven arui mok…®n. Eght…® gumaziba zurara ia ab…®n…®va ian biziba ok…®mam, eght…® gumazir ian akurvaghamiba puvat…®gham.
\p 
\v 30 ‚ÄúEgh ia gumazitam bagh amizim ginabaght…®, gumazir kam an ikeghan kogham. Puvat…®. Gumazir igharazim a gakaghon a gekuigh a ko dakuam. Ia d…®penim…®n ingarigh, egh an ikeghan kogham. Ia wain…®n azenim oparigh, egh an ov…®zibar ameghan kogham.
\v 31 Apaniba ian damazibar ian bulmakaubav sogh…®raright…® da iram, eght…® ia dar tuzitam ameghan kogham. Ia ganv…®ra ik…®t…® me ian donkibagh ekuigh mang…®gh, uam a da inigh izan kogham. Eght…® ian apaniba ian sipsipba ok…®m…®t…®, gumazir ian akurvaghamiba puvat…®gham.
\v 32 Ia pura gant…®, ik…®zir igharazibar gumaziba iz…® ian otariba ko guiviba inigh mangam. Eght…® ia zurara dughiabar me uamateghs…® me bagh tuavir akabar gan mang…® ian damaziba puv…®ra ia damuam. Egh ia ua boriba inigh iz…®s…® bizitam damuva avegham.
\v 33 Egh ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizir ia fozir puvat…®ziba iz…® dagher ia puv…®ra ingarava opariziba iniam. Egh me zurara paz…® ia damu, egh m…®zaziba ia dan…®ngam.
\v 34 Egh ia bizir kurar kabar gan…®va, ian n…®ghn…®ziba deraghan kogh…®va bar onganigham.
\v 35 Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, okar kurar av…®ribar amut…® da ian teviba ko suebar otivam, Guizbang…®ra, okaba ian m…®karziba bar dar anegham. Eght…® okar kaba ak…®right…® ia ua deraghamin tuaviba puvat…®gham.
\p 
\v 36 ‚ÄúEght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ia ko atrivir ia m…®sevezim ko, bar ia is…® kantrin ia ko ian inazir afeziaba fozir puvat…®zim…®n mang…®t…® ia an ikiam. Ia kantrin kam…®n ik…®va, men asebar ziaba fam, aser kabar marvir guaba, me temeba ko dag…®abar da ingari.
\v 37 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kantrin kam…®n ia amadaght…® ia mang…® an ikiam. Eght…® kantrin kam…®n gumazamiziba, ian ganigh aguaghfagh kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, manmagh…®ram amizir bizir kam ia bato. Egh me ia d…®pov ian ingar…®va akam.
\p 
\v 38 ‚ÄúIa dagher ov…®zir av…®riba oparam, eght…® odeziba da ag…®vt…® ia dar ov…®zir vabara iniam.
\v 39 Ia wain…®n azeniba oparigh, egh da deragh b…®s…® dar k…®rva dar aghariba aghoregh, eght…® apiziba dagh as…®ghasight…®, ia wain…®n ov…®ziba inighan kogh, wain…®n d…®pam damigh anemeghan kogham.
\v 40 Eght…® oliv…®n temer av…®rim ian nguazim…®n otivigh bam. Eght…® oliv…®n ov…®ziba t…®ghar magh…®n anis…® damu, puram asigh…®r…® nguazim giram. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia dar borem uarir aghuighan kogham.
\v 41 Egh ia otariba ko guiviba ikiam, eght…® me deraghv…®ra ia ko ikeghan kogham. Apaniba iz…® me inigh uan kantribar mangegham.
\v 42 Eght…® odeziba ian temeba ko azenibar dagheba sara as…®ghasigham.
\p 
\v 43 ‚ÄúEght…® ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizir ian tong…®n itiba, me biziba bar av…®rasemegh bar gavgavigh ghuavanangv…®ra ikiam. Eght…® ia biziba puvat…®ght…® ian gavgavim mag…®r…®gh…®vr…®ra ikiam.
\v 44 Egh me dag…®ar av…®riba ik…®va ian amamangat…®ght…®, ia me da pura da inigh g…®n da ikarvagham. Eght…® ia dag…®ar av…®riba puvat…®ght…®, me ia da biziba pura da inian kogham. Me ia gativagh ian gant…®, ia men apengan ikiam, mati me ian dapanim…®n ik…®t…®, ia men puem…®n ikiam.
\p 
\v 45 ‚ÄúIa Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n akaba bar deraghav…®ra da baregh, Akar Gavgavir a ia gan…®ngiziba ko, arazir a ifongeziba, ia dar g…®n mangan koght…®, os…®mt…®zir kaba ko bizir as…®ghas…®ziba, da ia bativ…®ra ik…® mang…® bar mogh…®ra ia kuavaremegham.
\v 46 Bizir kurar kaba ia ko ian ovavir boriba sara ian tong…®n ik…®t…®, igharaz darazi gan fogh suam, guizbang…®ra kar God ian an…®ngazi.
\v 47 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, bizir aghuir bar av…®riba ia gan…®ngi, ez…® ia, an ingangarim damuasa navir aghuim ko agorogem ian navibar d…®kavir puvat…®.
\v 48 Kamagh…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, apaniba ameght…®, me iz…® ia m…®sogh ia inigh mang…®t…® ia pura men ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar m…®n ik…®t…®, me ia ab…®nt…® ia men ingangarim damuam. Egh m…®tiriaba sara ik…®va, d…®paba bagh ar…®m…®ghir…®va, korotiaba, ko bizir igharaziba sara puvat…®gham. Eght…® apaniba ia d…®kab…®n mang…® bar ia ag…®vagham.
\v 49 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kantrin bar saghuiam…®n itir mam…®n gumaziba inigh izam. Gumazamizir kaba m…®geir akam, ia a g…®fozir puvat…®. Me kuarazir bagabar m…®n zuam…®ra m…®ghegh ia bagh iz…®ghir…®gham.
\v 50 Egh n…® gumazir aruam o borir dozim, ik…®zir kaba n…®n gan n…®n apangkuvighan kogham.
\v 51 Egh me ian bulmakauba, sipsipba, azenibar dagheba, witba ko, wain…®n d…®paba ko oliv…®n boreba, me bar adar amegham. Eght…® m…®tiriam puv…®ra ian agh…®t…® ia bar ar…®ghiregham.
\v 52 Egh me Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ia gan…®ngizir nguazir kaba bar a dagh as…®ghasigham. Eght…® nguibaba av…®nizir d…®vazir gavgavir ia dar aven mongasava amiba, ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim dar iti, eght…® me dagh as…®ghas…®ght…® da bar iregham.
\p 
\v 53 ‚ÄúApaniba iz…® nguibaba ek…®arugh ia m…®sogh ik…®t…®, ia bar dagheba puvat…®gh…®va, uan borir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, ia gan…®ngizibav sogh dar amam.
\v 54-55 Apaniba nguibam bar anek…®arught…®, gumazir aghuir ziam ikia ian tong…®n itim, a bizir damamitam bar puvat…®gh egh, a uaghan uan borim m…®suegh anemam. A kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gham, a dagheba bar puvat…®, ez…® ua tuaviba puvat…®. Egh a uan aveghbuaba, uan amuir aghuiba, ko borir igharazir ikiav…®ra itiba, a me gitagh ramegham. A m…®tiriam bang…®n, borir tuzir nar tam me danighan kogham.
\v 56-57 \x - \xo 28:56-57 \xt 2 Atriviba 6:28-29; Azir Akam 4:10\x*Apaniba nguibam bar anek…®arught…®, amizir aghuir ziaba ikia ian tong…®n dag…®aba ikia dabirabir aghuibagh apiaghiri gumaziba me aneteragharuiba, me dughiar kam…®n, damamin dagheba bar puvat…®gham. Kamagh…®n, a uan borir otibav sogh, dar m…®tariba sara dar amam. Egh a uan par a bar ifongeziba ko, borir igharazir ikiav…®ra itiba, me gitagh ramegham. A kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gham, a dagheba bar puvat…®, ez…® ua tuaviba puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a modogh uan borir iririvim amegham.
\p 
\v 58 ‚ÄúEght…® ia Ak…®nafarir kam…®n itir Akar Gavgavir osiriziba, deragha dar g…®n mangan kogh, deragh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God…®n ziam fan koght…®,
\v 59 an ar…®mariar igharagha garim amadaght…®, a ia ko ian ovavir borir g…®n otivamiba bativam.
\v 60 Egh a Isip…®n ia gan…®ngizir ar…®mariaba ua ia danight…® ia ua deraghan kogham.
\v 61 Egh an ar…®mariar igharagha garir bar kuraba ia dan…®ngam. Ar…®mariar kabar ziaba, Akar Gavgavim itir Ak…®nafarim…®n itir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n, ia bar mogh…®ra gevegham.
\v 62 Ia ghaze, ian d…®bobonim m…®kovezibar m…®n p…®n ikia bar av…®raseme, ez…® puvat…®gham ian varazira ikiam. Guizbang…®ra, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God en God, an akabar g…®n zuir puvat…®, kamagh…®n amiz…®, arazir kaba ia bativam.
\v 63 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ia damut…® ia ot…® bar av…®rasemegh bizir av…®riba ikiasa a ifonge. Kamagh…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God dat…®r…®gh…®n, ia gas…®ghas…®gh bar ia ag…®vasa ifonge. Egh a nguazir ia dat…®r…®gh…®n mang…® dapiamin kam…®n bar ia batuegham.
\p 
\v 64 ‚ÄúEgh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ia amangight…® ia nguazir kam…®n tintinibar kantrin igharazibar mangegham. Ia kantrin kabar ik…®va, men asebar ziaba fam, aser kabar marvir guaba, me temeba ko dag…®abar dar ingari. Ia ko ian inazir afeziaba fom…®ra aser kabar ziaba fer puvat…®.
\v 65 Ia kantrin kabar tong…®n ik…® ian dabirabim deraghan kogham. Egh ia uari nguibaba puvat…®gham. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ia damut…® ia puv…®ram atiating, naviba osemegh, ovengs…®v…®ra n…®ghn…®gham.
\v 66 Ia dughiabar zurara ovengs…® damuam. Egh arueba ko d…®magaribar ia ovevem g…®n…®ghn…®gh atiating ikiam.
\v 67 Ia biziba bar dar gan atiatim ian anangam. Egh dughiabar av…®gh m…®zarazibar suam, ‚ÄòAio! M…®zarazim zuam…®ra mang…®ght…®, Guarat…®zim iz…®t…®, deragham.‚Äô Egh guarat…®zibar ia zurara av…®gh suam, ‚ÄòAio! Guarat…®zim zuam…®ra mang…®ght…®, m…®zarazim iz…®t…®, deragham.‚Äô
\v 68 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, faragha ghaze, ia ua Isip…®n mangan kogham. Ez…® puvat…®, a ia is…® kurim dat…®gh ua ia amadaght…® ia Isip…®n mangam. Egh ia apaniba ateght…®, me ia givezeght…®, ia pura men ingangaribar amus…® ifuegham. Ez…® puvat…®, ia givezamin gumaziba puvat…®gham.‚Äù
\c 29
\s1 God, Moap…®n nguazim…®n, Israelia ko Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim gami
\p 
\v 1 Kar Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses m…®kemez…®, a Moap…®n nguibam…®n Israelia koma amizir Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n akaba. God, faragha Sainain M…®ghs…®am…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir me koma amizim, a ighara. Dat…®r…®gh…®n God akar maba sara isafuragha, me gan…®ga Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam gami.
\p 
\v 2 Moses Israelian diaz…® me iza uari akuvaz…® a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa bar mogh…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Isipian atrivim ko an ingangarir gumaziba bar, ko an nguazim bar, a me gamizir mirakel…®n biziba ia uan damazibar dar gani.
\v 3 Egha ia uan damazibar, ar…®mariar kurar av…®riba, ko arazarazir kuraba, ko d…®gavir kuram gamir arazir av…®rir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Isipian akazibar gani.
\v 4 Egha fom…®ra iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ia gamiz…®, ian n…®ghn…®ziba, ko damaziba ko kuariba p…®righav…®ra itima, ia deraghav…®ra bizir kabar m…®ngaribagh fozir puvat…®ghav…®ra iti.
\v 5 \x - \xo 29:5 \xt God…®n Araziba 8:2-4\x*Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòK…® 40plan azenibar ia inigha gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n zuima, ian korotiaba ko dagarir asuaba d…®ghoraghirezir pu. Bar puvat…®.
\v 6 Ia bret, ko wain, ko d…®par onganiba puvat…®z…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra God, k…® deraghav…®ra ian gari. K…® kamagh…®n ifonge, ia kamagh…®n fogh suam, K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…®rara ian God.‚Äô ‚Äù
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 29:7 \xt D…®boboniba 21:21-35\x*Egha Moses ua m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúE danganir kam…®n otiviz…®, Hesbon…®n Atrivim Sihon, ko Basan…®n Atrivim Ok, aning e m…®soghasa ize. Ez…® e aning m…®sogha aning ab…®ra.
\v 8 \x - \xo 29:8 \xt D…®boboniba 32:33\x*Egha e aning…®n nguazimning inigha aning tuiragha, Ruben…®n anabam ko, Gat…®n anabam ko, Manasen anabar me tuirazimning…®n mam, me gan…®ngi, eght…® me dar apiam.
\v 9 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia zurara Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam deraghv…®ra an g…®n mang…®, eght…® bizir ia amiba bar deragh otivam.
\p 
\v 10 ‚ÄúIa dat…®r…®gh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, an damazim…®n m…®tivighav iti. Kar, ian anababar gumazir dapaniba, ko ian gumazir aruaba, ko ian ingangaribar faragha zuir gumaziba, ko Israelian gumazir igharaziba,
\v 11 ko ian amuiba, ko boriba, ko ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizir ian tong…®n itiba. Gumazamizir kaba, ian daziba ko d…®paba isa ia bagha da atera izi.
\v 12 Ia gumazamizir dat…®r…®gh…®n bar kagh tuivighav itir kaba, dat…®r…®gh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ia ko Akar D…®k…®r…®zir igiam damuam. Egh ia Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam…®n g…®n mang…®s…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko n…®ghn…®zir vam…®ra ik…® anek…®righ.
