\v 14-15 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ia gumazir dat…®r…®gh…®n an damazim…®n tuivighav itir kabanang baghav…®ra Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam gamizir puvat…®. A uaghan en ovavir borir g…®n izamiba bagha a gami. Eght…® e bar, an g…®n mang…®s…® akam ak…®ram.
