\v 16 ‚ÄúIa e Isip…®n kantrin ikezir ik…®r…®m…®rim uam a g…®n…®ghn…®gh. Egh uaghan ia tuavim…®n iza ik…®zir igharazibar nguaziba ab…®gha izezir bizir ganizibagh n…®ghn…®gh.
