\v 22 ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, gumazir kam…®n nguazim damight…®, bizir kuraba ko os…®mt…®zir av…®riba a bativam. Eght…® an ovavir borir g…®n otivamiba, ko gumazamizir kantrin saghuiabar ikegha izeziba, bizir kurar kabar ganam.
\v 23 \x - \xo 29:23 \xt Jenesis 19:24-25\x*Eght…® ian nguazim, avim bar an isight…®, a nguazir k…®nim gavaght…®, salfan dag…®aba ko amangs…®ziba a giz…®vagh, graziba puvat…®ght…® dagheba oparamin danganir aghuiba puvat…®gham. A Sodom, ko Gomoran nguibar ekiamning…®n m…®n gan, egh uaghan Atma ko Seboim…®n ngubamning…®n m…®n ganam. Nguibar ekiar kaba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God dar an…®ngaghegha bar adagh as…®ghas…®ki.
