\v 11 ‚ÄúAkar Gavgavir k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia gan…®dir kaba, ia dar g…®n mang…®s…® iburaghburaghan mark…®. Ez…® Akar Gavgavir kaba ian saghon itir puvat…®.
\v 12 \x - \xo 30:12-14 \xt Rom 10:6-8\x*Akar kam overiam…®n itir puvat…®, ia kamagh…®n azangan mark…®, ‚ÄòTina God…®n Nguibam…®n mavanang a inigh izighir…® an gun m…®k…®mt…®, e ti a baragh an g…®n mangam?‚Äô
\v 13 Egha uaghan akar kam ongarim…®n vong…®n itir puvat…®, eght…® ia kamagh…®n azangan mark…®, ‚ÄòTinara vong…®n mang…® a inigh iz…®va an gun m…®k…®mt…®, e ti a baragh an g…®n mangam?‚Äô
\v 14 Ez…® puvat…®. God…®n akam bar n…®n borogh…®ra iti, a n…®n akatorim ko n…®n navir averiam…®n aven iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia dughiabar zurara an g…®n mang…®.
