\v 15 ‚ÄúIa gan, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n tuavir pumuning ia bagha aning at…®. Tuavir mam, ia an g…®n mang…®, egh ia angam…®ra itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim ik…®, zurara bar deraghv…®ra ikiam. Egh ia tuavir igharazim…®n g…®n mang…®t…®, bizir bar kuraba ia bagh iz…® ia gas…®ghas…®ght…®, ia ar…®m…®ghiregham.
\v 16 K…® kamaghsua ia m…®gei. Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n Akar Gavgavir k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia m…®geiba baragh, egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God gifuegh an tuavibar g…®n mang…®va an Akar Gavgaviba ko, arazir a ifongeziba ko, bizir a damuasa ia m…®kemeziba, bar dar amuva, ik…® borir av…®riba bat…® bar av…®rasemegham. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ian God, nguazir ia mang…® ikiamim…®n, a deraghv…®ra ia damuam.
