\v 17 ‚ÄúEgh ia uan navir averiabar aven akam batuegh, uamategh mang…®, ik…®zir igharazibar amamangat…®ght…®, me ia gekut…®, ia ik…®zir igharazibar asebar ziaba f…®, dar ingangarim damut…®,
\v 18 k…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ian apaniba bar ia gas…®ghasigh bar ia ag…®vagham. Eght…® ia Jordan…®n Fanem…®n vong…®n iniamin nguazim dughiar ruarim…®n an ikeghan kogham.
\v 19 K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n overiam ko nguazim…®n diaght…®, aning nan gan egh fogham, k…® guizbang…®ra tuavir kamning ia bagha aning at…®. Tuavir mam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God deragh ia damut…® ia dughiar ruarim…®n ik…®v…®ra ikiam. Eght…® tuavir igharazim…®n, God ia gas…®ghasigh bar mogh…®ra ia kuavaremegham. Ia dat…®r…®gh…®n tuavir manam am…®s…®vam? Ia tuavir aghuim…®n g…®n mangasa k…® ifonge, eght…® ia ko ian ovavir boriba sara angam…®ra ikiam.
\v 20 \x - \xo 30:20 \xt Jenesis 12:7; 26:3; 28:13\x*K…® kamaghsua, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, bar a gifongegh, egh an akaba baragh pamtem…®n an suiraghv…®ra ik…®. Ia kamagh…®n damut…®, ia ko ian ovavir boriba, nguazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian inazir afeziaba, Abraham, Aisak ko Jekop, dan…®ngasa akam ak…®rizim, ia dughiar ruarim…®n an ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.‚Äù
\c 31
