\v 2 \x - \xo 31:2 \xt D…®boboniba 20:12\x*A ghaze, ‚ÄúNan azeniba, dat…®r…®gh…®n 120…®n oto, ez…® k…® deraghav…®ra mang…® izegh damuan ibura. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God na m…®g…®a ghaze, N…®n darorim iza kamagh…®ra tu. Ez…® n…® Jordan…®n Fanem gir…®gh vong…®n mang…®ghan kogham.
\v 3 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, a uab…® ian faragh mang…® Jordan…®n Fanem gir…®gh vong…®n mang…®, ian damazim…®n danganir kam…®n itir ik…®zibagh as…®ghasight…®, ia men nguazim iniam. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, Josua ian gumazir dapanim…®n ik…® ian faragh mangam.
\v 4 \x - \xo 31:4 \xt D…®boboniba 21:21-35\x*Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God nguazir kam…®n itir ik…®zir kabagh as…®ghasigham, mati a fom…®ra Amorian atrivimning Sihon ko Ok, aning…®n nguazimning gas…®ghas…®ghiz…® mok…®n.
\v 5 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, bar me is…® n…®n dafarim dar…®gham. Eght…® k…® ia m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, ia bar me m…®soght…® me ar…®m…®ghiregh.
