\v 8 \x - \xo 31:8 \xt Josua 1:5; Hibru 13:5\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…® ko iti, egh a n…®n faragh mangam. An ak…®rim ragh n…® gasaragh, n…® ateght…® n…® ikuvighan kogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribar amu atiatingan mark…®.‚Äù
