\v 17 Eght…® k…® dughiar kam…®n bar men an…®ngaghegham. Egh k…® me ategh, egh uan guam bar men modogham. Eght…® me bar mogh…®ra ikuvigham. Eght…® bizir kurar av…®rim me bativt…®, me dar gan fogh suam, ‚ÄòGod ti e ko itir puvat…®z…®, bizir kurar kaba e batifi.‚Äô
\v 18 Me arazir kurar kam damuva, na ategh asebar ziaba fam. Eght…® men arazir kurar kam bang…®n, k…® dughiar kam…®n uan guam bar men modogh, men akurvaghs…® tong n…®ghn…®ghan kogham.
