\v 19 ‚ÄúK…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ighiar kam Josua ko Moses, gua m…®k…®mt…®, gua uaning bagh an osirigh. Egh Moses, n…® an Israelian gumazamizibar sure damight…®, a men navir averiabar ik…®t…®, me zurara ighiar kam…®n akabagh n…®ghn…®gh, fogh suam, k…® guizbang…®ra ikiangs…®zir kam me gan…®ga ghaze, me na atagh…®raghs…® n…®ghn…®ghan kogham.
