\v 23 \x - \xo 31:23 \xt D…®boboniba 27:23; Josua 1:6\x*Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Nun…®n otarim, Josua m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® tugh gavgavigh bizitam…®n atiatingan mark…®. N…® Israelia inigh nguazir k…® me dan…®ngasa akam ak…®rizir kam…®n mang…®. Eght…® k…® zurara ia ko ikiam.‚Äù
