\v 6 Egha Moses Ruben…®n anabam…®n adaraziv g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIan anabam…®n d…®bobonim, bar av…®rasemeghan kogham. Eght…® ia zurara ik…®v…®ra ikiam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 7 Egha a Judan anabam…®n adaraziv g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Judaba uarir akurvaghasa n…®n dei, ez…® n…® me barakigh. Egh men aku iz…® men igharaz darazi ko ua me akufagh. Eght…® me uan apaniba ko m…®soghamin dughiam…®n n…® men akuragh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 33:8 \xt Ua Me Ini 17:7; 28:30; D…®boboniba 20:13\x*Egha a Livain anabam…®n adaraziv g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Livain anabam…®n adarasi, me n…® baghav…®ra itir ingangarir gumazir aghuiba, n…® dag…®ar n…®n ifongiam g…®fofoghamin kamning me gan…®ngi. N…® Masan danganim ko Meriban D…®par Em…®m…®rim…®n, men ganigh foghasa os…®mt…®zim me gan…®ngi, ez…® men araziba dera.
\v 9 N…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim ko n…®n Akar Gavgaviba, me gavgavigha dar g…®n zui. Me uan ameboghfeziaba, ko namakaba, ko boribar ifongiabar g…®n mangan aghua.
\v 10 Egh Livaiba n…®n Araziba ko bizir n…® damuasa me m…®kemezibar Israelian sure damuam. Eght…® me pauran mughuriar aghuim zuiba is…® n…®n damazim…®n dar ar…®gh, n…®n ofa gamir dakozim…®n ofan bar isia m…®gh…®ribar amuam.
\v 11 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® Livain anabam…®n ofa gamir gumazibar akuraght…® me gavgavight…®, n…® me amir ingangarim bagh bar akongegh. Egh men apanir me gifongezir puvat…®ziba, bar me d…®kab…®ragh me ab…®night…®, me ua d…®kavan kogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 12 Egha a kamagh…®n Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adaraziv g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n Bar P…®n Itim, bar Benjamin…®n adarazigh ifuegha, dughiaba bar, a men borogh…®ra ikia me av…®nigha, me geghufi. Ez…® me dughiabar an d…®p…®zim…®n deraghav…®ra ikia avughsi.‚Äù
\p 
\v 13 Egha a kamagh…®n Josep…®n anabam…®n adaraziv g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, deragh Josep…®n adarazir amu. K…® God…®n azai, eght…® an overiam…®n itir amozim amadaght…®, a Josep…®n nguazim…®n izighir…®t…®, nguazir averiam…®n aven itir d…®par av…®riba anang…®va otiv nguazim giz…®vam.
\v 14 Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, deragh men azenibar amut…®, aruem dagher guar av…®ribagh isiraght…®, da uan dughiamram asegh egh aniam.
\v 15 Eght…® m…®ghs…®ar fom…®ra itiba, dat…®r…®gh…®n azenibar ingaramin danganir aghuibar otivt…®, dagher guar av…®rir aghuiba azenir kabagh iz…®vagham.
\v 16 Josep uan aveghbuabar gumazir dapanim…®n iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azangs…®si, eght…® a bizir kabar amight…® da Josep…®n anabam…®n adarazi bativ. Dagher bar aghuiba, Josep…®n adarazir nguazim…®n azenibagh iz…®vagham. K…® fo, God fom…®ra Sainain M…®ghs…®am…®n ikia, temer otevir mam…®n aguabar tong…®n avir m…®zariabar aven ikia na bativa na m…®gei. Ez…® k…® fo, a uaghan deraghv…®ra Josep…®n adarazir amuam.
\v 17 Josep…®n anabam, mati bulmakaun atiar apurir kom…®n pumuning itim…®n m…®n bar gavgafi. An otarir mam Manase, an ovavir borir bar av…®rim, me bar gavgavigha, mati bulmakaun kam…®n kom…®n mam. Ez…® an otarir igharazim Efraim, an ovavir borir bar av…®rim, me bar gavgavigha, mati bulmakaun kam…®n kom…®n igharazim. Egh aning uan kom…®n kamning…®n ik…®zir igharazibagh iniv me akunt…®, me saghon tintinibar nguazir kam…®n m…®kebaba bar dagh iregham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 18 Egha Moses kamagh…®n Sebulun ko Isakar…®n anabamning…®n adaraziv g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa Sebulun anabam…®n adarasi, ian dag…®ar ingangarir ia ik…®zir igharaziba ko amiba, da derav…®ram otivam. Eght…® Isakar, n…®n nguibam…®n itir dag…®ar ingangarim, a uaghan deragh otivam.
\v 19 Egh aning uan ik…®zir igharazibar diaght…® me aning…®n m…®ghs…®am…®n iz…®, egh me ofan aghuim damuam. Egh me bizir ongarir averiam…®n inizibar dag…®ar ingangaribar amuva, egh gigim…®n aven modozir bizibar, dag…®ar ingangaribar amuam. Egh ingangarir kam…®n, me dag…®ar av…®riba iniam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 20 Egha Moses kamagh…®n Gat…®n anabam…®n adaraziv g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, Gat…®n anabam…®n nguazim gamiz…®, an ekefe. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia bar an ziam f…®. Gat…®n adarasi, laion…®n m…®n, as…®zim m…®suegh an agharim asigham o, an dapanir inim adeghasa a m…®zua iti.
\v 21 Israelian gumazir dapaniba nguaziba tuiragh uari dan…®ngasa uari akuvagha, Gat…®n adarazi bagha nguazir bar aghuim ginabaz…® me a ini. Gat inizir nguazir otevir kam, a gumazir dapaniba iniamin nguazim…®n m…®n ghu. Ez…®, Gat…®n adarazi deraghav…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n guiz…®n araziba ko bizir a damuasa Israelia m…®kemezibar g…®n zui.‚Äù\f + \fr 33:21 \ft Hibrun akam vez…®n kam deragha a m…®geir puvat…®.\f*
\p 
\v 22 Egha a kamagh…®n Dan…®n anabam…®n adaraziv g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúDan…®n anabam…®n adarasi, mati laion…®n igiam, Basan…®n danganim…®n dag…®ar afam…®n ikegha uab…® ekura izi.‚Äù
\p 
\v 23 Egha a kamagh…®n Naptalin anabam…®n adaraziv g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God deragha Naptali gamua egha bizir bar aghuiba isa a gan…®ngi. Ez…® men nguazim Galilin D…®par Akarer m…®riam…®n ikegha ghua saut ko aruem ghuaghiri nagh…®n amadaghan iraghu.‚Äù
\p 
\v 24 Egha a kamagh…®n Aser…®n anabam…®n adaraziv g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, Aser…®n aveghbuabar tong…®n bar a gifongegh deraghv…®ra a damuam. Eght…® bizir kam…®n, a bar me gafiragham. Eght…® an oliv…®n temeba bar puv…®ra b…®t…®, an oliv…®n borer av…®rim iniam.
\v 25 Eght…® an nguibar ekiaba av…®nizir d…®vaziba, ain…®n itiar akar gavgaviba ikiam. Eght…® a zurara dar aven deraghv…®ra ik…®va, atiatingan kogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 26 Egha Moses kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúO Israelia, god…®n tam ua en God…®n m…®n itir puvat…®. A gavgavir ekiam ko angazangarim…®n aven m…®dorozir karis gaperagha, ian akurvaghasa ghuariam gis…®n izi.
\v 27 God…®n Zurara Itim, an en mogomer danganim. A zurara uan dafarimning…®n ian suigha ia atagh…®razir puvat…®. Ia mang…® Kenan…®n nguazim iniamin dughiam a ian faragh mang…®, ian apaniba batuegh ia m…®kemeght…®, ia mang…® me m…®sogh…®rarigham.
\v 28 Eght…® Jekop…®n ovavir boriba nguazir kam dapiagh deraghv…®ra ik…®t…®, apaniba ua iz…® me ko m…®soghan kogham. Nguazir me itir kam, d…®magarim…®n ghuariar d…®paba izighir…® a ruam, eght…® wit ko wain…®n av…®riba an otivt…® me da iniam.
\v 29 O Israelian gumazamiziba, ia bar akongegh! Ikiav…®ra Itir God ian akurvazi mogh…®n, a ik…®zir igharazitaba kamagh…®n men akurvaghizir puvat…®. Ikiav…®ra Itir God mati oram…®n m…®n ian p…®gha ian akurvasi. Egh a mati m…®dorozir sabam…®n m…®n, ian apanibav sogh…®raright…® me ar…®m…®ghiram. Eght…® ian apaniba iz…® uarir apangkuvs…® ian azangs…®gham. Eght…® ia me d…®k…® me ab…®nam.‚Äù
\c 34
\s1 Moses areme
\p 
\v 1 Egha Moses Moap…®n danganir zarim ategha, Nebon M…®ghs…®am…®n ghuavanabogha, ghua Pisgan M…®ghs…®am…®n orazim…®n ghuavanabo, kar Jerikon nguibam…®n aruem anadi nak…®n. Egha Moses danganir kam…®n tughav itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, nguazir a Israelia dan…®ngamiba bar an aka. Nguazir kam, a Gileat…®n nguazim…®n ikegha ghua Dan…®n anabam…®n nguazim…®n tu, a not…®n amadaghan iti,
\v 2 egha ghua Naptalin anabam…®n nguazim ko Efraim…®n anabam…®n nguazim ko, Manasen anabam…®n nguazim ko, Judan anabam…®n nguazim bar ghua Mediterenian…®n Ongarir Ekiam…®n tu, an aruem ghuaghiri nagh…®n iti.
\v 3 Egha a Judan anabam…®n amadaghan saut…®n nguazir ekiam Moses…®n aka. Ez…® danganir zarir ekiam, nguibar kam Jeriko an iti, a det…®n temer av…®riba iti. Israelian nguazim, a Jerikon nguazir zarir kam…®n ikegha ghua Soar…®n danganim…®n tu, a saut…®n amadaghan iti.
\v 4 \x - \xo 34:4 \xt Jenesis 12:7; 26:3; 28:13\x*Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® fom…®ra Abraham ko Aisak ko Jekop koma akam ak…®righa ghaze, K…® nguazir kam is…® men ovavir boribar an…®ngam. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® n…® ataghiz…® n…® an ganigha g…®fa. Eght…® k…® n…® ateght…® n…® an aven mang…®ghan kogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® God…®n ingangarir gumazim Moses, Ikiav…®ra Itir God a m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, a Moap…®n nguazim…®n ikiava areme.
\p 
\v 6 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Moap…®n danganir zarim…®n Moses…®n kuam afa, a Betpeor…®n nguibam…®n vong…®n iti. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n gumazitam fozir puvat…®, danganir manam…®n Moses…®n mozim iti.
\v 7 Moses 120plan azeniba ikia egha areme. Egha gavgavighv…®ra iti, ez…® an damaziba dera.
\v 8 Moses aremegha g…®vaz…®, Israelia Moap…®n danganir zarim…®n ikia a bagha azia a g…®bua ikia ghua 30plan aruebar tu.
\p 
\v 9 Bizir kabar g…®n, God fofozir av…®riba ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba isa Nun…®n otarim Josua gan…®ngi. Me bar fo, Moses faragha uan danganim iniasa anem…®sefe. Ez…® gumazamiziba Josuan akam baragha, Akar Gavgavir Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses gan…®ngizibar g…®n zui.
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 34:10 \xt Ua Me Ini 33:11\x*Bar fom…®ra iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, Israelian tong…®n God…®n akam inigha izir gumazitam Moses…®n m…®n otozir puvat…®. Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses ko m…®gei, mati gumazir pumuning uaning ko m…®gei.
\v 11 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, mirakel…®n igharagha garibagh amuava Isip…®n atrivim ko an ingangarir gumaziba, ko an nguazim sara bar puv me damuasa Moses amada. God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir igharazitaba, me Moses…®n m…®n mirakel…®n kamagh…®n garitabagh amizir puvat…®.
\v 12 Moses Israelian gumazamizibar damazim…®n amiz…® mogh…®n, me gumazamizibar amut…® me atiatingamin arazarazir ekiatabar amighan kogham.
